TT 3123 "Knowing how you play helps us improve our games!~ ~In order to ensure the best possible quality of the game's current and future content, we (Asobo Studio and Focus Entertainment) wish to collect and process data that will be useful to us. This includes information about the way you play, as well as error logs and hardware configuration. This process is entirely automatic and confidential, and this data will be automatically deleted after a maximum period of two years. You may also disable or reenable telemetry in the Settings Menu at any moment.~ ~To learn more about how we process this data and to exercise your rights, please refer to:" TRC__TELEMETRY_DESC
