TT 3168 "Press {STR_CROUCH} to ^761crouch^000." TUTO__CROUCH
TT 3169 "The sound of your sling will attract enemies to you.~For ^761greater discretion^000, hold {STR_WEAPON_SELECTION_OPEN} to use projectiles in another way." TUTO__DONT_SLING
TT 3170 "All of your ammunition can be shot with any of your weapons. ~Select the ^761Sling^000 using {STR_CUSTOM1}." TUTO__EFFECT_SELECT
TT 3171 "Lighting embers with the ^761Ignifer^000 helps you find your way among the rats." TUTO__EMBERS
TT 3172 "Press {STR_INTERACT} to ^761distract^000 an enemy that has been alerted to your presence." TUTO__EMERGENCY_DISTRACT
TT 3173 "Exstinguis ammunition can ^761put out fires^000. ~Aim at a lit fire and throw an Exstinguis to put it out." TUTO__EXTINGUISH
