TT 3181 "Press {STR_TRAVERSAL} again before you ^761run out of air^000 and alert surrounding enemies." TUTO__FREEZE_WATER_RELEASE
TT 3182 "To be stealthier you can throw projectiles by ^761hand^000.~Hold {STR_WEAPON_SELECTION_OPEN} to open the selection menu." TUTO__HANDTHROW
TT 3183 "You picked up a ^761pot^000. ~Hold {STR_WEAPON_SELECTION_OPEN} to open the selection menu" TUTO__HANDTHROW_JAR
TT 3184 "Select the ^761pot throw^000 using {STR_CUSTOM1}." TUTO__HANDTHROW_JAR_SWITCH
TT 3185 "Select the ^761hand throw^000 using {STR_CUSTOM1}." TUTO__HANDTHROW_SWITCH
TT 3186 "You can eliminate enemies by shooting at their ^761heads with your sling^000. Hold {STR_AIM_MODE} to aim then hold {STR_SHOOT} to ^761prime^000 and release to shoot." TUTO__HEADSHOT
TT 3187 "The sling is ^761ineffective against helmeted enemies^000. ~Be discreet and avoid direct confrontation." TUTO__HELMET
TT 3188 "Hugo can ^761crawl in tight spaces^000. Hold {STR_COMPANION_ORDER_MODE} to display available options." TUTO__HUGO_CRAWL
TT 3189 "Hold {STR_COMPANION_ORDER_MODE}, aim at the passage and press {STR_COMPANION_ORDER_INTERACT} to ^761ask him to crawl through^000." TUTO__HUGO_CRAWL_ORDER
TT 3190 "Using Hugo's abilities will increase his ^761stress level^000.~Use them with caution to avoid overstressing him." TUTO__HUGO_GAUGE
TT 3191 "The Ignifer lets you light embers onto which it is thrown.~Hold {STR_THROW_AIM_MODE} to ^761aim at embers^000." TUTO__IGNIFER
TT 3192 "Shoot an ^761Ignifer^000 with {STR_SHOOT} into embers to light them up." TUTO__IGNIFER_THROW
TT 3193 "When holding a flammable item, press {STR_INTERACT} near a fire source to ^761light it^000." TUTO__IGNITE
TT 3194 "Hold {STR_THROW_AIM_MODE} to aim and then use {STR_SHOOT} to throw the ^761pot^000. ~The circle indicates its ^761area of effect^000." TUTO__JAR_AIM_SHOOT
TT 3195 "Approach ^761stealthily behind^000 Lucas and hold {STR_SLING_SLASH} to scare him." TUTO__LUCAS_SCARE
TT 3196 "Approach ^761stealthily behind^000 an unarmoured enemy and hold {STR_SLING_SLASH} to kill him." TUTO__MELEE_BACK
TT 3197 "Hold {STR_SLING_SLASH} to ^761counter^000 an attacking enemy." TUTO__MELEE_COUNTER
TT 3198 "Hold {STR_SLING_SLASH} to strike and ^761kill an unarmoured enemy^000 in close combat with your sling." TUTO__MELEE_FINISH
TT 3199 "Attacking an enemy in close combat makes ^761noise^000 and alerts nearby enemies." TUTO__MELEE_NOISE
