TT 3206 "Shoot at ^761tar jars^000 to generate a tar puddle." TUTO__OIL_GENERATOR
TT 3207 "The ^761tar^000 can be ignited by throwing an Ignifer at it.~The light keeps the rats away but the flames burn everything they touch." TUTO__OIL_IGNIFER
TT 3208 "You can combine ^761tar with a pot^000. ~Throw the pot to create a puddle of tar on the struck surface." TUTO__OIL_JAR
TT 3209 "Slow an enemy down with a ^761tar puddle^000, then ^761ignite^000 it to eliminate him. Combine tar with a ^761pot^000 or break ^761tar jars^000 in the environment to trap enemies." TUTO__OIL_KILL
TT 3210 "Your companion is under attack! If you don't ^761help^000, he will die." TUTO__ORPHAN_DYING
TT 3211 "Use {STR_UPDOWN} to ^761push/pull^000 the cart and {STR_CUSTOM1} to orient it. Press {STR_DROP} to drop it." TUTO__PUSH
TT 3212 "The ^761Pyrite^000 generates light on impact and allows to escape rats for a short period of time." TUTO__PYRITE_USE
TT 3213 "Aim at a target then press {STR_SHOOT} to ^761send the rats^000." TUTO__RAT_STRIKE
TT 3214 "Press {STR_RATSENSE_AIM} to ^761stop^000 the horde control." TUTO__RATMOVE_CANCEL
TT 3215 "You can ^761move the horde^000 with {STR_CUSTOM2} and orient it with {STR_CUSTOM1}." TUTO__RATMOVE_CONTROLS
TT 3216 "Hugo can now ^761control^000 a horde of rats. Hold {STR_RATSENSE_AIM} to create a connection with the rats." TUTO__RATMOVE_START
TT 3217 "Aim at a ^761rat horde^000 and press {STR_SHOOT} to take control of the horde." TUTO__RATMOVE_TAKECONTROL
TT 3218 "Stay close to a light source to protect yourself from rats.~You can interact with a ^761torch^000 to pick it up and move around with it." TUTO__RATS_REPULSE
TT 3219 "Hold {STR_RATSENSE_AIM} to create a ^761connection^000 between Hugo and the rats." TUTO__RATSENSE
TT 3220 "Select the ^761sling^000 using {STR_CUSTOM1} and then use {STR_CYCLE_AMMO_DOWN} to select the ^761rock^000." TUTO__ROCK_SELECT
TT 3221 "Press {STR_INTERACT} near an ^761anchor point^000 to interact with the rope.~You can pull the rope to move or bring down objects attached to it." TUTO__ROPE_BASICS
TT 3222 "From an ^761anchor point^000, you can use the crossbow to create a link to an object." TUTO__ROPE_BOLT_SHOOT
TT 3223 "Hold {STR_INTERACT} to ^761pull the rope^000 towards you." TUTO__ROPE_CONTROLS
TT 3224 "Hold {STR_AIM_MODE} to ^761aim^000 with your sling." TUTO__SHOOT
TT 3225 "The way you handle situations will influence the evolution of ^761Amicia's skills^000.~Press {STR_SELECT_MODE} to open the Skills menu." TUTO__SKILLS
TT 3226 "Amicia will automatically increase the mastery of her ^7613 types of skills^000 depending on your approach style and the tools you use. Press {STR_SELECT_MODE} to close the menu." TUTO__SKILLS_OPEN
