TT 3229 "Hold {STR_SPRINT} to ^761sprint^000." TUTO__SPRINT
TT 3230 "Press {STR_CROUCH} to ^761get up^000." TUTO__STAND
TT 3231 "Stay ^761crouched^000 by pressing {STR_CROUCH} to stay silent and hide in the tall grass to stay invisible." TUTO__STEALTH
