TT 3233 "Stay ^761crouched^000 to remain silent and hide in the tall grass to stay invisible." TUTO__STEALTH_GARDEN
TT 3234 "Shoot the saltpeter bags or throw an Exstinguis on the guards to ^761stun them and lower their guard^000." TUTO__STUN_SHIELD
TT 3235 "The Ignifer allows you to ^761light embers^000.~Hold {STR_THROW_AIM_MODE} to aim at embers and then use {STR_SHOOT} to throw it." TUTO__THROW_AIM_SHOOT
TT 3236 "You can ^761throw^000 the object you are carrying.~Hold {STR_THROW_AIM_MODE} to aim and then press {STR_SHOOT} to throw it." TUTO__THROW_CARRIABLE
