TT 3247 "The daughter..." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__020__M__1
TT 3248 "That explains why those brutes downstairs are so quiet... The Order was quite impressed by the way you put down the Inquisition in Guyenne." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__040__M__1
TT 3249 "Not a choice, a calling. That of a Carrier's Protector." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__060__M__1
TT 3250 "A protector. Your function, among the Order." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__073__M__1
TT 3251 "And you are?" VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__080__M__1
TT 3252 "An apprentice. Does your Magistra know you entitle yourself?" VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__100__M__1
TT 3253 "Control your flame, Protector..." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__120__M__1
TT 3254 "Others have burned in it." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__140__M__1
TT 3255 "Take my bag. Let's go see that Carrier." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__160__M__1
TT 3256 "Where is he?" VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__180__M__1
TT 3257 "We should start immediately. I will need silence." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH02__RTC__100_AN_ALCHEMIST__230__M__1
TT 3258 "Yes. We've lost enough time already." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH03__RTC__122_GUILT__060__M__1
TT 3259 "He's fine. He's in good hands." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH03__RTC__122_GUILT__090__M__1
TT 3260 "The best, you can be sure." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH03__RTC__122_GUILT__100__M__1
TT 3261 "hah..." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH03__RTC__122_GUILT_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 3262 "A Carrier reaching the last threshold is a very rare event. A critical one. Of course, from now on we need to isolate him. The Order has special buildings..." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__124_CONDEMNED__070__M__1
TT 3263 "Do you know what your brother is capable of? He will do much worse." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__124_CONDEMNED__090__M__1
TT 3264 "This is why we need to take him away. His power will grow stronger as his days draw shorter." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__124_CONDEMNED__110__M__1
TT 3265 "The last threshold means the death of the Carrier." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__124_CONDEMNED__150__M__1
TT 3266 "Your friend bought you time when your brother reached the first threshold, but this is something else. There is no stopping it. No elixir. No potion." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__124_CONDEMNED__170__M__1
TT 3267 "It is a child's fantasy!" VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__124_CONDEMNED__190__M__1
TT 3268 "Poor girl... You're running away from reality!  You must accept your brother's fate and your own... And the fate of a Protector is to do as the Order commands." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__124_CONDEMNED__220__M__1
TT 3269 "We are going to the Order's quarters in Marseille as soon as possible. I've got a boat and a man, Joseph, waiting at the harbor, he needs to be warned. As for me, I'm going to rest. Let me know when you are ready to go." VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__124_CONDEMNED__280__M__1
TT 3270 "He's your son! Do something!" VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__150_JUST_A_NIGHTMARE__030__M__1
TT 3271 "Ah! The Protector, finally!" VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__150_JUST_A_NIGHTMARE__040__M__1
TT 3272 "haaaaaaa!" VO__ALCHEMIST__CH04__RTC__150_JUST_A_NIGHTMARE_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 3273 "Let's try through here..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__2ND_BEEKEEPER__020__M__1
TT 3274 "Stop! Wait..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__2ND_BEEKEEPER__030__M__1
TT 3275 "Now..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__2ND_BEEKEEPER__040__M__1
TT 3276 "We're going to have to climb up. Quietly." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__2ND_DISTRACT__010__M__1
TT 3277 "Maybe... he's still away..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_2ND_DISTRACT__040__M__1
TT 3278 "We get back to the cart, we get away from this place." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_DISTRACT__010__M__1
TT 3279 "We just won't tell her. We'll leave as soon as we get to the cart anyway." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_DISTRACT__030__M__1
TT 3280 "I don't know. We need a way out." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_DOOR__010__M__1
TT 3281 "Careful... You can do it." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_DROP__010__M__1
TT 3282 "Keep going..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_DROP__050__M__1
TT 3283 "No..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_FALL__010__M__1
TT 3284 "My sling...  Still in the cart... Move on... Stay low..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_FALL__017__M__1
TT 3285 "The cart... They need you... Hugo needs you..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_FALL__020__M__1
TT 3286 "Yes... Go away..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_FALL__070__M__1
TT 3287 "Yes... We have to be more careful." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_STUNG__020__M__1
TT 3288 "He was, yes." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__AFTER_THE_WAR__014__M__1
TT 3289 "I like your new home!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ARRIVAL_RUINS__030__M__1
TT 3290 "All right..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ARRIVAL_RUINS__050__M__1
TT 3291 "Mother... Come on... Come on..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__BEATRICE_SCREAM__020__M__1
TT 3292 "No!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__BEATRICE_SCREAM__030__M__1
TT 3293 "Mother! I'm coming!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__BEATRICE_VOICE__020__M__1
TT 3294 "We can't pass... They're in the way..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__BROTHER_BACK__050__M__1
TT 3295 "Get down! Quick!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__BROTHERS_ARRIVAL__030__M__1
TT 3296 "Shhh!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__BROTHERS_ARRIVAL__140__M__1
TT 3297 "No..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__BROTHERS_ARRIVAL__150__M__1
TT 3298 "Now! CHARGE!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CHARGE__010__M__1
TT 3299 "Let me see!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CHARGE_FAIL__020__M__1
TT 3300 "We need an exit!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CHASED__020__M__1
TT 3301 "Hmmm, we'll have to climb this. You pull me up this time." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CLIMB_TUTO__010__M__1
TT 3302 "Just kidding. I'll help you." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CLIMB_TUTO__035__M__1
TT 3303 "How dare you?!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CLIMB_TUTO__043__M__1
TT 3304 "So?" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CLOSE_TO_RIVER__010__M__1
TT 3305 "That branch is your frontier?" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CLOSE_TO_RIVER__030__M__1
TT 3306 "Why not..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CLOSE_TO_RIVER__050__M__1
TT 3307 "Oh no! What do we do?!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CLOSE_TO_RIVER__070__M__1
TT 3308 "Got it! My mighty sling is yours!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CLOSE_TO_RIVER__090__M__1
TT 3309 "No! No!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CLOSED_DOOR_HURRY__010__M__1
TT 3310 "Come!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CLOSED_DOOR_HURRY__020__M__1
TT 3311 "Keep an eye out for an exit!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__COURTYARD_RUIN__010__M__1
TT 3312 "We must get out of here!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CROUCH_PROGRESS__010__M__1
TT 3313 "They're crazy..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__CROUCH_PROGRESS__030__M__1
TT 3314 "I know... But we'll settle down soon, and you'll make friends!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__DEBRIEF_TONIN__020__M__1
TT 3315 "As soon as we know how you're doing." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__DEBRIEF_TONIN__040__M__1
TT 3316 "Not this time. This time is different. I know it!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__DEBRIEF_TONIN__060__M__1
TT 3317 "Very pretty..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__DISCOVER_RIVER__020__M__1
TT 3318 "It's locked up tight!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__DOOR_OPENING__010__M__1
TT 3319 "Yes! Well done!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__DOOR_OPENS__020__M__1
TT 3320 "Get that sling, quick, quick!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__DROP_ARROW__030__M__1
TT 3321 "Come on! Yes..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__DROP_ARROW__035__M__1
TT 3322 "Let's go!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__EMERGENCY_TUTO_OK__030__M__1
TT 3323 "Now this is what you get!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENCOUNTER_2_KILL__020__M__1
TT 3324 "Come on... Move!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENCOUNTER_2_KILL__030__M__1
TT 3325 "Hurry... They must be down that hill..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENCOUNTER_2_KILL__040__M__1
TT 3326 "Shouldn't have happened..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENCOUNTER_2_KILL__043__M__1
TT 3327 "Stupid... Stupid!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENCOUNTER_2_KILL__046__M__1
TT 3328 "It's... safe now... Move!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENCOUNTER_2_KILL__050__M__1
TT 3329 "This way..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_BEFORE_DROP__010__M__1
TT 3330 "Where are the people?" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_BEFORE_DROP__030__M__1
TT 3331 "Wow!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_COLLAPSE__010__M__1
TT 3332 "People live here." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_EXPLORE_ROOM__020__M__1
TT 3333 "Let's... just be careful, for now." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_EXPLORE_ROOM__040__M__1
TT 3334 "Ha... ha... Are you hurt?!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_FALLEN__010__M__1
TT 3335 "I... agree. That's enough for today." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_FALLEN__030__M__1
TT 3336 "I'm with you, don't worry." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_FLOOR__010__M__1
TT 3337 "Oh, I think the sorcerer's men are close..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_FLOOR__030__M__1
TT 3338 "What?!..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_OUTSIDE__010__M__1
TT 3339 "It's recent..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_OUTSIDE__030__M__1
TT 3340 "These baskets... they're beehives..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_OUTSIDE__050__M__1
TT 3341 "I don't know! Let's be discreet, and get out..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_OUTSIDE__070__M__1
TT 3342 "Oh, I feel evil around us..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_STAIRS__005__M__1
TT 3343 "Come on, my king! They don't expect us to sneak in..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_CASTLE_STAIRS__020__M__1
TT 3344 "What do you say? Do we attack it?" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__ENTER_THE_CASTLE__020__M__1
TT 3345 "That gate over there... let's try it..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__EXIT_DOOR__010__M__1
TT 3346 "Careful..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__EXIT_HOUSE__010__M__1
TT 3347 "Hold on..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__FINAL_SQUEEZE_THROUGH__010__M__1
TT 3348 "He'll kill her! Move!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__FINAL_SQUEEZE_THROUGH__050__M__1
TT 3349 "Ha... What...?" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__FIRE_HOUSE__025__M__1
TT 3350 "Don't stop..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__FIRE_HOUSE__030__M__1
TT 3351 "What the hell?!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__FIRE_SPREAD__010__M__1
TT 3352 "No, no, no!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__FIRE_SPREAD__011__M__1
TT 3353 "Run!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__FIRE_SPREAD__012__M__1
TT 3354 "The house!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__FIRE_SPREAD__020__M__1
TT 3355 "It's been a long road. You have the right to stretch your legs!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__FIRST_STEPS__020__M__1
TT 3356 "Look at that..." VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__FIRST_STEPS__050__M__1
TT 3357 "He'll manage! We must leave, Hugo! They'll kill us if they catch us!" VO__AMICIA__CH01__CHATTER__HELP_TONIN__020__M__1
