TT 5420 "onom" VO__AMICIA__CH07__RTC__310_SET_SAIL_ONOM__008__M__1
TT 5421 "Hugo... is it really your bird? Take a good look at it!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ABOUT_SCULPTURE__020__M__1
TT 5422 "Good. Very good. Let's go back to them." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ABOUT_SCULPTURE__040__M__1
TT 5423 "And no word about that to anybody here, all right? It's our secret!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ABOUT_SCULPTURE__045__M__1
TT 5424 "Such a nice bed. Our captain has good taste." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_CABIN_BED__010__M__1
TT 5425 "That smell... incense... that's amazing... Hmmm..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_CABIN_INCENSE__010__M__1
TT 5426 "Necklaces, rings... Quite the elegant, lady..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_CABIN_JEWELS__010__M__1
TT 5427 "The Mediterranean sea... La Cuna should be somewhere here... This one.. Or this one?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_CABIN_MAP__010__M__1
TT 5428 "Herbs and unguents... the one she gave to Hugo worked well... I hope he's feeling better." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_CABIN_POTS__010__M__1
TT 5429 "Animals... Maybe from... Africa?... Looks like Hugo played with them. Hope he didn't break anything..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_DECK_STATUETTES__010__M__1
TT 5430 "We can't see the continent anymore... Mother, Lucas, I hope you're safe..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_DECK_VIEW__010__M__1
TT 5431 "Books... Pretty rare..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_HOLD_BOOKS__010__M__1
TT 5432 "She must have travelled a lot to get all these... And now she'll probably sell them illegally..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_HOLD_CARPETS__010__M__1
TT 5433 "Oh yes, that's Arnaud's... Can't believe I heard him snore through the storm..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_HOLD_MATTRESS__010__M__1
TT 5434 "So... it survived the fire." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_INTERACT_SHIELD__010__M__1
