TT 5436 "You?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_INTERACT_SHIELD__050__M__1
TT 5437 "Oh... I see... It's a... sad memory to keep then..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_INTERACT_SHIELD__070__M__1
TT 5438 "I think I know what you mean..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_INTERACT_SHIELD__090__M__1
TT 5439 "He already is." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_INTERACT_SHIELD_AFTER__020__M__1
TT 5440 "They're here! The Count's alive!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ARNAUD_SIGHT__010__M__1
TT 5441 "Guyenne. We fled the war and the plague. We came here, hoping for... a better life. And we heard of this island." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_END__020__M__1
TT 5442 "I know! Can't wait to see our room!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_END__050__M__1
TT 5443 "A fruit, Hugo." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_OFFER__030__M__1
TT 5444 "Sure, your Grace. Please go easy Hugo." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_OFFER__060__M__1
TT 5445 "What?! No!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__BROKE_POTS_NOISE__030__M__1
TT 5446 "No, no!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__BROKE_POTS_NOISE__040__M__1
TT 5447 "Hurry!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__BROKE_POTS_NOISE__050__M__1
TT 5448 "Get down!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__BROKE_POTS_NOISE__060__M__1
TT 5449 "Yes!... What do we do?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__CALL_SAIL__020__M__1
TT 5450 "Understood!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__CALL_SAIL__040__M__1
TT 5451 "Ah, it's too high. Let's find something to climb up!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__CLIMB_SPOT__020__M__1
TT 5452 "Mind spending some time with your old sister?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__COMPASS_INTERACT__010__M__1
TT 5453 "Tools, probably... There might be some around. Or we can ask her." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__COMPASS_INTERACT__030__M__1
TT 5454 "Wow... She certainly has some real treasure down there." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__DISCOVER_HOLD_ALONE__010__M__1
TT 5455 "Let's go, now! To cover!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__DISTRACT_01__010__M__1
