TT 5466 "That's great..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__DOWN_STAIRS_BEFORE__030__M__1
TT 5467 "It was so good to sleep..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ENTER_CABIN__010__M__1
TT 5468 "It's very beautiful, yes. But now we need to find whatever called you here..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ENTRANCE__040__M__1
TT 5469 "Yes!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ENTRANCE__070__M__1
TT 5470 "All right, so it's, erm... a bit strange, but... Well, go on, Hugo..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ENTRANCE_ARNAUD__020__M__1
TT 5471 "We can ask at the market! Come on!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__ENTRANCE_ARNAUD__050__M__1
