TT 5473 "EMPTY" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__FABRICS_STAND__030__M__1
TT 5474 "Well, thank you, sir." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__FABRICS_STAND__060__M__1
TT 5475 "Let's see the rest." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__FABRICS_STAND__100__M__1
