TT 5511 "We still have plenty to discover." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__GOAT_DENIED__030__M__1
TT 5512 "Excuse me..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__GUEST__014__M__1
TT 5513 "Sure." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__GUEST__020__M__1
TT 5514 "Every child bears the future of the world. One child can change everything." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__GUEST__035__M__1
