TT 5611 "The sea's so quiet... Nothing but the horizon... Enjoy..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__START__010__M__1
TT 5612 "Wait..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__STATUE_REVEAL__020__M__1
TT 5613 "Should we be worried about the Count's army here? They look pretty quiet." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__STREET_COUNT_ARMY__010__M__1
TT 5614 "Good." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__STREET_COUNT_ARMY__030__M__1
TT 5615 "Here, some feathers! This one's dark..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_FEATHER_FALCON__010__M__1
TT 5616 "That'll suit you. Here." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_FEATHER_FALCON__030__M__1
TT 5617 "What a predator you make..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_FEATHER_FALCON__060__M__1
TT 5618 "Good afternoon!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_INTERACT__005__M__1
TT 5619 "We've just arrived and... we heard about a... beach? With a pond not too far?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_INTERACT__020__M__1
TT 5620 "Thank you anyway!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_INTERACT__060__M__1
TT 5621 "We'll ask again." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_LEAVE_INTERACT__030__M__1
TT 5622 "All right. Let's try and ask someone here..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_SHADE__010__M__1
TT 5623 "Be very careful..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__THROUGH_HOLE__010__M__1
TT 5624 "Hugo?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__THROUGH_HOLE__050__M__1
TT 5625 "Let's have a look..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__UP_GAME_FAR__020__M__1
TT 5626 "Good day! Can we play?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__UP_GAME_START__003__M__1
TT 5627 "Fine, let's see how I do!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__UP_GAME_START__010__M__1
TT 5628 "Yes, let's go back... This place is amazing..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__WRONGWAY_BASIN__020__M__1
TT 5629 "Yes, we're coming, sorry!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__CHATTER__WRONGWAY_BASIN__040__M__1
TT 5630 "Ha!..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__ONOM__BROKE_POTS_NOISE__010__M__1
TT 5631 "Oh!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__ONOM__MARKET_GOAT_MEMORY__075__M__1
TT 5632 "Ha!..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__ONOM__THIRD_SHOT_FAIL__010__M__1
TT 5633 "It must be great to pilot this thing." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__010__M__1
TT 5634 "EMPTY" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__040__M__1
TT 5635 "It's... amazing..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__070__M__1
TT 5636 "Thank you... for taking us." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__090__M__1
TT 5637 "Oh..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__110__M__1
TT 5638 "Oh, duty calls, I'm sorry..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__140__M__1
TT 5639 "Thank you." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__151__M__1
TT 5640 "EMPTY" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 5641 "Whatever's there, we'll find it together." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__350_EARTH__040__M__1
TT 5642 "Island explorers!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__350_EARTH__050__M__1
TT 5643 "What? What are you talking about?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__350_EARTH__070__M__1
TT 5644 "God... No. Hugo, I'm so sorry. It won't happen." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__350_EARTH__090__M__1
TT 5645 "Yes, sure..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__350_EARTH__140__M__1
TT 5646 "I'm happy to be here with you." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__350_EARTH__150__M__1
TT 5647 "Fine. We'll take a tour while it's still light. And find a place to sleep." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__070__M__1
TT 5648 "I see." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__090__M__1
TT 5649 "Good bye!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__170__M__1
TT 5650 "Well, that's a pretty good start, no?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__180__M__1
TT 5651 "Pray that we're successful." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__200__M__1
TT 5652 "Well, come on, your Majesty!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__210__M__1
TT 5653 "The rats..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__090__M__1
TT 5654 "Hey! What are you doing?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__110__M__1
TT 5655 "Wait! What? THAT was your deal?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__140__M__1
TT 5656 "You saved me so he would murder the Count for you?" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__150__M__1
TT 5657 "NO! You don't take advantage of a child and call it a deal, Arnaud! We came all this way for HIM! You WON'T ruin that!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__170__M__1
TT 5658 "No! Arnaud!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__190__M__1
TT 5659 "No... NO!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__260__M__1
TT 5660 "This is not our fight! Run!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__270__M__1
TT 5661 "Should've seen it coming!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__375_STOPPING_ARNAUD__010__M__1
TT 5662 "This is why you can't trust people, Hugo..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__375_STOPPING_ARNAUD__020__M__1
TT 5663 "We're going back." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__375_STOPPING_ARNAUD__060__M__1
TT 5664 "No. Things aren't always nice, but you can change them." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__375_STOPPING_ARNAUD__080__M__1
TT 5665 "The way we always do. We fight. We stop Arnaud before he does more damage." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__375_STOPPING_ARNAUD__100__M__1
TT 5666 "We save your dream." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__375_STOPPING_ARNAUD__110__M__1
TT 5667 "onom" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__375_STOPPING_ARNAUD_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 5668 "You did this to yourself!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__030__M__1
TT 5669 "No! Wait..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__050__M__1
TT 5670 "We shared a boat, and we had time to chat on the way but I didn't know he was after you, Sire." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__140__M__1
TT 5671 "Amicia. And this is Hugo, my brother. He's a bit afraid." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__160__M__1
TT 5672 "Are you sure? I mean..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__180__M__1
TT 5673 "Hugo, come!" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__381_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__010__M__1
TT 5674 "This is too much..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__020__M__1
TT 5675 "Shhh..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__050__M__1
TT 5676 "Hugo!..." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__080__M__1
TT 5677 "Thank you." VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__120__M__1
TT 5678 "onom" VO__AMICIA__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS_ONOM__050__M__1
TT 5679 "They look so eager to have this child. It's sad they're so wrong..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__1ST_STEPS__020__M__1
TT 5680 "Hugo... these things you dreamt of, they existed!... You just couldn't know what they really meant..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__1ST_STEPS__050__M__1
TT 5681 "Your dream showed us another truth! But it is a truth! We can still use it to change everything!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__1ST_STEPS__090__M__1
TT 5682 "No... Not even you." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_KITES__060__M__1
TT 5683 "Yes... Some kind of... temple?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_SANCTUARY__020__M__1
