TT 5685 "It seems so nice..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_SANCTUARY__050__M__1
TT 5686 "Sophia?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_SOPHIA__015__M__1
TT 5687 "Where are you?!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_SOPHIA__020__M__1
TT 5688 "Come on, Hugo." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_SOPHIA__050__M__1
