TT 5690 "Yes. I'm even more curious now." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__AFTER_CLIMB__030__M__1
TT 5691 "Oh I can't wait to see it!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__AFTER_MAP__020__M__1
