TT 5764 "I'll go with you." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_PET__040__M__1
TT 5765 "See? It's easy. They don't all scream." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_PET__090__M__1
