TT 5822 "You're right!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_TWO__020__M__1
TT 5823 "Only one way to find out..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_TWO__040__M__1
