TT 5825 "Hello! There's a sculpture of a bird there... do you know... anything about it?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_CHICKENS_INT__010__M__1
TT 5826 "Well, thank you!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_CHICKENS_INT__040__M__1
