TT 5849 "We can do this... they're probably distracted by the ceremony up there." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_NO_FEAR__010__M__1
TT 5850 "Well, we'll... see once we're there." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_NO_FEAR__040__M__1
TT 5851 "That's a lot of security for a ceremony." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_SECURITY__005__M__1
TT 5852 "He's a waste of time. And of trust." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_SECURITY__020__M__1
TT 5853 "You're taking huge risks for people you barely know, Sophia.  You know you don't have to." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_SOPHIA__010__M__1
TT 5854 "Good. Let's just... stay safe." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_SOPHIA__030__M__1
