TT 5857 "It's probably a brake... To stop the windmill." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__INSIDE_1ST_WINDMILL__020__M__1
TT 5858 "Maybe... it will start the windmill." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__INSIDE_1ST_WINDMILL_ALT__010__M__1
