TT 5880 "I don't know why, but I feel... stronger?..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_VAMBRACE__066__M__1
TT 5881 "All right, let's go back before... some smuggler ghost comes shouting at us." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_VAMBRACE__070__M__1
