TT 5955 "No door... Some sort of... observation hallway?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__TO_LIBRARY__020__M__1
TT 5956 "All right, I trust you, I guess..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__TO_SANCTUARY_2__020__M__1
TT 5957 "Hugo's sickness is... special. Our mother's an alchemist, but she couldn't do anything about it. It's almost like... a curse." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__TO_SANCTUARY_2__034__M__1
