TT 6011 "Strange..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__WINDMILL_WIN__040__M__1
TT 6012 "Look..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__WOODEN_HORSE__010__M__1
TT 6013 "It's your size. Pretty sure he was your age." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__WOODEN_HORSE__030__M__1
TT 6014 "Look at that..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__WOODEN_TOYS_INTERACT__010__M__1
TT 6015 "They're people... Important ones maybe?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__WOODEN_TOYS_INTERACT__030__M__1
TT 6016 "Come, we've barely started." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__WOODEN_TOYS_INTERACT__080__M__1
TT 6017 "Yes, right..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__CHATTER__WRONGWAY_EXPLORER__020__M__1
TT 6018 "Ha!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__ONOM__PHOENIX__040__M__1
TT 6019 "Ha!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__ONOM__PHOENIX_WAIT__010__M__1
TT 6020 "These clothes feel so nice..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__400_FRESH_START__010__M__1
TT 6021 "Hey... Come here, sleepy head." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__400_FRESH_START__030__M__1
TT 6022 "Come on, it's just the sun! Look. It's worth it." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__400_FRESH_START__050__M__1
TT 6023 "Like a dream?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__400_FRESH_START__070__M__1
TT 6024 "Quickly, let's eat something and get going!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__400_FRESH_START__090__M__1
TT 6025 "Come on." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__400_FRESH_START__091__M__1
TT 6026 "It's so warm already..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__400_FRESH_START__110__M__1
TT 6027 "Hey, we're here to know why you dreamt about this place, right?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__400_FRESH_START__130__M__1
TT 6028 "Hello, can we go outside?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__003__M__1
TT 6029 "How did you know...?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__026__M__1
TT 6030 "Yes, that bastard... He betrayed us..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__032__M__1
TT 6031 "And worse, he used Hugo!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__034__M__1
TT 6032 "I'm not joking, Sophia. Arnaud may be your friend, but he almost got us killed!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__040__M__1
TT 6033 "No! I don't care about them! I kneel to no lord, Sophia. No count, no king—no one!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__050__M__1
TT 6034 "I only care about him!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__055__M__1
TT 6035 "It's antique..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__040__M__1
TT 6036 "What drawing?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__080__M__1
TT 6037 "Yes! I see it!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__100__M__1
TT 6038 "A very ancient order of alchemists." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__120__M__1
TT 6039 "You overheard us on the boat, Sophia... Hugo is sick. It's not contagious. Still, the order wanted to lock him away to do whatever they pleased, but I..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__130__M__1
TT 6040 "Whatever can help him." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__170__M__1
TT 6041 "It makes sense." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__210__M__1
TT 6042 "Let's go visit those Mothers then?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__215__M__1
TT 6043 "Come on then." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__240__M__1
TT 6044 "It's going to be quite a walk!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__410_TO_THE_MOUNTAIN__010__M__1
TT 6045 "Hey! Easy! I don't want to carry you!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__410_TO_THE_MOUNTAIN__050__M__1
TT 6046 "Are you tired? We've been walking a while..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH__010__M__1
TT 6047 "Looks like someone's more tired than you." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH__040__M__1
TT 6048 "You know, it's his first time climbing one!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH__070__M__1
TT 6049 "This is unbelievable..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__060__M__1
TT 6050 "A child's throne... He... he lived here..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__080__M__1
TT 6051 "There's no Child of Embers... I told you about the Order... This place belonged to them. And this child on the frescos, it's the Carrier of the Prima Macula." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__100__M__1
TT 6052 "Alchemists call it “the First Corruption”. It awoke in Hugo's blood when he was a baby. It keeps growing inside him..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__120__M__1
TT 6053 "That's what this whole place is about: the advent of a Carrier of the Macula. The Order gathering around him, studying him, trying to find a solution. And the rats..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__140__M__1
TT 6054 "Not only... The rats are..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__160__M__1
TT 6055 "Anyway, they got it all wrong! There is no “Child of Embers” that will come to save the world! That's a fantasy they crafted to fit their hopes!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__170__M__1
TT 6056 "Part of it is true. The part that can save him. The only one that matters" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__190__M__1
TT 6057 "“Basilius and Aelia”." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__200__M__1
TT 6058 "The water..." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__230__M__1
TT 6059 "Oh, from the healing pond in your dream!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__240__M__1
TT 6060 "It's like a symbol, like mother's alchemic drawings." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__250__M__1
TT 6061 "Hey! Come see!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__270__M__1
TT 6062 "That's his throne... And this, I think, is his name." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__280__M__1
TT 6063 "He was a carrier, just like you! You're not the only one... That's why you dreamt of all this! Something called you here and for a good reason. I mean, look at this place! If there's a cure, it HAS to be here!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__300__M__1
TT 6064 "Let's keep looking!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__330__M__1
TT 6065 "onom" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 6066 "What is it?" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__010__M__1
TT 6067 "541... What does it say?!" VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__030__M__1
TT 6068 "It really did all happen! They where just like us." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__050__M__1
TT 6069 "Well we have something to go on... A fort... A round tower." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__070__M__1
TT 6070 "Yes. Let's get out of here, fast." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__130__M__1
TT 6071 "Risky, but the water will help." VO__AMICIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__170__M__1
