TT 6098 "But... If you need to leave, do it now, Sophia." VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_IS_BACK__060__M__1
TT 6099 "Thanks... It's a bit hard for him." VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_SOPHIA__010__M__1
