TT 6106 "Nice way to put it..." VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__BABY_BOAT__050__M__1
TT 6107 "Thank you, Sophia..." VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__BABY_BOAT__080__M__1
