TT 6158 "He won't hold... I need to end this quickly..." VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_SEVENTH_WAVE__030__M__1
TT 6159 "No! Close your eyes and cover your ears, you hear me?!" VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_SEVENTH_WAVE__050__M__1
