TT 6835 "I don't know, I..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__150__M__1
TT 6836 "Yes. We can't run away from this I guess..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__170__M__1
