TT 8137 "Good suggestion." VO__AMICIA__GENERIC__RESPONSE__HELPER_ANSWER_DISCREET__001__M__3
TT 8138 "Great idea, thanks." VO__AMICIA__GENERIC__RESPONSE__HELPER_ANSWER_DISCREET__001__M__4
TT 8139 "Great! It helps." VO__AMICIA__GENERIC__RESPONSE__HELPER_ANSWER_STRESSED__001__M__1
TT 8140 "Good idea." VO__AMICIA__GENERIC__RESPONSE__HELPER_ANSWER_STRESSED__001__M__2
TT 8141 "Good thinking." VO__AMICIA__GENERIC__RESPONSE__HELPER_ANSWER_STRESSED__001__M__3
TT 8142 "Timely advice!" VO__AMICIA__GENERIC__RESPONSE__HELPER_ANSWER_STRESSED__001__M__4
TT 8143 "Looks like something's over there." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__BIRD_NOISE__010__M__1
TT 8144 "You're so loud... Where did you go?" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__BIRD_NOISE__020__M__1
TT 8145 "You're good at killing, I'll give you that! But what now?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__CHASE_CORNER__010__M__1
TT 8146 "Enjoying the view?" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__CHASE_DOWN_BOAT__011__M__1
TT 8147 "If you kill, be ready to be killed. It's only fair, no?" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__CHASE_FALL__030__M__1
TT 8148 "Why are you running?! I came for you, just like you asked!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__CHASE_FENCE__010__M__1
TT 8149 "What's the matter? I thought you wanted to die!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__CHASE_SLOPE__009__M__1
TT 8150 "That's it... Bury yourself. It's just like you. I'll catch you anyway!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__CHASE_SLOPE__011__M__1
TT 8151 "I'm here! Now show me how you fight a fully armoured warrior!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__CHASE_START__010__M__1
TT 8152 "Look at you... So unprepared..." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__CHASE_TREES__010__M__1
TT 8153 "The girl's in here somewhere. See if you can find her." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__EXIT_CAVE__010__M__1
TT 8154 "To take care of her family. That'll bring her out." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__EXIT_CAVE__030__M__1
TT 8155 "Found her?" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__SEARCHING__030__M__1
TT 8156 "How are you enjoying your tomb, lady? Wasn't such a great idea..." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__SEARCHING__050__M__1
TT 8157 "Are you over here?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__SEARCHING__080__M__1
TT 8158 "You think I won't find you?" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__SEARCHING__100__M__1
TT 8159 "She's here! Gather more men!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__CHATTER__SEARCHING_MORE__010__M__1
TT 8160 "Mmmh." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__ONOM__SEARCHING__090__M__1
TT 8161 "So here's the famous “girl with the sling”!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__200_EMBUSH__030__M__1
TT 8162 "But it seems you're pretty versatile when it comes to killing my men!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__200_EMBUSH__040__M__1
TT 8163 "Yeah. Try that." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__200_EMBUSH__055__M__1
TT 8164 "Men! Get them!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__200_EMBUSH__060__M__1
TT 8165 "Oh, so we're done playing?" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__220_THE_ROPE__004__M__1
TT 8166 "Stay where you are or you're next!" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__220_THE_ROPE__030__M__1
TT 8167 "Last lesson: if you want to be reckless..." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__220_THE_ROPE__040__M__1
TT 8168 "...be better than that." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__220_THE_ROPE__050__M__1
TT 8169 "Look at that... Reinforcements..." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__220_THE_ROPE__090__M__1
TT 8170 "onom" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__220_THE_ROPE_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 8171 "Not that easy...." VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__ARNAUD_CHASE__010__M__1
TT 8172 "So what will you do now?" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__ARNAUD_CHASE__023__M__1
TT 8173 "Hm. You have to do better" VO__ARNAUD__CH05__RTC__ARNAUD_CHASE__028__M__1
TT 8174 "He should have trained more." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_ARNAUD_SKILLS__010__M__1
TT 8175 "Why not wield a sword yourself?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_ARNAUD_SKILLS__030__M__1
TT 8176 "Shame." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_ARNAUD_SKILLS__050__M__1
TT 8177 "Says the boy with the rats..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_ARNAUD_SKILLS__070__M__1
TT 8178 "Never makes a man immortal." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_LAST_SOLDIER__030__M__1
TT 8179 "No doubt." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_RATS__010__M__1
TT 8180 "One day he'll be big enough to choose." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_RATS__030__M__1
TT 8181 "To think you sent your critters after me that first time..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_RATS_KILL__050__M__1
TT 8182 "Water under the bridge." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_RATS_KILL__070__M__1
TT 8183 "The best. It's in her blood. 'Guess that's also why she's unable to stay put." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_SOPHIA__020__M__1
TT 8184 "The Count's a man of law and order. A goddamn asshole. But he's disappeared who-knows-where like the coward he is." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_THE_COUNT__020__M__1
TT 8185 "We hate each other." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ABOUT_THE_COUNT__040__M__1
TT 8186 "Let's hope it calms down before we get to that boat." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__AFTER_LEDGE_2__030__M__1
TT 8187 "Who taught you how to shoot?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__AMICIA_KILL__010__M__1
TT 8188 "Good. Discipline..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__AMICIA_KILL__030__M__1
TT 8189 "What?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ANCHOR_CHECK__020__M__1
TT 8190 "Then let's make sure he gets there." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ANCHOR_CHECK__040__M__1
TT 8191 "Sophia! I think they've blocked the anchor!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ANCHOR_ISSUE__020__M__1
TT 8192 "Clean shot." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ANCHOR_OK__010__M__1
TT 8193 "It's an anchor. It's made to anchor." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ANCHOR_PULL__020__M__1
TT 8194 "There's a counterweight with a lock!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ANCHOR_RELEASED__011__M__1
TT 8195 "Need a hand?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ANCHOR_RELEASED__020__M__1
TT 8196 "That chain is blocking the anchor!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ANCHOR_SPOTTED__010__M__1
TT 8197 "It's what I do." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ARNAUD_2ND_KILL__020__M__1
TT 8198 "So what? I'll take care of him... Say the word— Command and I'll execute." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ARNAUD_KILL__030__M__1
TT 8199 "We're almost there. Your brother will soon see La Cuna." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ARNAUD_LEVER__010__M__1
TT 8200 "Break that thing!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ARNAUD_LEVER__030__M__1
TT 8201 "Stay here!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ARNAUD_MOVES__040__M__1
TT 8202 "It changes with the wind... but she owes me either way." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ARNAUD_SOPHIA__020__M__1
TT 8203 "For not killing her when I was ordered to." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ARNAUD_SOPHIA__040__M__1
TT 8204 "That you can't. And you shouldn't." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ARNAUD_X_KILL__020__M__1
TT 8205 "It's pretty broken, but that's what it's for—it suffers so I don't." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__BEACH_2_START__020__M__1
TT 8206 "Me too." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__BEACH_2_START__040__M__1
TT 8207 "Here we are." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__BOAT__009__M__1
TT 8208 "Of course not, but it leads to it." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__BOAT__020__M__1
TT 8209 "See that pole? There's a rope on it. Pull the boat from there while I push on my side! You think you can do it?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__BOAT__030__M__1
TT 8210 "When you're ready..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__BOAT__070__M__1
TT 8211 "Good. Keep going!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__BOAT_PULL_READY__020__M__1
TT 8212 "What?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__BOAT_PULL_READY__040__M__1
TT 8213 "Don't want a recipe, I just hope it holds!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__BOLT_FIRE_REACT__030__M__1
TT 8214 "Yes. It's a shortcut." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CAVE_HALLWAY__020__M__1
TT 8215 "Erm, yes... Which means less soldiers. And we have the boy, no?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CAVE_HALLWAY__040__M__1
TT 8216 "It is. We're almost there. Her hideout is on the other side of that boat." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CAVE_WRECK__020__M__1
TT 8217 "Yes... Sophia. “The Sea Scorpion”. She's the leader." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CAVE_WRECK__040__M__1
TT 8218 "Less scary than those damn biters." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CAVE_WRECK__060__M__1
TT 8219 "The hideout is just at the end." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL__011__M__1
TT 8220 "She's right!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL__047__M__1
TT 8221 "We're almost there... Can't you argue later?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL__065__M__1
TT 8222 "Enough! I'll carry you all the way and that's it!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL__090__M__1
TT 8223 "Good! There you go!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL__092__M__1
TT 8224 "Is that high enough for you? Look, you're not even touching the water!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL__100__M__1
TT 8225 "Well, every day can't be easy when you're that small." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL__120__M__1
TT 8226 "Are you still scared?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL_FOWARD__010__M__1
TT 8227 "Now you know why they call me The Wall!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL_FOWARD__030__M__1
TT 8228 "Exactly! Nothing gets past me." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL_FOWARD__050__M__1
TT 8229 "How's it going back there?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL_FOWARD__070__M__1
TT 8230 "Time to meet the Sea Scorpion." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__CHANNEL_OK__040__M__1
TT 8231 "Of course. She's been a thorn in their side for years now." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ENCOUNTER_1ST_PART__040__M__1
TT 8232 "We're making good progress. How's the head?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ENTER_CAVE__020__M__1
TT 8233 "Thank me..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ENTER_CAVE__050__M__1
TT 8234 "Finally!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__EPISANGUIS_BACK__030__M__1
TT 8235 "All right! I'm ready!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__EPISANGUIS_BACK__050__M__1
TT 8236 "On your go!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__EPISANGUIS_BACK__060__M__1
TT 8237 "Really?! Hey shorty, they obey you! Just send them all into the sea!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__FIRST_CROSSING__010__M__1
TT 8238 "Ah, great..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__FIRST_CROSSING__030__M__1
TT 8239 "Hungry bastards... Erm. No offense, shorty..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__FISHES__010__M__1
TT 8240 "Jump! I'll catch you." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__GAP__030__M__1
TT 8241 "Hey! What's that stuff? You used it against my men!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__HUGO_SIGNALS__010__M__1
TT 8242 "She'll do it. She's good." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__HUGO_SUPPORT__030__M__1
TT 8243 "A bunch. Scum she gathered from all around the Mediterranean sea. Sophia's their lighthouse in the dark. They see her as a saint." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__IDLE_CAVE_1__020__M__1
TT 8244 "Oh no..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__IDLE_CAVE_1__040__M__1
TT 8245 "Her boat's called “la Rascasse” — A local fish with poisonous stingers, also known as  a sea scorpion, so..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__IDLE_CAVE_2__010__M__1
TT 8246 "Pretty sure she can sting too..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__IDLE_CAVE_2__030__M__1
TT 8247 "So what are you searching for on La Cuna?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__IDLE_CAVE_3__010__M__1
TT 8248 "I had ears in the city. Heard of a mess inside the garrison. A girl and a boy?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__IDLE_CAVE_3__040__M__1
TT 8249 "Nicely done." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__IDLE_CAVE_3__060__M__1
TT 8250 "Pretty sharp." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__KILL_ARNAUD_REACT_1__010__M__1
TT 8251 "You can do better though." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__KILL_ARNAUD_REACT_1__030__M__1
TT 8252 "Can't wait to show you how I do it." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__KILL_ARNAUD_REACT_3__010__M__1
TT 8253 "No, but it might be a necessity." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__KILL_ARNAUD_REACT_3__030__M__1
TT 8254 "Ouh... that's nasty..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__KILL_RNO_RATS_1__010__M__1
TT 8255 "But it's effective." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__KILL_RNO_RATS_1__030__M__1
TT 8256 "One hell of a weapon you got there..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__KILL_RNO_RATS_2__010__M__1
TT 8257 "So, how do we get this thing into the water?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__LA_RASCASSE__030__M__1
TT 8258 "Leave it to me!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__LA_RASCASSE__090__M__1
TT 8259 "Ah, shit!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__LEDGE_FALL__010__M__1
TT 8260 "They're coming for me! I need light, fast!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__LEDGE_FALL__040__M__1
TT 8261 "Come on! Come on!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__LEDGE_FALL__060__M__1
TT 8262 "Damn... How big is that thing?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__LEDGE_NEST__002__M__1
TT 8263 "This thing doesn't look..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__LEDGE_NEST__020__M__1
TT 8264 "They won't... follow us, right?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__LET_GO_OK__030__M__1
TT 8265 "I've been in a hundred battles... looked death in the eyes about as many times... but these little turds... they make me feel like a fresh recruit..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__MEETING_AGAIN__020__M__1
TT 8266 "You're the patron saint of optimism... So... do you have any tricks left to keep us going?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__MEETING_AGAIN__040__M__1
TT 8267 "No, no, we're getting out of here... Wait... I know." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__MEETING_AGAIN__060__M__1
TT 8268 "Not really. I'd say we make good partners, but not good friends." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__MID_SECTION__020__M__1
TT 8269 "We work well together, but we want to kill each other after a while." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__MID_SECTION__040__M__1
TT 8270 "EMPTY" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__MID_SECTION__060__M__1
TT 8271 "What?! There are millions!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__MORE_RATS__030__M__1
TT 8272 "Great." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__MORE_RATS__050__M__1
TT 8273 "Hey! I need you down there!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEGOCIATION__050__M__1
TT 8274 "I really don't see why..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_CART__020__M__1
TT 8275 "Come on, even the boy is scared! You're sure about this?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_PUSH__030__M__1
TT 8276 "I'm not ready for this..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_PUSH__050__M__1
TT 8277 "The stench... What is that thing? Makes my skin crawl..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_PUSH_ENTER__010__M__1
TT 8278 "Bloody Hell..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_PUSH_ENTER__040__M__1
TT 8279 "You said you lived in Guyenne. It all started there! You..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_PUSH_ENTER__050__M__1
TT 8280 "You started this?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_PUSH_ENTER__070__M__1
TT 8281 "This is the hell we all deserve." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_PUSH_ENTER__090__M__1
TT 8282 "That's crazy..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_PUSH_ENTER__120__M__1
TT 8283 "What? What is that?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_REVEAL__030__M__1
TT 8284 "Don't tell me we're going in there..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_REVEAL__050__M__1
TT 8285 "We shouldn't." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__NEST_REVEAL__070__M__1
TT 8286 "That torch, down there, by the wreck. It's there." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__OBJECTIVE_HIDEOUT__020__M__1
TT 8287 "I hope Sophia's still there..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__OBJECTIVE_HIDEOUT__040__M__1
TT 8288 "Oh, she's pretty... unpredictable..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__OBJECTIVE_HIDEOUT__060__M__1
TT 8289 "Tell me when to release it!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ODORIS_BOLT_OK__020__M__1
TT 8290 "Yes! Whatever!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ODORIS_DONE__030__M__1
TT 8291 "Yes! I don't know what that was, but you saved my skin!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ODORIS_SUCCESS__020__M__1
TT 8292 "No idea! We could try it..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ODORIS_SUCCESS__060__M__1
TT 8293 "Huh... You sure about that bait?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__ODORIS_USELESS__010__M__1
TT 8294 "Looks like something you could use, no? With your crossbow magic?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__PLANK_LIFT__010__M__1
TT 8295 "You bet I will!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__PLANK_RELEASE__020__M__1
TT 8296 "We call them “laughing gulls” here." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__POST_FEATHER__010__M__1
TT 8297 "See? You're turning into one..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__POST_FEATHER__030__M__1
TT 8298 "So you've... already seen all this?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__PUSH_CHEST_ADD__010__M__1
TT 8299 "This is what hell looks like." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__PUSH_CHEST_ADD__030__M__1
TT 8300 "As have I.... but never like this." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__PUSH_CHEST_ADD__050__M__1
TT 8301 "Yes... must be a heat storm..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__RAIN_VISTA__020__M__1
TT 8302 "All right, they're... They're really obeying you. How... How do you do that? Where did you get that from?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__RAT_MOVE__040__M__1
TT 8303 "Bloody rats... Can you do something about them?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__RATS_BELOW__010__M__1
TT 8304 "Y'know, some people would pay a fortune to have you on their side, shorty..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__RATS_FIRST_KILL__010__M__1
TT 8305 "She's right." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__RATS_FIRST_KILL__040__M__1
TT 8306 "Ha, what the hell?! There's something sticky on the ground!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__RNO_CROSSING__010__M__1
TT 8307 "Are you joking?! I'm burning these boots!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__RNO_CROSSING__018__M__1
TT 8308 "Bloody... rotten... crap!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__RNO_CROSSING__030__M__1
TT 8309 "I'm there!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__RNO_CROSSING_OK__010__M__1
TT 8310 "Let's get up there!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SAILS_ORDER__070__M__1
TT 8311 "I'll take port-side." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SAILS_START__010__M__1
TT 8312 "When you're ready!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SAILS_START__030__M__1
TT 8313 "Well, it should!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SAILS_STUCK__020__M__1
TT 8314 "Then let's untie it!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SAILS_STUCK__070__M__1
TT 8315 "Yes! Get on the starboard pontoon! You'll get a better angle!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SAILS_STUCK__076__M__1
TT 8316 "Looks like it... And I say you should sound the charge." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SEAGULLS__020__M__1
TT 8317 "C'mon soldier! CHARGE!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SEAGULLS__050__M__1
TT 8318 "If we had more like him in our ranks, we'd have pushed back the English a long time ago." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SEAGULLS__070__M__1
TT 8319 "I was a knight back then, in Guyenne." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SEAGULLS__090__M__1
TT 8320 "T'was a waste." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SEAGULLS__110__M__1
TT 8321 "Shoot one of your flaming bolts at my shield." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_IDEA__010__M__1
TT 8322 "Does it look like it cares?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_IDEA__040__M__1
TT 8323 "Hey! This fire's roasting my face, so could you hurry?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_QUICK_1__010__M__1
TT 8324 "Amicia! I need you... to come here... NOW!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_QUICK_2__010__M__1
TT 8325 "We're doing this! Mark my words!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_RUN__010__M__1
TT 8326 "Out of the way!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_RUN__020__M__1
TT 8327 "Look at the cowards crawling back to their holes!... That's it! Fall back before the might of the Wall!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_RUN__040__M__1
TT 8328 "Bloody hell, yes!... My arm feels like it's aflame though..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_RUN__070__M__1
TT 8329 "And this Wall has taken enough blows, shorty...  My body is as battered as my shield." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_RUN__074__M__1
TT 8330 "That's war for you..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_RUN__078__M__1
TT 8331 "Oh I'll hold. That's what I do..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_RUN__090__M__1
TT 8332 "All right, enough!..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_RUN_OK__010__M__1
TT 8333 "Wouldn't say that... Just a good sweat. Let's keep going." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_RUN_OK__030__M__1
TT 8334 "I felt that... Good! When you're ready! Quick please!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SHIELD_SHOOT__010__M__1
TT 8335 "Told you... The Count is on a mission to clean Provence." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SMUGGLERS_HUNT__010__M__1
TT 8336 "Yes... This hull has kissed a lot of sand and rocks on its travels." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_1__020__M__1
TT 8337 "Well, rename it..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_1__040__M__1
TT 8338 "Sure! Why not? I think it deserves it." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_1__060__M__1
TT 8339 "Well... nothing's totally dead till it's completely buried." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_1__090__M__1
TT 8340 "Oh... that's old... Very old..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_CAVE__020__M__1
TT 8341 "No... handprints. Of the first people who lived here... even before the Romans." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_CAVE__040__M__1
TT 8342 "We should keep going." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_CAVE__060__M__1
TT 8343 "Yes. A discreet way for discreet people." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__SQUIZZ_THROUGH__020__M__1
TT 8344 "I'm trusting you here..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__STICK_CROSSING_1__020__M__1
TT 8345 "Sorry, pretty hard to relax right now..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__STICK_CROSSING_1__040__M__1
TT 8346 "Well I don't envy you..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__STICK_CROSSING_1__060__M__1
TT 8347 "That's the word I was searching for..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__STICK_CROSSING_OK__020__M__1
TT 8348 "Nobody does, shorty." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__STICK_CROSSING_OK__040__M__1
TT 8349 "That tiny stick?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__STICK_GRAB__020__M__1
TT 8350 "We'll get to your island. La Cuna's a nice, sunny place." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__THE_SEA__030__M__1
TT 8351 "You're not light... Your sister feeds you well..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__TO_THE_BEACH__010__M__1
TT 8352 "He's the one sprinting! Slow down, shorty! We have wounded!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__TO_THE_BEACH__040__M__1
TT 8353 "Goddamn... pieces of shit!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__TORCH_OK__030__M__1
TT 8354 "I'm good! Except I'm stuck and they're looking at me like I'm a piece of roast meat!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__TORCH_OK__050__M__1
TT 8355 "Stay low." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__UNEXPECTED_FOES__050__M__1
TT 8356 "Yes, soldiers. I'll get rid of them." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__UNEXPECTED_FOES__080__M__1
TT 8357 "Still don't trust me, heh? Go on then, I'm watching." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__UNEXPECTED_FOES__100__M__1
TT 8358 "What the hell?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__UNEXPECTED_RATS__010__M__1
TT 8359 "Oh shit! SHIT!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__UNEXPECTED_RATS__030__M__1
TT 8360 "They almost got me! You're sick, goddammit!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__UNEXPECTED_RATS__060__M__1
TT 8361 "Those soldiers are a disgrace." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__UPPER_HOUSE__010__M__1
TT 8362 "That's mercenaries for you." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__UPPER_HOUSE__030__M__1
TT 8363 "Good shot!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__USE_HAM__020__M__1
TT 8364 "Let's keep going." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__VILLAGE_ENTRANCE__060__M__1
TT 8365 "All right, look... The caves keep going on over there. That's our path." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__VISTA_BOAT__010__M__1
TT 8366 "Yes, well, with those rats... I say we go back out." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__VISTA_BOAT__040__M__1
TT 8367 "As long as we make it out alive..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__VISTA_BOAT__060__M__1
TT 8368 "You see the light? It's the lighthouse from the fishermen's village. Sophia's boat is there." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__VISTA_LIGHTHOUSE_FAR__010__M__1
TT 8369 "Ah, those soldiers are too stupid for her..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__WONT_GET_HER__010__M__1
TT 8370 "Stop worrying. She's the Sea Scorpion. She's the real pest." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__WONT_GET_HER__030__M__1
TT 8371 "Currents are pretty tricky 'round here." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__CHATTER__WRECK_SECRET__020__M__1
TT 8372 "Need a hand with that crank?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__ANCHOR_CRANK_1__010__M__1
TT 8373 "You should let me raise the chain." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__ANCHOR_CRANK_2__010__M__1
TT 8374 "Come on! Help me raise this anchor!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__ANCHOR_FREE_2__010__M__1
TT 8375 "Come on, stop daydreaming and get over here!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__ANCHOR_PULL_REMINDER_1__010__M__1
TT 8376 "Are you going to help me with this crank or not?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__ANCHOR_PULL_REMINDER_2__010__M__1
TT 8377 "What are you waiting for?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__ANCHOR_RELEASED_ARNAUD_1__010__M__1
TT 8378 "Go on! Break that chain!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__ANCHOR_RELEASED_ARNAUD_2__010__M__1
TT 8379 "Hey, rats are the boy's thing, right? Isn't there anything you could do about it?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__RAT_MOVE_1__010__M__1
TT 8380 "The damn fish stuck on a trapdoor!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__TRADPOOR_1__010__M__1
TT 8381 "Hey! That lock is keeping the trapdoor shut! Break it!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__TRADPOOR_2__010__M__1
TT 8382 "Amicia! You could keep these rats occupied, no? I mean... it's what you do." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__USE_HAM_BOAT_1__010__M__1
TT 8383 "Hey! That fish! You could bring it down with your sling if you find a good angle!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__HELPER__USE_HAM_BOAT_2__010__M__1
TT 8384 "Hmmm..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__ONOM__LET_GO_OK__050__M__1
TT 8385 "Haha!" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__ONOM__SEAGULLS__061__M__1
TT 8386 "Because you couldn't get out..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__060__M__1
TT 8387 "Huh... I see." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__080__M__1
TT 8388 "It's not far. I'll free the horses. We'll take a safe route walking for the last part." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__105__M__1
TT 8389 "Just a quick check. May I?..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__112__M__1
TT 8390 "It's been two days... so..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__115__M__1
TT 8391 "Good. You're fixed. Sort of. Just let it breathe from now on." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__120__M__1
TT 8392 "That's going to hurt from time to time. Just breathe and relax." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__130__M__1
TT 8393 "Stop trying to be so tough. You might learn something." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__150__M__1
TT 8394 "The Count's army is at war with us - the “scum of Provence”. Most of my men... my friends... have been killed or ran away. It's just a matter of time before they get me." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__190__M__1
TT 8395 "Yes. The noose is tight already but... you have something I don't." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__210__M__1
TT 8396 "The safest way out of this mess for the most wanted man. I know where your island is. All you must do is keep me alive until we get there." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__280_SCAR__230__M__1
TT 8397 "Let's go. We're not here to enjoy the view." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__290_TRANSPORT__020__M__1
TT 8398 "To get your boat. I know someone." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__290_TRANSPORT__040__M__1
TT 8399 "A smuggler. Discreet ship. Fast. What you need." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__290_TRANSPORT__060__M__1
TT 8400 "Yes. Get used to it. This is your life now. So if you want to get to La Cuna after the mess you made, it's that boat or a ten mile fucking swim." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__290_TRANSPORT__080__M__1
TT 8401 "Ah, you see that? That is the right attitude..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__290_TRANSPORT__100__M__1
TT 8402 "I know you like to lead, but I'd better pass first." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__003__M__1
TT 8403 "It's me, goddammit..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__010__M__1
TT 8404 "I've had help." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__055__M__1
TT 8405 "This is Amicia and Hugo. The small one has potential. The big sister... still needs to be tamed..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__080__M__1
TT 8406 "You see?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__100__M__1
TT 8407 "Your boat. We need to go to La Cuna. No questions asked." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__140__M__1
TT 8408 "Then come alone. Sophia, you owe me." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__160__M__1
TT 8409 "Go on..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__180__M__1
TT 8410 "Deal." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__200__M__1
TT 8411 "Oh! “The Call of the Sea”, huh?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__220__M__1
TT 8412 "Sure." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__250__M__1
TT 8413 "Let's go." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__260__M__1
TT 8414 "hahahaha" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 8415 "Yes... It'll do." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__302_WAITING_FOR_SOPHIA__020__M__1
TT 8416 "I can take him. Get some rest." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__302_WAITING_FOR_SOPHIA__050__M__1
TT 8417 "It will be fine." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__302_WAITING_FOR_SOPHIA__060__M__1
TT 8418 "We'll be just there." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__302_WAITING_FOR_SOPHIA__070__M__1
TT 8419 "Don't be so happy when she says things like that..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__302_WAITING_FOR_SOPHIA__110__M__1
TT 8420 "Show off..." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__310_SET_SAIL__030__M__1
TT 8421 "Hey, where 'you going, sailor? You all have a death wish in this family or what?" VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__310_SET_SAIL__070__M__1
TT 8422 "It's alright. I've got you." VO__ARNAUD__CH07__RTC__310_SET_SAIL__080__M__1
TT 8423 "I'd like to see a dragon-man too..." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ABOUT_PROCESSION__020__M__1
TT 8424 "Yes, it would take more than that. It survived Spain, Burgundy... Guyenne... well, barely, that time." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_INTERACT_SHIELD__020__M__1
TT 8425 "Yes. The only time it... failed to protect." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_INTERACT_SHIELD__040__M__1
TT 8426 "No. Someone I shared my coat of arms with." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_INTERACT_SHIELD__060__M__1
TT 8427 "Some memories don't want to be let go of, child." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_INTERACT_SHIELD__080__M__1
TT 8428 "Keep looking out for your brother. It will save you." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ALONE_INTERACT_SHIELD_AFTER__010__M__1
TT 8429 "Shut up! I'll kill you, like I killed your men!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ARNAUD_FIGHT__010__M__1
TT 8430 "I don't care!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ARNAUD_FIGHT__030__M__1
TT 8431 "Go pull the rope on the other side! I'll give you some slack on mine!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__CALL_SAIL__030__M__1
TT 8432 "...not bad..." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ENTRANCE__030__M__1
TT 8433 "Hey, wait, wait... So I heard of this dream, and, well... I'd like to help, but first I must know what you're searching for." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ENTRANCE_ARNAUD__010__M__1
TT 8434 "Good. So bird, tree and water... Could be anywhere. But I guess it's a start!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__ENTRANCE_ARNAUD__040__M__1
TT 8435 "You're about as subtle as you are tall." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__FABRICS_STAND__080__M__1
TT 8436 "Oh, that's bad..." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__FIRST_SHOT_FAIL__020__M__1
TT 8437 "I'm so proud of you!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__FIRST_SHOT_SUCCESS__020__M__1
TT 8438 "Well, he knows about seagulls." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__FISHERMAN_EXIT__020__M__1
TT 8439 "Not a bird much dreamed of, I'd wager." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__FISHERMAN_STAND__043__M__1
TT 8440 "Hey!... Thank you, sir!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__FISHERMAN_STAND__060__M__1
TT 8441 "I'll judge you harshly if you don't..." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__GAME_AIM__010__M__1
TT 8442 "Those crowns didn't stand a chance." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__GAME_FULL_WIN__040__M__1
TT 8443 "Having trouble with your right hand?" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__GAME_LOSE__040__M__1
TT 8444 "EMPTY" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__GAME_LOSE__060__M__1
TT 8445 "Not too good either..." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__GAME_MEDIUM_WIN__020__M__1
TT 8446 "It does its job. Saved my life often enough." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__HUGO_INTERACT_ARNAUD__020__M__1
TT 8447 "It's a griffin—half-lion, half eagle... so you're half right. It was my coat of arms.  Courage and cunning. That's me." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__HUGO_INTERACT_ARNAUD__040__M__1
TT 8448 "It's a good crest too. Strength, stability, wisdom..." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__HUGO_INTERACT_ARNAUD__060__M__1
TT 8449 "The village stretches all the way up." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__MARKET_CRIER__050__M__1
TT 8450 "That would actually be a good way to disorientate an enemy." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__MARKET_GOAT_AFTERMEMORY__020__M__1
TT 8451 "Next time, maybe." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__MARKET_GOAT_AFTERMEMORY__040__M__1
TT 8452 "She loves you!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__MARKET_GOAT_MEMORY__050__M__1
TT 8453 "There! That's “I love you” in goat." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__MARKET_GOAT_MEMORY__080__M__1
TT 8454 "Just like some of my men." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__MARKET_GOAT_TEETH__020__M__1
TT 8455 "You shouldn't tell them that it's a dream. And don't ask too many people. You never know." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__MARKET_SPICES_CALL__020__M__1
TT 8456 "A local deity, obviously. It's Saint John's week on the continent—The summer solstice, so it's probably all about fertility and prosperity." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__PROCESSION_ARNAUDBUSINESS__020__M__1
TT 8457 "He's a god. Pagan one." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__PROCESSION_ARNAUDBUSINESS__040__M__1
TT 8458 "Do I look like it?" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__PROCESSION_DANCE__011__M__1
TT 8459 "You're thirty years too late, lad." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__PROCESSION_DANCE__030__M__1
TT 8460 "You're a savage, shorty..." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__PROCESSION_FLOWERS_INTERACT__150__M__1
TT 8461 "Islands can be nice little havens. But they're fragile ones." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__PROCESSION_WATERWHEEL__030__M__1
TT 8462 "Me too!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__SAIL_PULL_DONE__015__M__1
TT 8463 "You're not supposed to hit the same one twice, you know?" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__SAME_CROWN_THREE__010__M__1
TT 8464 "EMPTY" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__SECOND_SHOT_FAIL__010__M__1
TT 8465 "Slaughter them crowns!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__SECOND_SHOT_SUCCESS__020__M__1
TT 8466 "She'll come. She'd never miss a pint of good ale." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__SOPHIA_BOAT_FAR__030__M__1
TT 8467 "Different captain, different men, different land. Don't think so." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__STREET_COUNT_ARMY__020__M__1
TT 8468 "A bird of prey I'd say... Small one. Fast predators, smart as Hell." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_FEATHER_FALCON__020__M__1
TT 8469 "Looking good, shorty." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_FEATHER_FALCON__040__M__1
TT 8470 "Dreams are tales of the soul, pipsqueak. Not of this world." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__THEATER_LEAVE_INTERACT__020__M__1
TT 8471 "Can't handle the pressure, hm?" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__THIRD_SHOT_FAIL__030__M__1
TT 8472 "Impressive indeed." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__CHATTER__THIRD_SHOT_SUCCESS__020__M__1
TT 8473 "Amicia... It would be nice if you could help with your side!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__HELPER__SAIL_1__010__M__1
TT 8474 "Hey! I've got my side! Mind getting your hands dirty helping with those ropes?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__HELPER__SAIL_2__010__M__1
TT 8475 "Hahaha!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__ONOM__PROCESSION_FLOWERS_INTERACT__110__M__1
TT 8476 "Hi!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__030__M__1
TT 8477 "Alright people, come!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__040__M__1
TT 8478 "Looks like we have a new king." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__130__M__1
TT 8479 "I wonder what the Church would think of this... But they seem successful!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__190__M__1
TT 8480 "Yes..." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__030__M__1
TT 8481 "It's him, come..." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__070__M__1
TT 8482 "We had a deal! Call your rats!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__130__M__1
TT 8483 "You survived! That comes with a price!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__160__M__1
TT 8484 "Fuck it. I don't need you." VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__180__M__1
TT 8485 "I won't miss this time!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__210__M__1
TT 8486 "onom" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 8487 "No! NO!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__010__M__1
TT 8488 "You fucking traitor!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__020__M__1
TT 8489 "I'll kill your bitch, Count! I'll teach you what it is to lose what you care for!" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__100__M__1
TT 8490 "onom" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 8491 "onom" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 8492 "onom" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS_ONOM__030__M__1
TT 8493 "onom" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS_ONOM__050__M__1
TT 8494 "onom" VO__ARNAUD__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS_ONOM__060__M__1
TT 8495 "Kick their arses till they're mincemeat!" VO__ARNAUD__CH13__CHATTER__AMICIA_KILLS_1__010__M__1
TT 8496 "That's it! Show them how worthless they are!" VO__ARNAUD__CH13__CHATTER__AMICIA_KILLS_2__010__M__1
TT 8497 "I'll be damned... Did you come to finish me?" VO__ARNAUD__CH13__CHATTER__FIRST_SHOT__017__M__1
TT 8498 "EMPTY" VO__ARNAUD__CH13__CHATTER__FIRST_SHOT__019__M__1
TT 8499 "Watch out! Heavy bastards approaching!" VO__ARNAUD__CH13__CHATTER__FURIOUS_RATSTRIKE_INTRO__010__M__1
TT 8500 "Come on! Kill the damn bastards!" VO__ARNAUD__CH13__CHATTER__HEAVY_INCOMING__070__M__1
TT 8501 "Good! Now d'you mind taking this bloody rope off my neck?!" VO__ARNAUD__CH13__CHATTER__LAST_ONE_STANDING__020__M__1
TT 8502 "More of them are coming!" VO__ARNAUD__CH13__CHATTER__MORE_COMING_1__010__M__1
