TT 10080 "You're not wrong. But crumbs of gold are still gold..." VO__BANDIT_S2__CH10__CHATTER__MILO_REPUTATION__040__M__1
TT 10081 "It's working too well! They took several of our men yesterday and there were only half as many rats! Milo has to finish this fast!" VO__BANDIT_S2__CH10__CHATTER__PATROL_MERCENARIES__020__M__1
TT 10082 "We'll see about that." VO__BANDIT_S2__CH10__CHATTER__PATROL_MERCENARIES__040__M__1
TT 10083 "That cart is a goddamn waste of good money..." VO__BANDIT_S2__CH10__CHATTER__RELIEVED__005__M__1
TT 10084 "To hell with this shit!" VO__BANDIT_S2__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__015__M__1
TT 10085 "Well... These things come out of the ground to eat us, our slaves escape, and now what?! You're wasting what remains for that mad Countess!" VO__BANDIT_S2__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__040__M__1
TT 10086 "So tell me... How many of us will feed the rats before we see your Child?!" VO__BANDIT_S2__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__060__M__1
