TT 10198 "Seems like we've got some jokers in the area! Search the place!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__1
TT 10199 "Someone's messing with us! Search the place!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__2
TT 10200 "Start searching men! Intruders think they're smarter than us!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__3
TT 10201 "That's it! I'm coming to find you!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 10202 "Again? Think you can fool me?!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 10203 "You're going to regret messing with me!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 10204 "Trespassers here!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__1
TT 10205 "Get over here! We've got intruders!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__2
TT 10206 "We've got intruders! Go after them!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__3
TT 10207 "You! Stay there! I'm coming!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 10208 "Though I wouldn't see you, come here!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 10209 "You! Don't think you can escape!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 10210 "Think you got away? We'll see!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__1
TT 10211 "Well played, but I'll still catch you..." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__2
TT 10212 "Enjoy it while you can. I'll be right there." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__3
TT 10213 "I'll get you! I'll find a way!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__4
TT 10214 "Think you're safe? We'll see about that!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__5
TT 10215 "Laugh while you can: I'm still coming for you!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__6
TT 10216 "Man down!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__1
TT 10217 "No! One of us got killed!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__2
TT 10218 "Someone's dead! Watch out!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__3
TT 10219 "You're about to see what happens when grass burns!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__1
TT 10220 "Wanna hide in the grass, huh? Not very smart." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__2
TT 10221 "How long do you think you can hide in that grass now?!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__3
TT 10222 "Intruders here! Help me stop them!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__1
TT 10223 "Hey! Some bastards here! Catch them!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__2
TT 10224 "With me! Corner the intruders!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__3
TT 10225 "Spread out! Cover the area!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__1
TT 10226 "Get moving and surround them! Don't let them get away!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__2
TT 10227 "Split up and get the bastards!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__3
TT 10228 "You've had it!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__1
TT 10229 "Let's end this!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__2
TT 10230 "It's all over for you now!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__3
TT 10231 "Something's burning!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__1
TT 10232 "Where did that fire come from?!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__2
TT 10233 "Something's caught on fire!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__3
TT 10234 "You better hope there's a Heaven." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__1
TT 10235 "Bet you regret coming here now." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__2
TT 10236 "No one's gonna find your body." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__3
TT 10237 "You sleeping? Come on, get up!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__1
TT 10238 "Get up you drunk! Now!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__2
TT 10239 "Oi! Stop fooling around!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__3
TT 10240 "Don't tell me you fell asleep!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_AFAR__001__M__1
TT 10241 "Hey! What are you doing?!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_AFAR__001__M__2
TT 10242 "What's he doing on the ground?" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_AFAR__001__M__3
TT 10243 "He burnt to death!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_CALCINED__001__M__1
TT 10244 "Was he burnt alive?!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_CALCINED__001__M__2
TT 10245 "He was set on fire!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_CALCINED__001__M__3
TT 10246 "Oh... Eaten to the bones!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_RATS__001__M__1
TT 10247 "Bloody hell. I'm gonna make sure I don't end up like you..." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_RATS__001__M__2
TT 10248 "You let the damn rats get you. Bloody idiot." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_RATS__001__M__3
TT 10249 "He's dead! Let's find who did this!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_SEARCH__001__M__1
TT 10250 "Man down! We've got intruders!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_SEARCH__001__M__2
TT 10251 "We lost one of our men! Search the area!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_SEARCH__001__M__3
TT 10252 "I'm gonna crush the bastard who killed you!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 10253 "Body's still fresh! Whoever you are, you'll pay for that!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 10254 "Dead... The killer must still be close!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__3
