TT 10259 "Good Lord! What's happening?!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__DYING__001__M__2
TT 10260 "Bloody hell!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__DYING__001__M__3
