TT 10262 "Don't touch me!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__FLEE_RATS__001__M__2
TT 10263 "You won't kill me, rats!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__PATROL__FLEE_RATS__001__M__3
