TT 10466 "They're up there! Hurry!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SEARCH_SPOTTER_UP__001__M__2
TT 10467 "Climb up there and catch the bastards!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SEARCH_SPOTTER_UP__001__M__3
TT 10468 "I saw you climb up! Coward!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SEARCH_SPOTTER_UP_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 10469 "Get back down here and fight!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SEARCH_SPOTTER_UP_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 10470 "Don't think I didn't see you climb up there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SEARCH_SPOTTER_UP_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 10471 "Again?! Get over there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AGAIN_SPOTTER__001__M__1
TT 10472 "There it is again! See what it was!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AGAIN_SPOTTER__001__M__2
TT 10473 "It's back! See what it is!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AGAIN_SPOTTER__001__M__3
TT 10474 "It's back! Can't be!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AGAIN_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 10475 "Again?" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AGAIN_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 10476 "Not again!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AGAIN_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 10477 "What was that noise? We'll better have a look!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER__001__M__1
TT 10478 "See what made that noise!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER__001__M__2
TT 10479 "I heard something over there! Go take a look!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER__001__M__3
TT 10480 "What was that noise?" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 10481 "What's making that noise?" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 10482 "What was that noise?" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 10483 "Go check what's wrong with that fire!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_LIGHT_SPOTTER__001__M__1
TT 10484 "What's happening to that fire? Go check!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_LIGHT_SPOTTER__001__M__2
TT 10485 "The fire! You saw it too! Go take a look!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_LIGHT_SPOTTER__001__M__3
TT 10486 "The fire! Something's not right!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_LIGHT_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 10487 "The hell is wrong with this bloody fire, damn it?!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_LIGHT_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 10488 "Must be witchcraft!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_LIGHT_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 10489 "I saw something there." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER__001__M__1
TT 10490 "There's something out there." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER__001__M__2
TT 10491 "Something moved over there." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER__001__M__3
TT 10492 "Who's there?! Show yourself!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 10493 "What was that...?" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 10494 "Hey! Someone there?!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 10495 "I think I saw something back there..." VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_COVER__001__M__1
TT 10496 "Huh?! Something just moved back there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_COVER__001__M__2
TT 10497 "Back there! I just saw something!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_COVER__001__M__3
TT 10498 "Something's going on down there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_DOWN__001__M__1
TT 10499 "Did you see that?! There's something down there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_DOWN__001__M__2
TT 10500 "Movement! Down there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_DOWN__001__M__3
TT 10501 "I think I saw something move in the grass!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_GRASS__001__M__1
TT 10502 "Something moved in that grass!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_GRASS__001__M__2
TT 10503 "I saw movement in the grass!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_GRASS__001__M__3
TT 10504 "Hey! Something moved in there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_INSIDE__001__M__1
TT 10505 "I swear I saw something  in there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_INSIDE__001__M__2
TT 10506 "Hey! I just saw movement in there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_INSIDE__001__M__3
TT 10507 "Something's going on up there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_UP__001__M__1
TT 10508 "Did you see that?! There's something up there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_UP__001__M__2
TT 10509 "Movement! Up there!" VO__BANDIT_S2__GENERIC__STATIC__SUSPICION_SPOTTER_UP__001__M__3
TT 10510 "Got it." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__BROTHERS_BACK__010__M__1
TT 10511 "He's probably hiding somewhere..." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__BROTHERS_BACK__050__M__1
TT 10512 "I see her! She's here!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__FATHER_FIRE__010__M__1
TT 10513 "I don't care! You killed my son! Burn in Hell!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__FATHER_FIRE__022__M__1
TT 10514 "It's a bloodbath... Lord..." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__JACQUES__005__M__1
TT 10515 "I don't feel well, Mathias..." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__JACQUES__020__M__1
TT 10516 "It's... whatever." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__JACQUES__040__M__1
TT 10517 "We don't have to kill all of them.... you lunatic..." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__JACQUES__060__M__1
TT 10518 "Is someone still hiding?" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__JACQUES_DISTRACTED__010__M__1
TT 10519 "Again? I'll find you, y'bloody fools!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__JACQUES_DISTRACTED__020__M__1
TT 10520 "The hell?!... I've got an axe, I warn you!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__JAR_TUTO_OK__010__M__1
TT 10521 "Saints protect me..." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__JAR_TUTO_OK__030__M__1
TT 10522 "Just needed goddamn work!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__NO_EXIT__020__M__1
TT 10523 "I need to get out of here..." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__NO_EXIT__030__M__1
TT 10524 "Look for the girl! The others ran down the hill!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH01__CHATTER__VISTA_ROOF__015__M__1
TT 10525 "Spread out! Search the perimeter! Remember your training. Arnaud expects discipline!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_INTRO__035__M__1
TT 10526 "You just shot a dead body, you idiot!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_INTRO__110__M__1
TT 10527 "Stop playing and keep your eyes open! Or you'll be explaining to Arnaud why we're empty-handed when he arrives!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_INTRO__130__M__1
TT 10528 "I expected more soldiers... Where are they? Maybe sick or... up to something..." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_UP_INTRO__010__M__1
TT 10529 "We wait for reinforcement! Hold the place!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_FIELD_AFTER_BANDITS_ARNAUD__020__M__1
TT 10530 "Hold it, that's all!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_FIELD_AFTER_BANDITS_ARNAUD__040__M__1
TT 10531 "Well, if he's here, he didn't make much effort trying to cure these people... Look at that, they're poorer than us. Not a coin..." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__BANDIT_LOOTING__010__M__1
TT 10532 "Someone will find him." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__BANDIT_LOOTING__030__M__1
TT 10533 "So, any sign of the doctor? I've heard nothing yet." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__INSIDE_BANDITS_CHAT_A__010__M__1
TT 10534 "And the boss will be here soon..." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__INSIDE_BANDITS_CHAT_A__030__M__1
TT 10535 "Stop panicking! Stay in the light and you'll be fine!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__MERCENARY_REACT_1__010__M__1
TT 10536 "Rats! They're coming!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH02__CHATTER__RATS_CHASED__020__M__1
TT 10537 "Once this is over, you'll feast every day of your life!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH10__CHATTER__BROKEN_BRIDGE__020__M__1
TT 10538 "All of you! Hold your positions and watch those trenches! Milo! You can go whenever you want!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH10__CHATTER__FIRE_CROSS__020__M__1
TT 10539 "They all look pretty dead to me..." VO__BANDIT_S3__CH10__CHATTER__GATE_WAIT__020__M__1
TT 10540 "Almost!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH10__CHATTER__IMPATIENT__020__M__1
TT 10541 "Hey! What?! Who let you in?!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH10__CHATTER__KNIFE_EVENT__010__M__1
TT 10542 "Damn intruder!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH10__CHATTER__KNIFE_EVENT__050__M__1
TT 10543 "I'll kill you!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH10__CHATTER__KNIFE_EVENT__070__M__1
TT 10544 "You heard the boss! Everybody keep watch! And close that portcullis!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH10__CHATTER__MILO_LEFT__020__M__1
TT 10545 "Well I guess it just takes time!" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH10__CHATTER__MILO_STUCK__020__M__1
TT 10546 "Rats... bloody rats... It's all true... Hoped it was just a damn lunatic's joke. Well I'm not laughing now, am I?" VO__BANDIT_S3__CH10__CHATTER__PATROL_DOWN__010__M__1
