TT 11168 "They're coming! Keep them off my back!" VO__BOATMAN__CH05__CHATTER__ROCKS__026__M__1
TT 11169 "On the right!" VO__BOATMAN__CH05__CHATTER__ROCKS_RIGHT__010__M__1
TT 11170 "Shit!" VO__BOATMAN__CH05__CHATTER__TO_THE_SITE__030__M__1
TT 11171 "Hurry! Burn that thing so we can get out of here!" VO__BOATMAN__CH05__HELPER__CART_FIRE_1__010__M__1
TT 11172 "Look in the rafters for something to break! The counterweight should be there!" VO__BOATMAN__CH05__HELPER__CHAIN_BREAK_2__010__M__1
TT 11173 "I heard the same thing happened in Guyenne... The rats, the Bite that poisons your blood. It seemed far from us..." VO__BOATMAN__CH05__RTC__190_AFTER_CARNAGE__010__M__1
TT 11174 "The debris... It all piled up here." VO__BOATMAN__CH05__RTC__190_AFTER_CARNAGE__240__M__1
