TT 11177 "He's a big problem you have now. We must leave." VO__BOATMAN__CH05__RTC__200_EMBUSH__028__M__1
TT 11178 "We're out of the gorge! Current's getting stronger!" VO__BOATMAN__CH05__RTC__210_LANDING__010__M__1
TT 11179 "You're doing good, lady! That crossbow was made for you!" VO__BOATMAN__CH05__RTC__210_LANDING__040__M__1
TT 11180 "onom" VO__BOATMAN__CH05__RTC__210_LANDING_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 11181 "You'll die anyway! And for what?! The past is the past!" VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__ARNAUD_FIGHT__020__M__1
TT 11182 "So where are you from?" VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_END__010__M__1
TT 11183 "Yes... During the Brighter Days, all the people of La Cuna are one, united around the Child of Embers." VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_HUGO__020__M__1
TT 11184 "A “bon vivant”!" VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_HUGO__050__M__1
TT 11185 "Of course, my love." VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_FOLLOWING__020__M__1
TT 11186 "To us, His Mother and Father." VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_HERITAGE_TALK__020__M__1
TT 11187 "You're quite young for such a long trip. Where are your parents?" VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_PARENTS__010__M__1
TT 11188 "By who? How?!" VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_PARENTS__030__M__1
TT 11189 "Hm, you know me." VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_PARENTS__060__M__1
TT 11190 "Finally, they cleaned the basins!" VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_PRIDE_INTRO__030__M__1
TT 11191 "Is everything ready for tomorrow?" VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__GUEST__005__M__1
TT 11192 "I must say, we... appreciate that you paid homage to the Child so willingly." VO__COUNT__CH08__CHATTER__GUEST__030__M__1
TT 11193 "Where is she? She should have been here already!" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__010__M__1
TT 11194 "Alright! You all know me! I'm not a man of words.  Emilie, your Priestess, she... will be here soon!" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__020__M__1
TT 11195 "She will open these Brighter Days with her beautiful words. The words of a mother!" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__050__M__1
TT 11196 "The Mother of the Child of Embers!" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__060__M__1
TT 11197 "The Child who protects his sacred lands from the rats of disease and war!" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__080__M__1
TT 11198 "What is this?" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__195__M__1
TT 11199 "I knew it!" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__200__M__1
TT 11200 "I'll take care of him! Catch the girl!" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__250__M__1
TT 11201 "onom" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 11202 "So this is his army? A girl and a boy!" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__040__M__1
TT 11203 "Emilie..." VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__070__M__1
TT 11204 "Of course, my love." VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__090__M__1
TT 11205 "You've always been a disgrace to the knighthood, Arnaud! And you've been a pain in my arse for too long!" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__110__M__1
TT 11206 "Lock him up, I'll handle that later!" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__120__M__1
TT 11207 "So where do you know this beast from?" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__130__M__1
TT 11208 "Sure! Emilie's right. You helped. You deserve it." VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__190__M__1
TT 11209 "onom" VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS_ONOM__040__M__1
TT 11210 "Nonsense. You're our guests. There is a good dinner being cooked." VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__030__M__1
TT 11211 "He will be judged. All those who do bad things are. And he did a lot." VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__090__M__1
TT 11212 "But you will have the chance to testify if you wish to do so." VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__100__M__1
TT 11213 "My lady." VO__COUNT__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__135__M__1
TT 11214 "Open your mind and heart! It is now time to tell his tale!" VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__BEGINNING_RITUAL__010__M__1
TT 11215 "Centuries ago, a child was born on this land! His heart was blessed by the Sun, from which he inherited the flame that rules everything. And so was born the Child of Fire." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__CHILD_OF_LIGHT__010__M__1
TT 11216 "Of all places, La Cuna was his home. It became a land of life and peace. A place to heal. To thrive." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__CHILD_OF_LIGHT__030__M__1
TT 11217 "La Cuna became a cradle of light." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__CHILD_OF_LIGHT__040__M__1
TT 11218 "Evil found the Child, inside these very halls." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__DARKNESS__010__M__1
TT 11219 "It fed on His fire. Weakened it... Marked His flesh with coal black scars. His Mother's arms couldn't warm Him anymore." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__DARKNESS__040__M__1
TT 11220 "You are back, and your torch is gone. You are not alone anymore." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__EMBERS__010__M__1
TT 11221 "Everyone! It is almost time!" VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__LATECOMERS_RITUAL__010__M__1
TT 11222 "And evil knows no mercy." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__LIGHT_TO_DARK__010__M__1
TT 11223 "Please kneel." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__LIGHT_TO_DARK_REMINDER__040__M__1
TT 11224 "Join us! Blow on those flames!" VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__PHOENIX__025__M__1
TT 11225 "May this putrid water seal our determination." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__PRAYER__010__M__1
TT 11226 "I feel your sickness." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__PRAYER__030__M__1
TT 11227 "We will protect you." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__PRAYER__050__M__1
TT 11228 "I am the Father. I am waiting for you." VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__PRAYER__070__M__1
TT 11229 "The Carriers have been chosen! Take your places!" VO__COUNT__CH09__CHATTER__TORCH_BEARER__040__M__1
TT 11230 "Here we are, my Child... We respect your sleep, and won't move further." VO__COUNT__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__140__M__1
TT 11231 "Friends and children! Today marks the longest day of the year! The light of the summer solistice shines upon us once again!" VO__COUNT__CH09__RTC__FIRST_RITUALS__010__M__1
TT 11232 "It is time to bring the flame of the Phoenix to his dormant embers!" VO__COUNT__CH09__RTC__FIRST_RITUALS__017__M__1
TT 11233 "Like Father..." VO__COUNT__CH09__RTC__FIRST_RITUALS__075__M__1
TT 11234 "Not only the rats. Come, you'll see for yourself." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__AFTER__010__M__1
TT 11235 "Haaa! Damn you!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__AFTER_HIT__010__M__1
TT 11236 "The main gate is secure enough for now, but the western rampart is still weak! If the rats enter through there we won't be able to evacuate the wounded. Now, I want to know where those rats come from. Send scouts. If we can find a way to slow them, stop them or send them to Hell, it'll be worth the risk." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__BATTLE_PLAN__020__M__1
TT 11237 "Good." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__BATTLE_PLAN__065__M__1
TT 11238 "This is a war unlike any other. But it's still a war." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__BATTLE_PLAN__067__M__1
TT 11239 "Dismissed! And have faith! It's not over yet!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__BATTLE_PLAN__070__M__1
TT 11240 "Oh, you remind me of old times... Of myself... Now I'll see you... where your blood flows..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__BEHIND_DOOR__010__M__1
TT 11241 "Just let go." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CELLAR_AGAIN__010__M__1
TT 11242 "The truth is everything's rotten but her! She's the only reason this world is not burning!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CELLAR_AGAIN__030__M__1
TT 11243 "But we'll protect your brother from that rot! We have the power to!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CELLAR_AGAIN__040__M__1
TT 11244 "Emilie... Her bloody parents broke her mind until she tried to take her own life. Poisoned her own body... So I brought her here, offered her this Child of Embers story... Not only did she believe it, she turned it into hope for the people!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION__020__M__1
TT 11245 "What are you trying to do?... Accept your fate." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION__040__M__1
TT 11246 "I'll find you! And you will DIE like a dog!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_KITCHEN__021__M__1
TT 11247 "How dare you?! Come back!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_RUN__010__M__1
TT 11248 "I won't lose her! Not for you!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_RUN__030__M__1
TT 11249 "Where are you going?!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_RUN__050__M__1
TT 11250 "Even I can't save her from herself! But your brother can!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_STAIRS__010__M__1
TT 11251 "You can't imagine what's at stake!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_STAIRS_LOW__030__M__1
TT 11252 "You're going nowhere!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_AGGRESSIVE__010__M__1
TT 11253 "Emilie! I'm here!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_COME_BACK__010__M__1
TT 11254 "Let him go, Emilie! He's not the Child of Embers! Come to me!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_COME_BACK__030__M__1
TT 11255 "You can! Try! Give me your hand!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_COME_BACK__050__M__1
TT 11256 "EMPTY" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_ENTERS__005__M__1
TT 11257 "Where is she?!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_ENTERS__040__M__1
TT 11258 "You chose the hard way!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK__040__M__1
TT 11259 "I hear you! Fear makes you sloppy!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK__060__M__1
TT 11260 "All right, let's play! I'm good at this game, you'll see!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__DOOR_CLOSE__010__M__1
TT 11261 "You're stuck here! Wherever you go, I'll find you! I've been trained for this!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IDLE_CHASE4__010__M__1
TT 11262 "It hurts terribly, doesn't it?! I can ease the pain! Trust me..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IDLE_CHASE5__010__M__1
TT 11263 "Your survival instinct... I admire it...  You've been through a lot, I can tell. It makes this even more exciting." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IDLE_CHASE6__010__M__1
TT 11264 "It's been a while since I hunted... Since I met Emilie... And you are wonderful prey!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IDLE_CHASE8__010__M__1
TT 11265 "She liked you, you know, Emilie... But you're too much of a threat... For us... For the child!..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IDLE_CHASE9__010__M__1
TT 11266 "No! Emilie, quick!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IMPENDING_LAST_STRIKE__020__M__1
TT 11267 "Your hand!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IMPENDING_LAST_STRIKE__040__M__1
TT 11268 "Where are you running?! There is no escape!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__KITCHEN_DOOR__010__M__1
TT 11269 "Come on, let's finish this!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__KITCHEN_HIDE__010__M__1
TT 11270 "I know it seems unfair..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__KITCHEN_HIDE__035__M__1
TT 11271 "But you don't know what it takes to rule!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__KITCHEN_HIDE__040__M__1
TT 11272 "War... it's so easy. I could destroy everything... But she showed me another way... She has a light about her! You've seen it!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__KITCHEN_HIDE__050__M__1
TT 11273 "Right, everybody out!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__KITCHEN_IN__010__M__1
TT 11274 "You and me, now..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__KITCHEN_IN__030__M__1
TT 11275 "You're trapped..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__LURE__020__M__1
TT 11276 "Enough games! Come here!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__LURE_OUT__010__M__1
TT 11277 "Aaargh! I'll kill you!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__LURE_OUT_AGAIN__010__M__1
TT 11278 "What? You dirty little..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__LURE_TRAPPED__010__M__1
TT 11279 "You insolent brat! I'll make you suffer for this!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__LURE_TRAPPED_AGAIN__010__M__1
TT 11280 "I tried to be patient..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__NOISES_KITCHEN__025__M__1
TT 11281 "All the signs are here." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__PRAYING__030__M__1
TT 11282 "Running again?!... You are tireless..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__RUN__020__M__1
TT 11283 "If only my men had half your determination!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__RUN__030__M__1
TT 11284 "You did it! Amazing..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__RUN__050__M__1
TT 11285 "It's too late! Now she knows he exists!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__RUNNING__020__M__1
TT 11286 "People believe in her as much as in the Child!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__RUNNING_CELLAR__020__M__1
TT 11287 "Don't you get it?! This is bigger than you!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__RUNNING_CELLAR__027__M__1
TT 11288 "Give up! Surrender your brother! We can do this the easy way!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__RUNNING_CELLAR__028__M__1
TT 11289 "Don't be so dramatic... You'll simply disappear. And the world won't care!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__RUNNING_CELLAR__050__M__1
TT 11290 "So you survived those beasts..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__WALK__040__M__1
TT 11291 "A lord should know that no peace lasts forever. But I confess that... after years of war... I had... dared to hope that this one would." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__WALK__044__M__1
TT 11292 "No, no. That's... exactly it." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__WALK__047__M__1
TT 11293 "You're right. But it doesn't stop you from being there when battle calls." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__WALK__050__M__1
TT 11294 "Come, I need you." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__WALK_OUT__010__M__1
TT 11295 "Ha!" VO__COUNT__CH12__ONOM__CRANK__020__M__1
