TT 11297 "Ha!" VO__COUNT__CH12__ONOM__RUNNING_HALL__020__M__1
TT 11298 "Emilie wants the boy, Amicia. I'm sorry but she is sure now." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__620_DECEIVED__020__M__1
TT 11299 "That your brother is the Child of Embers. She must have him, so you must die." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__620_DECEIVED__040__M__1
TT 11300 "You're probably right... Because I invented most of it. And I did it for her." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__620_DECEIVED__060__M__1
TT 11301 "Sorry my love, but this one is a hell of a fighter!" VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__630_THE_BALLROOM__080__M__1
TT 11302 "Now this..." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__630_THE_BALLROOM__090__M__1
TT 11303 "This is an invitation I can't refuse." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__630_THE_BALLROOM__100__M__1
TT 11304 "Onom" VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__630_THE_BALLROOM_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 11305 "You caught me by surprise. I'm impressed." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__640_DUEL__010__M__1
TT 11306 "You're quite something you know... You face me. Thinking with all your soul, that you can defeat me!" VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__640_DUEL__020__M__1
TT 11307 "Huh. Such dedication..." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__640_DUEL__040__M__1
TT 11308 "You have a burning fire inside you." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__640_DUEL__050__M__1
TT 11309 "But a flame without a discipline doesn't make a soldier..." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__640_DUEL__060__M__1
TT 11310 "... it consumes them from within." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__640_DUEL__070__M__1
TT 11311 "Oh I know. You fight because you don't have the choice. I chose this life. This is why you'll fail." VO__COUNT__CH12__RTC__640_DUEL__090__M__1
