TT 11446 "That cover won't save you from me..." VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SEARCH_SPOTTER_COVER_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 11447 "Amicia, you can't hide from me behind that!" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SEARCH_SPOTTER_COVER_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 11448 "Do you really think hiding behind that will save you?" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SEARCH_SPOTTER_COVER_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 11449 "Amicia, don't hide behind there! Come out!" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SEARCH_SPOTTER_COVER_ALONE__001__M__4
TT 11450 "You won't be safe behind there! Face me!" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SEARCH_SPOTTER_COVER_ALONE__001__M__5
TT 11451 "Hiding behind that... Amicia I expected more from you?!" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SEARCH_SPOTTER_COVER_ALONE__001__M__6
TT 11452 "I saw you. Get out from under there." VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SEARCH_SPOTTER_INSIDE_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 11453 "Hiding under there won't save you." VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SEARCH_SPOTTER_INSIDE_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 11454 "Do you think hiding under there will fool me?" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SEARCH_SPOTTER_INSIDE_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 11455 "Are you really playing games with me?" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SUSPICION_AGAIN_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 11456 "Amicia stop playing with me!" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SUSPICION_AGAIN_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 11457 "Your little games are useless!" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SUSPICION_AGAIN_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 11458 "Amicia you are so noisy... You won't escape like this..." VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 11459 "I've heard you! Stay right where you are!" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 11460 "That is the sound of someone trying to hide." VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 11461 "So much noise! It'll lead me right to you!" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__4
TT 11462 "Ah, I hear you! You can't run away from me." VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__5
TT 11463 "You won't escape me hiding like this, young lady!" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__6
TT 11464 "So noisy Amicia! You'll have to do better!" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SUSPICION_AUDIO_SPOTTER_ALONE__001__M__7
TT 11465 "Where could you be?" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SWITCH_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 11466 "You know how to hide, I'll give you that." VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SWITCH_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 11467 "Sooner or later, I will find you." VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SWITCH_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 11468 "If you're not here, where are you?" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SWITCH_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__4
TT 11469 "Where did you go?" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SWITCH_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__5
TT 11470 "Where are you?" VO__COUNT__GENERIC__PATROL__SWITCH_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__6
TT 11471 "You were right to come here. Let's keep going. You must be tired after this... adventure." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_END__030__M__1
TT 11472 "I know this all looks pretty formal, but please... Here I'm not “your grace”. I am the Mother. I am myself, so be yourself!" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_HUGO__010__M__1
TT 11473 "So?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_HUGO__030__M__1
TT 11474 "Be careful. They're very rich." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_HUGO__060__M__1
TT 11475 "It is! And it's only a small part of the palace! Oh, do you fancy some dates, before we show you to your room?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_OFFER__010__M__1
TT 11476 "Come on." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__BANQUETHALL_FRUIT_OFFER__050__M__1
TT 11477 "Let me show you something else. Victor?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_FOLLOWING__010__M__1
TT 11478 "Come next to me, Hugo." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_GO_FLOWERS__010__M__1
TT 11479 "The land here is strong. The Child of Embers breathes life into it. We created the Brighter Days to celebrate him, in the hope he'll come back to us, as it is foretold." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_HERITAGE_TALK__010__M__1
TT 11480 "And to the people." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_HERITAGE_TALK__030__M__1
TT 11481 "Victor, don't be so... military." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_PARENTS__050__M__1
TT 11482 "And these are our gardens! My favourite part!" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_PRIDE_INTRO__010__M__1
TT 11483 "Yes. Aren't they nice?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_PRIDE_INTRO__040__M__1
TT 11484 "You see those plants? Most of them are not from here. But we managed to make them grow anyway." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_TALK_FLOWERS__010__M__1
TT 11485 "Thanks to a lot of love and care. We are just like them, you know..." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_TALK_FLOWERS__030__M__1
TT 11486 "And we need a good soil, love, and care. This land is open to you, if you wish to... keep growing here." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_TALK_FLOWERS__050__M__1
TT 11487 "But of course, the big sister will decide, right Amicia?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GARDENS_TALK_FLOWERS__060__M__1
TT 11488 "Yes... the new robes look wonderful. It will be... perfect." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GUEST__010__M__1
TT 11489 "Oh... Shall we go?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GUEST__016__M__1
TT 11490 "That is very true." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__GUEST__037__M__1
TT 11491 "Agnes? Go get a room ready for two, please." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__MAID_TALK__010__M__1
TT 11492 "So, how do you like our terrace?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__PALACE__010__M__1
TT 11493 "This is home!" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__PALACE__030__M__1
TT 11494 "Come! Come inside!" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__PALACE_GETTINGINSIDE__010__M__1
TT 11495 "Would you pray with me? You can do it in your own way." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__PRAY__010__M__1
TT 11496 "A humble flame... to light his night. And may he rise... a sun... a son... so bright!" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__PRAY__020__M__1
TT 11497 "Thank you... I appreciate it. Shall we go?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__PRAY__060__M__1
TT 11498 "Of course, I understand. I'll wait for you. Come when it is done." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__PRAY_AFTER__010__M__1
TT 11499 "Here it is." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__ROOM_ARRIVAL__040__M__1
TT 11500 "We pray to him not as a god, but as our long sleeping child." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__STATUE_INTRO__010__M__1
TT 11501 "We love and revere him..." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__STATUE_INTRO__020__M__1
TT 11502 "To revive his flame." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__STATUE_INTRO__030__M__1
TT 11503 "You'll have plenty of time to wander around later." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__CHATTER__WRONGWAY_BASIN__030__M__1
TT 11504 "Victor! STOP!" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__060__M__1
TT 11505 "Don't get carried away. She helped. They're not a threat." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__080__M__1
TT 11506 "Are you alright?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__125__M__1
TT 11507 "Now if you're not bandits... who are you?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__150__M__1
TT 11508 "Well don't be. There was more fright than danger. These days are dedicated to life and peace! Would you agree to be our guests for dinner?" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__170__M__1
TT 11509 "Come with us!" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__380_COUNT_AND_COUNTESS__200__M__1
TT 11510 "Go on!" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__010__M__1
TT 11511 "Oh! We'll need to get you some new clothes. It looks like you had a long journey." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__060__M__1
TT 11512 "But enough of that. We'll leave you to rest. Tomorrow, feel free to enjoy La Cuna. Brighter Days are the best time for it." VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__110__M__1
TT 11513 "Beds are great! Try jumping on them!" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS__140__M__1
TT 11514 "onom" VO__COUNTESS__CH08__RTC__390_COUNTESS_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 11515 "So that it is never forgotten." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__BEGINNING_RITUAL__020__M__1
TT 11516 "His flame shone over the world. He blessed it with his perfume. His laughter. His joy." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__CHILD_OF_LIGHT__020__M__1
TT 11517 "But light tempts evil." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__CHILD_OF_LIGHT__050__M__1
TT 11518 "And so his light faded. Almost entirely. And the Child of Fire turned into the Child of Embers." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__DARKNESS__050__M__1
TT 11519 "A dark era began. Men forgot about him." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__DARKNESS__070__M__1
TT 11520 "But we did not! This flame is the last gleam of His light. Our hope. And now, two of you, a woman and a child, will carry it through his night." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__DARKNESS__080__M__1
TT 11521 "You. Your heads are bent. Your humility honours you. You will walk His flame through His darkest hours." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__DARKNESS__090__M__1
TT 11522 "Take it." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__DARKNESS__100__M__1
TT 11523 "His embers glow in the dark... I am the Mother and I welcome him." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__EMBERS__020__M__1
TT 11524 "Pass it to me." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__EMBERS__030__M__1
TT 11525 "You did well." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__EMBERS__040__M__1
TT 11526 "Gather round please!" VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__LATECOMERS_RITUAL__020__M__1
TT 11527 "We are still waiting for a few latecomers! Feel free to come closer, in the meantime!" VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__LATECOMERS_RITUAL__050__M__1
TT 11528 "Come." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__LIGHT_TO_DARK__020__M__1
TT 11529 "Take your place at our sides." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__LIGHT_TO_DARK_1__030__M__1
TT 11530 "Hear me, Child! I am not barren anymore for your flame lives in me! I am the Mother! Become the Phoenix! The Child of Fire reborn!" VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__PHOENIX__010__M__1
TT 11531 "To stand by your side, day and night." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__PRAYER__020__M__1
TT 11532 "I share your pain." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__PRAYER__040__M__1
TT 11533 "We will care for you." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__PRAYER__060__M__1
TT 11534 "I am the Mother. I am waiting for you." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__PRAYER__080__M__1
TT 11535 "Join us, whenever you feel ready. We are." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__PRAYER__090__M__1
TT 11536 "May the breeze of life reignite his flame!" VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__SOPHIA_BACK__040__M__1
TT 11537 "You will walk in his steps, know the cold that bites the flesh, the drowning in the absence of light. The uncertainty." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__TORCH_BEARER__010__M__1
TT 11538 "You will see the Child die through the eyes of His Mother. You will be the victim and the witness." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__TORCH_BEARER__020__M__1
TT 11539 "Keep that torch alive, at all costs." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__TORCH_BEARER__030__M__1
TT 11540 "Come." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__TORCH_BEARER__060__M__1
TT 11541 "Go forth and bring Him the light. Much depends on it..." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__CHATTER__TORCH_BEARER_END__010__M__1
TT 11542 "Have no fear. Come to us." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__HELPER__LOCKED_UP_1__030__M__1
TT 11543 "Bring the flame to the end of the path. Give it to me." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__HELPER__LOCKED_UP_2__040__M__1
TT 11544 "We've walked in your steps, our souls bared, ready to ease your pain. Our arms and hearts are opened for you." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__150__M__1
TT 11545 "And yet... in these cold hallways, hidden from the sun, the Child of Embers still slumbers." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__RTC__FIRST_RITUALS__012__M__1
TT 11546 "Thus will we prove that we deserve to care for him. Like Mother..." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__RTC__FIRST_RITUALS__065__M__1
TT 11547 "Let us pray together before we enter." VO__COUNTESS__CH09__RTC__FIRST_RITUALS__085__M__1
TT 11548 "Victor! He's gone mad!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_COME_BACK__020__M__1
TT 11549 "I can't reach you!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_COME_BACK__040__M__1
TT 11550 "I can't!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_COME_BACK__060__M__1
TT 11551 "What are you doing?!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__CHATTER__FIRST_STRIKES__030__M__1
TT 11552 "It's too late, Victor!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__CHATTER__IMPENDING_LAST_STRIKE__030__M__1
TT 11553 "It's all right!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__CHATTER__IMPENDING_LAST_STRIKE__050__M__1
TT 11554 "She's deceiving you, Hugo! Stop this!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__CHATTER__SECOND_STRIKES__040__M__1
TT 11555 "Please!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__CHATTER__SECOND_STRIKES__060__M__1
TT 11556 "Stop! They won't hurt you, my child! It's her they want!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__CHATTER__SECOND_WAVE__010__M__1
TT 11557 "No, Hugo! This is a mistake!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__CHATTER__SECOND_WAVE__030__M__1
TT 11558 "Don't be afraid... Yes, you've failed but... this child was never truly yours." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__630_THE_BALLROOM__010__M__1
TT 11559 "No! He will be loved! He will shine like a brighter sun! Repel this darkness! And I... I'll just be a mother, watching the first steps of a god." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__630_THE_BALLROOM__014__M__1
TT 11560 "I feel so... full of him." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__630_THE_BALLROOM__015__M__1
TT 11561 "How are you still alive?" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__630_THE_BALLROOM__040__M__1
TT 11562 "At last!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__630_THE_BALLROOM__060__M__1
TT 11563 "Enough games, Victor. This is not what we're here for." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__650_AMICIAS_CALL__010__M__1
TT 11564 "I'm sorry. War took its toll on my husband. He gets... carried away sometimes." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__650_AMICIAS_CALL__012__M__1
TT 11565 "I admire you. Your children are strong. Your bonds are strong." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__650_AMICIAS_CALL__013__M__1
TT 11566 "When I was her age... I could only wish for this kind of love." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__650_AMICIAS_CALL__014__M__1
TT 11567 "But it's not just about us, for love is meant to be shared..." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__650_AMICIAS_CALL__015__M__1
TT 11568 "To be turned into light, shone over the whole world!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__650_AMICIAS_CALL__016__M__1
TT 11569 "Such is the fate of the Child of Embers." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__650_AMICIAS_CALL__020__M__1
TT 11570 "For now, it will be quick." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__650_AMICIAS_CALL__024__M__1
TT 11571 "Oh my baby boy..." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__660_NOW_THEY_DIE__040__M__1
TT 11572 "You should get back to bed." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__660_NOW_THEY_DIE__046__M__1
TT 11573 "No, no... I'll take you back to bed? Victor... take him back, will you?" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__660_NOW_THEY_DIE__060__M__1
TT 11574 "It's you... It's you! I knew it!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__660_NOW_THEY_DIE__080__M__1
TT 11575 "No! What are you doing?... Please... Please..." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__660_NOW_THEY_DIE__100__M__1
TT 11576 "I'll be a better mother..." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__660_NOW_THEY_DIE__120__M__1
TT 11577 "I'll be a better mother!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__660_NOW_THEY_DIE__130__M__1
TT 11578 "Please!" VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__660_NOW_THEY_DIE__140__M__1
TT 11579 "My love..." VO__COUNTESS__CH12__RTC__665_DEVOURED__008__M__1
