TT 13734 "Enjoy your freedom!" VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__CLIFF_FALL__060__M__1
TT 13735 "Damn bastard made me sweat!" VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__CLIFF_FALL_REACTION__050__M__1
TT 13736 "We really need to teach them discipline..." VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__CLIFF_FALL_REACTION__060__M__1
TT 13737 "I got that one. The others ran away." VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__INTRO_SLAVES__010__M__1
TT 13738 "Keep watch in case they come back to free the rest. I'll take this one back." VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__INTRO_SLAVES__030__M__1
TT 13739 "Oh... I will. Soon." VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__INTRO_SLAVES__080__M__1
TT 13740 "I want quiet. Kill any trespassers." VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__INTRO_SLAVES__090__M__1
TT 13741 "Light up the trench! We must buy some time!" VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__POST_WAVE__020__M__1
TT 13742 "Hold off the rats from the chapel for as long as you can!" VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__RATS_IN_SCARED__010__M__1
TT 13743 "Make sure I'm not disturbed! This is between the Child and me!" VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__RATS_IN_SCARED__040__M__1
TT 13744 "It's alright, it will be over soon." VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__010__M__1
TT 13745 "You got a problem, Diaz?" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__025__M__1
TT 13746 "Wrong! We're not working for her anymore..." VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__043__M__1
TT 13747 "It's all in the fresco! The rats announce the coming of the Child, and you've seen how hungry they are! So it's simple: we please them, we please the Child, we buy ourselves a seat next to his throne!" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__046__M__1
TT 13748 "Then the Count will bow before us, and the world will follow." VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__050__M__1
TT 13749 "You have so little faith..." VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__070__M__1
TT 13750 "But you keep... fucking... arguing with me!" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__080__M__1
TT 13751 "Anyone else?" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__100__M__1
TT 13752 "Fine. Let's begin. The blood will show the Child the way to the chapel." VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__110__M__1
TT 13753 "Dear Diaz here has the honor of starting it." VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__115__M__1
TT 13754 "No... It's too early... That's too early!" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__490_ENTER_FORT2__210__M__1
TT 13755 "Move! Quicker!" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__490_ENTER_FORT2__220__M__1
TT 13756 "Breach!" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__490_ENTER_FORT2__260__M__1
TT 13757 "I'm going to the chapel! I'll close the bloodline!" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__490_ENTER_FORT2__280__M__1
TT 13758 "What the hell were you doing in there?" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE__010__M__1
TT 13759 "This place is sacred!" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE__020__M__1
TT 13760 "You..." VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE__040__M__1
TT 13761 "It's you!... You've answered my call! Did you like my offering?" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE__050__M__1
TT 13762 "I can help you rule! I've got men! Slaves!" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE__060__M__1
TT 13763 "For you! The Countess, she calls herself a mother but... you need no mother... You need servants!" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE__080__M__1
TT 13764 "You're the girl... from the painting..." VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE__100__M__1
