TT 13789 "Eight! Nine! Ten!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__115__M__1
TT 13790 "I'm cooomminnng!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__120__M__1
TT 13791 "Fair enough. Well, I'll get back to studying now." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_END__010__M__1
TT 13792 "Well, if I want to become an alchemist..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_END__030__M__1
TT 13793 "Goodness!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_END__040__M__1
TT 13794 "I'm still your mother's apprentice." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_END__050__M__1
