TT 13796 "I smell fear..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_1__030__M__1
TT 13797 "I Lucas, perfidious among the perfidious, swear to make a stew out of your toes! AND EAT IT!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_1__040__M__1
TT 13798 "Where are youuuu? I can smell your fear! Or is it... your royal bad breath?!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_2__030__M__1
TT 13799 "All kings fall, Sire!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_2__040__M__1
TT 13800 "Too easy! So... I'll give you a second chance!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_2_BEGIN__010__M__1
