TT 13803 "Fine! My black, evil heart can still enjoy the thrill of the hunt... Go! Go you fools!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_3_BEGIN__020__M__1
TT 13804 "This time, I'll only count to five!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_3_BEGIN__030__M__1
