TT 13809 "Ha..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__ONOM__ARRIVAL_RUINS__020__M__1
TT 13810 "Ah!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__ONOM__CART_SQUEEZE_THROUGH__040__M__1
TT 13811 "Onom" VO__LUCAS__CH01__ONOM__HIDESEEK_CHECK_COVER__010__M__1
TT 13812 "Onom" VO__LUCAS__CH01__ONOM__HIDESEEK_CHECK_COVER__010__M__2
TT 13813 "Onom" VO__LUCAS__CH01__ONOM__HIDESEEK_CHECK_COVER__010__M__3
TT 13814 "Onom" VO__LUCAS__CH01__ONOM__HIDESEEK_CHECK_COVER__010__M__4
TT 13815 "Bloody brambles!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__010_OPENING__090__M__1
TT 13816 "You're going too fast for me.." VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__010_OPENING__095__M__1
TT 13817 "Doesn't he ever get tired? I really should get back to studying..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__010_OPENING__200__M__1
TT 13818 "onom" VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__010_OPENING_ONOM__080__M__1
TT 13819 "onom" VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__010_OPENING_ONOM__090__M__1
TT 13820 "onom" VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__010_OPENING_ONOM__110__M__1
TT 13821 "Did you sleep well?" VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__035_CART__006__M__1
TT 13822 "It's probably just a lack of salt in your blood." VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__035_CART__040__M__1
TT 13823 "You know, we're going to meet a great alchemist there from the Order! They know the Macula very well. They've been studying it for centuries." VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__035_CART__070__M__1
TT 13824 "They will. The Macula's not just in Hugo's blood, it concerns everybody, and it can change everything." VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__035_CART__110__M__1
TT 13825 "Hello..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__040_CONSEQUENCES__065__M__1
TT 13826 "He's still breathing." VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__050_ONCE_AGAIN__050__M__1
TT 13827 "It's the shock..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__RTC__050_ONCE_AGAIN__060__M__1
TT 13828 "Oh... I'm going to be sick..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__2ND_SYMBOL__020__M__1
TT 13829 "I... I need help! They're coming after me!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ACROSS__010__M__1
TT 13830 "For now!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ACROSS__030__M__1
TT 13831 "All right. Be fast. Be brave, and don't fall this time." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ACROSS_COMING__010__M__1
TT 13832 "Too late for that!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ACROSS_COMING__030__M__1
TT 13833 "Oh goodness, they're so, so close..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ACROSS_RATS__010__M__1
TT 13834 "You mean, the bite?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_DISPENS_AFTER__020__M__1
TT 13835 "The real question is—will it stop the rats? I don't know yet." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_DISPENS_AFTER__040__M__1
TT 13836 "If they're here..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_DISPENS_AFTER__060__M__1
TT 13837 "You smell that?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_DISPENS_INTRO__040__M__1
TT 13838 "What is this place? A hospital?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_DISPENS_INTRO__060__M__1
TT 13839 "No wonder they all fell ill." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_DISPENS_INTRO__080__M__1
TT 13840 "You were pretty discreet back there..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_DISPENS_SKILL_TUTO__010__M__1
TT 13841 "You didn't leave much alive back there..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_DISPENS_SKILL_TUTO__025__M__1
TT 13842 "The archer..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_GROUND_BRIDGE__020__M__1
TT 13843 "Careful... If they know we're here..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_GROUND_FIRSTBLOOD__020__M__1
TT 13844 "He's smarter than them..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_GROUND_INTRO__020__M__1
TT 13845 "You're right." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_GROUND_INTRO__040__M__1
TT 13846 "Try to breathe. We're making progress." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_GROUND_LEFT__020__M__1
TT 13847 "Soldiers turned bad. That doesn't sound good." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_INTRO__090__M__1
TT 13848 "Be careful." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_ENCOUNT_UP_ARCHER__009__M__1
TT 13849 "It's a massacre..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_PP_CART_PUSH__020__M__1
TT 13850 "It's still going on in Guyenne. It's already spreading." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_PP_CART_PUSH__050__M__1
TT 13851 "It wouldn't have changed a thing." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_PP_CART_PUSH__070__M__1
TT 13852 "There's some sort of... half-cart here... But it's not high enough... I think they were moving the bodies with it." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_PP_CART_UP__010__M__1
TT 13853 "Ha... It's full of bodies..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_PP_CART_UP__030__M__1
TT 13854 "Up there... Looks like it leads back inside..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_PP_INTRO_HELPER__010__M__1
TT 13855 "They think he's a doctor!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_PP_INTRO2__020__M__1
TT 13856 "The symbol! He's in that tower! He has to be!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_TOWER__020__M__1
TT 13857 "It's the Order. A high magister would just... live in the high tower, no?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_TOWER__040__M__1
TT 13858 "There's so many dead already... like it's... one step ahead of us." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_UP_HOMES__020__M__1
TT 13859 "Look... I think they were keeping count of the dead." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARCADES_UP_KNIFE__005__M__1
TT 13860 "A makeshift chapel... Do you... want to pray? If you think it could help..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_COMMUNE_CHAPEL__010__M__1
TT 13861 "Whoever planted it won't see it grow." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_COMMUNE_FLOWER__020__M__1
TT 13862 "It suits you." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_COMMUNE_FLOWER__040__M__1
TT 13863 "A vegetable garden... Oh, look at that!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_COMMUNE_FLOWER_CALL__010__M__1
TT 13864 "It looks like the safest place anyway." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_COMMUNE_GALLERY__020__M__1
TT 13865 "This place actually seemed pretty nice..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_COMMUNE_SQUARE__010__M__1
TT 13866 "Let's hope it doesn't mean they found him..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_COMMUNE_START__020__M__1
TT 13867 "We're almost there!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_FIELD_AFTER_NEAR__020__M__1
TT 13868 "He really is in the tower!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_FIELD_INTRO__010__M__1
TT 13869 "Yes, we must get Magister Vaudin out before their chief arrives!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_FIELD_INTRO__030__M__1
TT 13870 "They're getting out!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_FIELD_RATS_HEROES__010__M__1
TT 13871 "That was horrible... Thank you." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_REUNITED_INTRO__010__M__1
TT 13872 "Yes!... Oh! Look!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_AMICIA_MOVES__010__M__1
TT 13873 "That wall's a door! It's so archaic!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_DONE__010__M__1
TT 13874 "That's an entrance hall..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_INTRO__010__M__1
TT 13875 "I see no door. But these sorts of iron bells. Look, they bear planet symbols. And here, the Sun sits in their center. The order of the planets is not right." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_INTRO__030__M__1
TT 13876 "There are locks for a key under each bell. It's one big mechanism!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_INTRO__050__M__1
TT 13877 "I think the key makes each bell pivot, but your sling may do the trick. Let's start from the left!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_INTRO__070__M__1
TT 13878 "That's it, Jupiter!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_JUPITER_AMICIA__010__M__1
TT 13879 "Jupiter's symbol looks like a Z. Like for Zeus." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_JUPITER_HELPER__020__M__1
TT 13880 "To Jupiter's right is Mars. The god of war." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_MARS_HELPER__010__M__1
TT 13881 "It's a shield crossed by a spear." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_MARS_HELPER__020__M__1
TT 13882 "Mars should be a circle with a line going through it." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_MARS_HELPER__030__M__1
TT 13883 "The last one is Mercury. God of commerce." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_MERCURY_HELPER__010__M__1
TT 13884 "He carries a staff with two snakes intertwined." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_MERCURY_HELPER__020__M__1
TT 13885 "Mercury's symbol is two snakes intertwined." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_MERCURY_HELPER__030__M__1
TT 13886 "From left to right the correct order is... Jupiter, Mars, the Sun, Venus and Mercury." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_PUZZLEPLAN__010__M__1
TT 13887 "Yes!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_VENUS_AMICIA__020__M__1
TT 13888 "Now, Venus is the first to the right of the sun." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_VENUS_HELPER__010__M__1
TT 13889 "It's shaped like a necklace." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_VENUS_HELPER__020__M__1
TT 13890 "Look for a circle with a line going down." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_TOWER_VENUS_HELPER__030__M__1
TT 13891 "We're going down again?!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_UP_AFTERDOOR__010__M__1
TT 13892 "It's a joke..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_UP_AFTERDOOR__030__M__1
TT 13893 "Your mother is with him. He should be fine." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_UP_AFTERDOOR__050__M__1
TT 13894 "Maybe we'll get out closer to that tower?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_UP_VAUDIN__010__M__1
TT 13895 "I can't wait to hear Magister Vaudin's plan about this." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_UP_VAUDIN__020__M__1
TT 13896 "It will be." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARENA_UP_VAUDIN__040__M__1
TT 13897 "I'm waiting for your go!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ARMS_READY__020__M__1
TT 13898 "Rails in the walls... It looks like an elevator! It could be a way out!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BACKSTAGE_ENTRANCE__020__M__1
TT 13899 "But he's dressed as one." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BANDITS__011__M__1
TT 13900 "Amicia, he'll see us..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BANDITS__040__M__1
TT 13901 "Embers... There's a brazier over there!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_BRASERO_HELPER__040__M__1
TT 13902 "Wow... All right..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_FALL_CROSSING__020__M__1
TT 13903 "I knew it!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_FALL_LUCASFALLS__030__M__1
TT 13904 "No! I'm surrounded!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_FALL_LUCASFALLS__050__M__1
TT 13905 "Yes!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_FALL_LUCASFALLS__070__M__1
TT 13906 "Of course it had to happen to me..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_FALL_LUCASFALLS__080__M__1
TT 13907 "Really? A beam?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_FALL_START__010__M__1
TT 13908 "Yes... I... I need to breathe..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_INTRO_RATS__010__M__1
TT 13909 "You think we can get out of this?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_INTRO_RATS__060__M__1
TT 13910 "Look! They are climbing!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM1_CLIMB__020__M__1
TT 13911 "This is so bad..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM1_CLIMB__040__M__1
TT 13912 "My materials... I lost all of it in the fall..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM1_FURTHER__010__M__1
TT 13913 "Yes... Please, don't drop that torch..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM1_FURTHER__030__M__1
TT 13914 "I can't believe we're leaving the torch behind." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM1_TORCHHOLD__030__M__1
TT 13915 "It should work! Time to light it up!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_BRASEROFREE__010__M__1
TT 13916 "Good. One brazier at a time." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_BRASEROFURTHER__010__M__1
TT 13917 "The lock on that chain looks weak..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_BRASEROLIGHTUP__020__M__1
TT 13918 "That brazier up there..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_BRASEROOFF__010__M__1
TT 13919 "Yes! Well done!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_EXIT__005__M__1
TT 13920 "There's a ladder!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_SPOTLADDER__020__M__1
TT 13921 "What do we do?!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_START__020__M__1
TT 13922 "Quick now." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_STICKFIRST__009__M__1
TT 13923 "We really must get to higher ground..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_STICKFIRST__010__M__1
TT 13924 "For now..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_STICKFIRST__030__M__1
TT 13925 "It will burn fast..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_WHERE__009__M__1
TT 13926 "Yes. Very straight." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_WHERE__011__M__1
TT 13927 "Yes. Nothing will stop them from getting out..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BASE_ROOM2_WHERE__030__M__1
TT 13928 "Like... pieces of meat..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__BIG_CART_DEAD_END__020__M__1
TT 13929 "Cages... They had other beasts in there." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CAGES_LODGE__020__M__1
TT 13930 "It's all right, I'll stay here. You can go manage the other one." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CANCEL_LUCAS_NOTREADY__010__M__1
TT 13931 "I need light here!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CANT_LIGHT_BRASIER__010__M__1
TT 13932 "I'll give you a hand." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CART_SPOT__020__M__1
TT 13933 "Thanks but... I need one that's not lit! It'll be safer!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CATCH_FLAM_STICK__010__M__1
TT 13934 "There are our cranks: up there, under the arches!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CENTRAL_LIFT_CRANK__010__M__1
TT 13935 "We're done..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CHASE_BURST__020__M__1
TT 13936 "Come! Quick!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CHASE_DOOR__005__M__1
TT 13937 "Help me!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CHASE_DOOR__020__M__1
TT 13938 "Yes! Some spilled on these planks. The chest up there might contain more! Fresh sulfur would be perfect!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CHEST_SPOT_SMITHY__020__M__1
TT 13939 "Erm? You hear that? That might be the brake breaking!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CLIMB_QUICK__010__M__1
TT 13940 "What happened?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CRANK_DROP_INCOMPLETE__020__M__1
TT 13941 "I can't..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CRANK_USE_ALONE__025__M__1
TT 13942 "That's what the crank on the other side is for! You need two people!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CRANK_USE_ALONE__040__M__1
TT 13943 "I'll wait for your go!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CRANK_USE_ALONE__070__M__1
TT 13944 "There are millions of them!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CROSSING_RATS_TORCH__020__M__1
TT 13945 "How?! How can there be so many already?!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__CROSSING_RATS_TORCH__030__M__1
TT 13946 "Ha... I... can't get used to it..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__DEAD_FAMILY__010__M__1
TT 13947 "You did well..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__DYING_WOMAN__070__M__1
TT 13948 "I read about this... It's an elephant! From Africa! Romans used them during circus games!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ELEPHANT_REMAINS__020__M__1
TT 13949 "This is... surreal." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ELEPHANT_REMAINS__040__M__1
TT 13950 "A crank..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ELEVATOR_LEVER__010__M__1
TT 13951 "Huh... On your go." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ELVATR_CART__010__M__1
TT 13952 "You're doing all right?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ELVATR_CRANK_USE__010__M__1
TT 13953 "Can I help?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ELVATR_CRANK_USE__020__M__1
TT 13954 "The tower's not that far! As soon as we find Vaudin, he'll..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ELVATR_POSITIONING__020__M__1
TT 13955 "Hey! One thing at a time!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ELVATR_POSITIONING__040__M__1
TT 13956 "You're not that heavy." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ELVATR_WITH_AMICIA__020__M__1
TT 13957 "Look, over there... Another symbol!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ENTER_ENCOUNTER__020__M__1
TT 13958 "I've seen no signs of attack..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ENTER_ENCOUNTER__040__M__1
TT 13959 "We'd need a preservative agent, like... alcohol... Maybe in that chest!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__ENTER_STOCKS__020__M__1
TT 13960 "Good. But it won't be enough." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__FIRST_HAM_SHOOT__010__M__1
TT 13961 "You're sure about this?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__FIRST_KILL__010__M__1
TT 13962 "Amicia, you should come see this. I think you'll like it." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__FLOWER_NO_LEAVE__010__M__1
TT 13963 "He's here." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__FOUND_HIM_2__010__M__1
TT 13964 "Huh... Oh... What the hell?!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__GATE_PASS_1__010__M__1
TT 13965 "It looks safe!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__HAM_SHOOT__009__M__1
TT 13966 "They still look like they haven't eaten in a million years." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__HAM_SHOOT__020__M__1
TT 13967 "What do we do?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__HIDDEN_HELPER__011__M__1
TT 13968 "Ready to come inside?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__HOUSE_FINAL_LUCAS__010__M__1
TT 13969 "Yes... Home... I haven't said that word in a while." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__HOUSE_LUCASCHAT__010__M__1
TT 13970 "We must get out of here..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__HUNGRY_PIGGY__020__M__1
TT 13971 "In such a packed place, locked down... The bite probably took them all." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IDLE_BODIES__030__M__1
TT 13972 "They even had crops..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IDLE_CROPS__010__M__1
TT 13973 "Same old story..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IDLE_CROPS__030__M__1
TT 13974 "Be careful or we're dead anyway..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IDLE_ENCNTR_GROUND_1__020__M__1
TT 13975 "This is unbelievable..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IDLE_ENCNTR_GROUND_2__010__M__1
TT 13976 "Don't know. Daylight will slow them down, but..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IDLE_ENCNTR_GROUND_2__030__M__1
TT 13977 "They'll get out, for sure." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IDLE_ENCNTR_GROUND_2__050__M__1
TT 13978 "She'll deal with it. She's strong." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IDLE_ENCOUNTER_2__020__M__1
TT 13979 "Wait! There are clay pots lying around... Take one! It could concentrate the effect of an Ignifer and release it on impact!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNI_NO_POT__010__M__1
TT 13980 "Throw it to make a brief fire! It'll get us across, but we'll have to be quick!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNI_POT_READY__020__M__1
TT 13981 "Yes! Move!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNI_POT_THROW__020__M__1
TT 13982 "Pretty easy... You just need a pot." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNI_SUCCESS__020__M__1
TT 13983 "That clay pot you have... it could concentrate the effect of an Ignifer and release it on impact! Go on, try!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNI_WITH_POT__010__M__1
TT 13984 "Throw it on those rats, Amicia! We need to reach the fire behind!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNI_WRONG_THROW__010__M__1
TT 13985 "Good. We have sulfur and alcohol. It's one of the best basis for an Ignifer. Highly reactive. Mix them together!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNIFER_CRAFT__010__M__1
TT 13986 "It's a life saver." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNIFER_CRAFT__030__M__1
TT 13987 "Shoot it at those embers with your sling, and... well, hope that it works..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNIFER_DONE__020__M__1
TT 13988 "Wow!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNIFER_USE__020__M__1
TT 13989 "That was HIGHLY reactive indeed..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNIFER_USE__040__M__1
TT 13990 "I think I've seen other cranks around." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__IGNIFER_USE__070__M__1
TT 13991 "Sure." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__INTERACT_LIFT__020__M__1
TT 13992 "Yes! That's good! Very good! Come back!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__INTRCT_CHEST_STOCKS__020__M__1
TT 13993 "I can't believe it!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__INTRCT_LIFT__020__M__1
TT 13994 "I think he's just being discreet. The Order works like this." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__INVEST_DOWN_WHERETO__020__M__1
TT 13995 "Hello, excuse me, would you know the whereabouts of Magister Vaudin?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__INVEST_GUARD__010__M__1
TT 13996 "Thank you..." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__INVEST_GUARD__030__M__1
TT 13997 "Here, a town guard. I'll ask him." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__INVEST_GUARD_INTRO__010__M__1
TT 13998 "I should have known... Of course he doesn't go by his Order's title publicly!" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__INVEST_GUARD_OUTRO__020__M__1
TT 13999 "Thank you." VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__INVEST_HERBORIST_GUARDHELP__030__M__1
TT 14000 "You're sure you remember where this florist is?" VO__LUCAS__CH02__CHATTER__INVEST_HERBORIST_IDEA__020__M__1
