TT 14193 "The rats?" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__DEAD_BLACKSMITH__020__M__1
TT 14194 "At last..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__ENTER_SQUARE__020__M__1
TT 14195 "They could use the people's help... Killing them all is..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EVIL_SOLDIERS_IDLE__010__M__1
TT 14196 "That's... evil." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EVIL_SOLDIERS_IDLE__030__M__1
TT 14197 "We're here... Good work..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTERIOR__003__M__1
TT 14198 "So they stopped at the city walls?" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTERIOR__010__M__1
TT 14199 "I don't see any soldiers either..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTERIOR__030__M__1
TT 14200 "All right, all right! I'll... try to ask..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTERIOR__050__M__1
TT 14201 "They want that hanging carcass, right?" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTINGUIS_BAG_TUTO__005__M__1
TT 14202 "That bag... It's like the ones in the cart..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTINGUIS_BAG_TUTO__010__M__1
TT 14203 "Try hitting it with your sling!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTINGUIS_BAG_TUTO__015__M__1
TT 14204 "Saltpeter! It normally preserves meat, but it's thick enough to choke the flames." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTINGUIS_BAG_TUTO_OK__020__M__1
TT 14205 "Listen... You can use that saltpeter against them. Take this to craft some Exstinguis. It should be enough to put out that torch." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTINGUIS_TUTO_EXPLANATION__010__M__1
TT 14206 "Now shoot it at that torch, to... you know..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTINGUIS_USE__020__M__1
TT 14207 "Amicia? Take it!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTINGUIS_WAIT__010__M__1
TT 14208 "Shoot the bags, Amicia! It will blind them!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__EXTINGUISH_REMINDER__010__M__1
TT 14209 "Oh. A nice plant. Very useful." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FAKE_NIGHTSHADE__020__M__1
TT 14210 "There'll be better days." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FAKE_NIGHTSHADE__040__M__1
TT 14211 "We'd need some saltpeter..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FIRE_HAM__004__M__1
TT 14212 "We've got saltpeter outside..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FIRE_HAM__015__M__1
TT 14213 "Ha... Goodness..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FIRST_KILL_EXTINGUIS__003__M__1
TT 14214 "Well, it... worked..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FIRST_KILL_EXTINGUIS__005__M__1
TT 14215 "Disturbing." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FIRST_KILL_EXTINGUIS__008__M__1
TT 14216 "They wanted to keep their dead close." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FIRST_MEMORY__020__M__1
TT 14217 "He's home and at peace, Amicia..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FIRST_MEMORY__040__M__1
TT 14218 "Hey! There's a workbench here! You can improve your gear with it...  You should take a look right now... We don't know what awaits us." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FIRST_WORKBENCH__010__M__1
TT 14219 "Townsfolk?" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FLEEING_HOUSE__025__M__1
TT 14220 "I think it's through here..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FOLLOW_LUCAS__010__M__1
TT 14221 "You have to stop! We'll die here!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__FOLLOWING_WAVE__010__M__1
TT 14222 "Do you know where we're going?" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__GALLOWS__005__M__1
TT 14223 "Soldiers!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__GATE_PATROL__020__M__1
TT 14224 "Wait, I'm taking some. This stuff is too useful!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__GET_EXTINGUIS__020__M__1
