TT 14226 "I am!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__GET_READY__020__M__1
TT 14227 "Oh no, no, no!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__GOING_DOWN__040__M__1
TT 14228 "I know you're worried... but you should give Magister Vaudin some time." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__GOINGDOWN_RAIN_ANGER__010__M__1
TT 14229 "He's conducting tests! But he knows what he's doing. He's the most competent in this domain." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__GOINGDOWN_RAIN_ANGER__030__M__1
TT 14230 "A dream! What can we do with a dream, Amicia?" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__GOINGDOWN_RAIN_ANGER__050__M__1
TT 14231 "I care! But it's not enough anymore..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__GOINGDOWN_RAIN_ANGER__070__M__1
TT 14232 "This way's blocked..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__GOINGDOWN_RAIN_BLOCKED__010__M__1
