TT 14241 "I guess you're right." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__HELMET_RUNAWAY__080__M__1
TT 14242 "Just try to calm down! You won't make it in that state!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__HERBALIST_ANGER__010__M__1
TT 14243 "Not yet! I know what it looks like! We can still do this. We just need to find the herbalist's shop." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__HERBALIST_CONCLUSION__020__M__1
