TT 14265 "Oh no... They're heading out! Our herbalist's out there!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__HIGHER_SQUARE__020__M__1
TT 14266 "Hey, hey... We can still reach him before them." VO__LUCAS__CH03__CHATTER__HIGHER_SQUARE__040__M__1
