TT 14388 "We won't be able to pass with that soldier in the way..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__EXTINGUIS_STREET_1__010__M__1
TT 14389 "Amicia, you have to shoot the Exstinguis on the torch!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__EXTINGUIS_STREET_2__010__M__1
TT 14390 "Make sure you hit the torch..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__EXTINGUIS_TUTO_1__010__M__1
TT 14391 "Amicia, you have to shoot the Exstinguis on the torch!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__EXTINGUIS_TUTO_2__010__M__1
TT 14392 "Make sure you get both of them with the jar..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__EXTINGUISH_JAR_1__010__M__1
TT 14393 "Throw the jar right between them!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__EXTINGUISH_JAR_2__010__M__1
TT 14394 "There may be a way to break that chain to free the ballista!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__FREE_BALLISTA_1__010__M__1
TT 14395 "I think there's a lock at the end of that chain!  You could break it with your sling!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__FREE_BALLISTA_2__010__M__1
TT 14396 "Amicia, I still have some Stupefacio! I can use it, on your word!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__GUARD_1ST_REMPART_1__010__M__1
TT 14397 "I can create another cloud of smoke with that fire. Just tell me when." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__GUARD_1ST_REMPART_2__010__M__1
TT 14398 "We need to keep those rats occupied..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__HANGING_SHEEP_1__010__M__1
TT 14399 "Look up there! That's our distraction!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__HANGING_SHEEP_2__010__M__1
TT 14400 "There's a ladder... We must find a way to move the rats..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__HOUSE_CARCASSSES_1__010__M__1
TT 14401 "Amicia! Try cutting down a ham. It may be enough to distract them!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__HOUSE_CARCASSSES_2__010__M__1
TT 14402 "Ha... We'll need to put that fire out somehow..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__HOUSE_FIRE_1__010__M__1
TT 14403 "The saltpeter! We could use some to choke the flames!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__HOUSE_FIRE_2__010__M__1
TT 14404 "Hey! There's a fire already alight over by that house! We should try and find a way to reach it!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__PIG_BRASIER_1__010__M__1
TT 14405 "Look! Another brasier! By those pig carcasses! That's our way across!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__PIG_BRASIER_2__010__M__1
TT 14406 "We'll need something to reach that crank..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__REACH_BALLISTA_1__010__M__1
TT 14407 "I think this cart might be enough to get us up there!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__REACH_BALLISTA_2__010__M__1
TT 14408 "Tell me when and I'll create a distraction..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__SMOKE_TUTO_1__010__M__1
TT 14409 "Give me a signal and I'll get us out of here..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__SMOKE_TUTO_2__010__M__1
TT 14410 "The cranks should be up there..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__HELPER__TO_CRANK__010__M__1
TT 14411 "Ah!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__ONOM__CART_ROLL__020__M__1
TT 14412 "*Cough cough*" VO__LUCAS__CH03__ONOM__CART_ROLL__035__M__1
TT 14413 "Coming!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__112_CLOSEDDOOR__020__M__1
TT 14414 "Of course." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__112_CLOSEDDOOR__110__M__1
TT 14415 "No, they're going in... What do we do?" VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST__010__M__1
TT 14416 "Hey..." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST__020__M__1
TT 14417 "You're not alright." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST__040__M__1
TT 14418 "No you're not, you're not even breathing right now." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST__060__M__1
TT 14419 "I know... Listen, the Count's soldiers are going to seize everything. We've got to get the nightshade before they do. I have to." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST__080__M__1
TT 14420 "You're in no state to do this. I'm going. I'll sneak in. I can do it." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST__100__M__1
TT 14421 "I will run. It's not my first time." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST__120__M__1
TT 14422 "Stop! Let me go!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST__132__M__1
TT 14423 "Ah!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 14424 "onom" VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__120_JAIL_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 14425 "Oh so that's all you have to say!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__121_JAIL__030__M__1
TT 14426 "Come on, you can do better than that! You have a whole garrison here! Why don't you really let yourself go?!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__121_JAIL__040__M__1
TT 14427 "NO!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__121_JAIL__060__M__1
TT 14428 "Do you see the situation we're in? We were just supposed to get herbs. How do you think Hugo feels right now without them? How will he feel when his sister is hanged?" VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__121_JAIL__070__M__1
TT 14429 "Yes, because this world hurts, and it keeps hurting, and you want to hurt it back... But it's a fight you cannot win... Amicia... You are not them. You are a De Rune." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__121_JAIL__100__M__1
TT 14430 "That's us... Listen." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__121_JAIL__110__M__1
TT 14431 "This thing works with fire. I'll tell you when I'm ready." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__121_JAIL__130__M__1
TT 14432 "It worked!" VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__122_EXIT_RUN__030__M__1
TT 14433 "The herbalist was out when we arrived. We had to wait." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__122_GUILT__030__M__1
TT 14434 "But we have everything." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__122_GUILT__040__M__1
TT 14435 "Yes, it's the butchers' district. It's the shortest way to the herbalist." VO__LUCAS__CH03__RTC__ENTER_BUTCHER_DISTRICT__020__M__1
TT 14436 "It's homemade! Basic alchemy!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__1ST_BASIN_LIGHT__040__M__1
TT 14437 "He doesn't seem to know about our escape." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__1ST_BASIN_SHOULD_POUR__030__M__1
TT 14438 "Light it up, Amicia!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__3RD_BASIN_SHOULD_LIGHT__020__M__1
TT 14439 "Don't panic... We have resin... It just needs that diluent up there and we get tar!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__A_WAY_OUT__010__M__1
TT 14440 "That barrel is pretty high though..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__A_WAY_OUT__030__M__1
TT 14441 "This isn't possible..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__AFTER_ATTACK__010__M__1
TT 14442 "Good!... I think you can light it up!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__ALCOHOL_DONE__010__M__1
TT 14443 "Let's see what our tar's worth..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__ALCOHOL_DONE__030__M__1
TT 14444 "Forgive us..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__AMPLIFY__010__M__1
TT 14445 "He's right! You should open the way to that second basin first!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__AMPLIFY_LUCKY_USES__030__M__1
TT 14446 "Throw tar on that fire!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__AMPLIFY_TUTO_MISS__010__M__1
TT 14447 "Come on, throw tar in that basin!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__AMPLIFY_TUTO_MISS__020__M__1
TT 14448 "There should be a way..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__AMPLIFY_TUTORIAL__020__M__1
TT 14449 "That's... well, yes, that will work..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__AMPLIFY_TUTORIAL__040__M__1
TT 14450 "My eyes..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__AMPLIFY_TUTORIAL__084__M__1
TT 14451 "That was actually pretty smart..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__AMPLIFY_TUTORIAL__122__M__1
TT 14452 "EMPTY" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__ATTACK__020__M__1
TT 14453 "We should go now, no?" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BACK_CITY__013__M__1
TT 14454 "Oh come on!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BACK_CITY__055__M__1
TT 14455 "Amicia! You could blind him! With the tar!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BACK_CITY__092__M__1
TT 14456 "Now Amicia!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BACK_CITY__100__M__1
TT 14457 "Time to meet him face-to-face?" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BEFORE_MEETING__010__M__1
TT 14458 "Follow orders?" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BEFORE_MEETING__030__M__1
TT 14459 "Red and white sail.... Right there!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BIG_BOATS__020__M__1
TT 14460 "That's why they locked the city down!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BITE__010__M__1
TT 14461 "This is... a war strategy..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BITE__020__M__1
TT 14462 "Here they are!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BOAT__010__M__1
TT 14463 "Are you all right?! I thought you were..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BOAT__020__M__1
TT 14464 "Come aboard, quick!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BOAT__040__M__1
TT 14465 "What happened to Hugo?!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BOAT__060__M__1
TT 14466 "I think... they've started purging the lower districts first. The house is in the upper part of town. There's still time." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__BODIES_REACTIONS_1__020__M__1
TT 14467 "Joseph broke a jar of tar! It reacted with the torch!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__CAREFUL__020__M__1
TT 14468 "Yes... Do what you must. We need that boat at all costs." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__CAREFUL__040__M__1
TT 14469 "I think... it's too late. They're here..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__CART_PULL__022__M__1
TT 14470 "I think... I know what happened to this place..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__CART_STUCK__040__M__1
TT 14471 "We're here." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__CHARIOT_WHAT__010__M__1
TT 14472 "Wait! I think they... experimented with some ingredients here and... Yes, that could work! I'll throw them to you!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__COMPONENTS_THROW__010__M__1
TT 14473 "Here! Say when you're ready to catch!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__COMPONENTS_THROW__030__M__1
TT 14474 "You've got resin and alcohol now. Mix them!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__COMPONENTS_THROW__050__M__1
TT 14475 "These people..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__DID_IT_DOOR__020__M__1
TT 14476 "Yes..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__DID_IT_DOOR__040__M__1
TT 14477 "Remember the locked district..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__DOWN_PATROL__060__M__1
TT 14478 "I don't know..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__DOWN_PATROL__080__M__1
TT 14479 "Wow... What a mess..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__ENTRY_DEPOT__005__M__1
TT 14480 "Tar... makes your head spin..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__ENTRY_DEPOT__009__M__1
TT 14481 "No... but they were here. Look at this." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__ENTRY_DEPOT__020__M__1
TT 14482 "A tar workshop... they must use it to seal boat hulls." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__ENTRY_DEPOT__040__M__1
TT 14483 "We're out of the harbour—why are there soldiers here?" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FIRE_AFAR__010__M__1
TT 14484 "That was close..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FIRS_STEPS_JETTY__010__M__1
TT 14485 "Soldiers..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FLAMES__020__M__1
TT 14486 "A gentian, I think... I'm sure he'll love it." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FLOWER__030__M__1
TT 14487 "He loves anything that comes from you..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FLOWER__050__M__1
TT 14488 "Wow!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FOOTBRIDGE_MOVE__010__M__1
TT 14489 "Come back to the basins!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FOOTBRIDGE_MOVE__020__M__1
TT 14490 "The diluent... I see... It's alcohol, of course!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FOOTBRIDGE_MOVE__040__M__1
TT 14491 "Good! Hold it until I tell you..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FOOTBRIDGE_SET__010__M__1
TT 14492 "I'm ready!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FOOTBRIDGE_SET__030__M__1
TT 14493 "That building on the left looks safer..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__FRONT_HANGAR__020__M__1
TT 14494 "Hopefully there's a side way to pass that gate." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__GATE__090__M__1
TT 14495 "We'll know way too soon..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__GATE__110__M__1
TT 14496 "Where's Joseph's boat?!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__GATE_END__010__M__1
TT 14497 "If he's docked already..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__GATE_END__030__M__1
TT 14498 "Let's see... These ropes make the platform move. Operators climbed on it with that ladder, behind the grating." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__GEAR_SPOTTED__010__M__1
TT 14499 "This city's going to fall into chaos. People won't go down that easily. They'll fight back." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__IDLE_FIRE_ZONE_3__010__M__1
TT 14500 "This stench... The tar covered it but..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__IDLE_FIRE_ZONE_4__010__M__1
TT 14501 "Mercenaries only believe in money." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__IDLE_FIRE_ZONE_6__030__M__1
TT 14502 "Oh! All right, that works too! Now come on! Ignite that second pool there! It's tar!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__IGNIFER_OK__010__M__1
TT 14503 "Yes! Turn it all the way!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__INTERACT_CRANK__010__M__1
TT 14504 "On my way!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__INTERACT_LADDER__020__M__1
TT 14505 "Perfect! Now throw a pot of tar between these two big basins..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__JAR_DONE__020__M__1
TT 14506 "That won't work! Here! Craft another one! If you fail and need one more, just ask me! But... please focus!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__JAR_FAIL__010__M__1
TT 14507 "How does he do that?" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__JOSEPH_3RD_KILL__010__M__1
TT 14508 "That's crazy..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__JOSEPH_4TH_KILL__020__M__1
TT 14509 "One more down! He never misses..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__JOSEPH_5TH_KILL__010__M__1
TT 14510 "Do something, Amicia! Joseph can't shoot!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__JOSEPH_NO_HELP__010__M__1
TT 14511 "Well spotted!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__LOCK_SHOT__010__M__1
TT 14512 "I know... but it shouldn't take us long." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__LOCK_SHOT__030__M__1
TT 14513 "I've made it!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__LUCAS_ARRIVED__010__M__1
TT 14514 "All right!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__LUCAS_SHOULD_JOIN__020__M__1
TT 14515 "Amicia! I'm blocked!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__LUCAS_SHOULD_JOIN__030__M__1
TT 14516 "Amicia, we should finish this basin before moving on to the next one." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__LUCAS_WONT_MOVE_FOOTBRIGE__010__M__1
TT 14517 "Let's hope Marseille is different..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__MARKET_STEALTH__020__M__1
TT 14518 "Joseph's boat..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__MARKET_VISTA__010__M__1
TT 14519 "Look at that fire in the middle..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__MID_ZONE__005__M__1
TT 14520 "I smell tar!... So this is what they've been doing with it!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__MID_ZONE__020__M__1
TT 14521 "Amicia! Wait! The second basin isn't lit yet!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__MOVE_2ND_GATE_EARLY__010__M__1
TT 14522 "Lord, we're here... Please, be there, Joseph. Please, please!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__NEAR_LAST_DOOR__020__M__1
TT 14523 "Yes... Phew..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__NEAR_SQUEEZE__020__M__1
TT 14524 "Amicia, you should get on that footbridge to manage the diluent. I'll handle the crank to get it moving!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__NEXT_2ND_BASIN__030__M__1
TT 14525 "It smells like tar! If it is, it's highly flammable! Try setting it on fire!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__OIL_TUTO__022__M__1
TT 14526 "I... didn't expect that..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__OIL_TUTO__040__M__1
TT 14527 "Neither did they..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__OIL_TUTO__050__M__1
TT 14528 "Are you... all right?" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__OUTSIDE3_INTRO__010__M__1
TT 14529 "I... I wanted to tell you, but—" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__OUTSIDE3_INTRO__030__M__1
TT 14530 "I didn't know Magister Vaudin would tell you like this!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__OUTSIDE3_INTRO__050__M__1
TT 14531 "Fine..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__OUTSIDE3_INTRO__070__M__1
TT 14532 "What happened here?!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__OVER_GATE__020__M__1
TT 14533 "What are they doing?" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__PASSAGE__010__M__1
TT 14534 "Good. Shall I handle the reservoir part? What d'you think?" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__PLANNING__010__M__1
TT 14535 "The rats destroyed the rest of the pontoon..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__PONTOON_CHEST__005__M__1
TT 14536 "Our boat should be straight ahead, right?" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__POST_DEPOT_DEBRIEF__005__M__1
TT 14537 "Listen Amicia... about Hugo... I was stuck between Magister Vaudin and your mother and... I have no excuse. I was wrong." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__POST_DEPOT_DEBRIEF__020__M__1
TT 14538 "We'll do what's right." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__POST_DEPOT_DEBRIEF__040__M__1
TT 14539 "Yes! Let's make that tar!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__POURING_ALCOHOL__010__M__1
TT 14540 "Pouring!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__POURING_ALCOHOL__012__M__1
TT 14541 "No! I'm improvising!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__POURING_ALCOHOL__030__M__1
TT 14542 "That brazier... it can be pushed..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__PUSHABLE_BRAZIER__010__M__1
TT 14543 "The tar did... this stuff works miracles." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__PUZZLE_END__010__M__1
TT 14544 "No need for that..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__PUZZLE_END__030__M__1
TT 14545 "That fire... It's not wood burning..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__PYRE__010__M__1
TT 14546 "It's bodies..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__PYRE__015__M__1
TT 14547 "Here they are..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__QUAI__065__M__1
TT 14548 "Well, that's one step!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__RAT_BURST__020__M__1
TT 14549 "Amicia, the Order will have special buildings in Marseille... equipment, and people!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__RATS_THINKING__010__M__1
TT 14550 "Ha..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__RATS_THINKING__030__M__1
TT 14551 "As soon as we reach Joseph, we must hurry back to the house..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__REGION__010__M__1
TT 14552 "I didn't think they could do worse than the Inquisition." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__REGION__020__M__1
TT 14553 "I hope our pilot is too." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SHORE__030__M__1
TT 14554 "You didn't really give him a chance..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SIMON_DEAD_SAD__010__M__1
TT 14555 "Yes..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SIMON_END__020__M__1
TT 14556 "He seems... Reasonable." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SIMON_GO_TO_CRANK__010__M__1
TT 14557 "Good for us, then." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SIMON_GO_TO_CRANK__040__M__1
TT 14558 "If the Count had been here, maybe... He'd have been reasonable. We could have asked for a meeting and..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SOLUTION__010__M__1
TT 14559 "It's too late anyway. This is the epicentre. It can only spread now." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SOLUTION__030__M__1
TT 14560 "It probably came from China... I've never seen so much... there's a fortune here..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SOUVENIR__020__M__1
TT 14561 "Do you think it's same, in China? Do you think they have... the rats too?" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SOUVENIR__035__M__1
TT 14562 "We have to stop this..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SOUVENIR__040__M__1
TT 14563 "So many... people must be... dying right now... But it's... so silent..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_TWO__010__M__1
TT 14564 "You keep thinking you have control over this... But we're merely grains of sand in the Macula's path." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_TWO__030__M__1
TT 14565 "I'm just saying... you need to stop feeling guilty." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_TWO__050__M__1
TT 14566 "Very well." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_TWO__070__M__1
TT 14567 "That's depressing." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__SOUVENIR_UP__020__M__1
TT 14568 "I know... The island, the Macula waking up, the Order... It's too much." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__STAIRS__010__M__1
TT 14569 "Well, it's of little help." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__STAIRS__030__M__1
TT 14570 "You're not. I'm here." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__STAIRS__050__M__1
TT 14571 "It looks good! Light it up!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__TAR_AIM_OK__010__M__1
TT 14572 "Yes!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__TAR_SHOOT__011__M__1
TT 14573 "Yes! That last pool here is already full of tar!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__TAR_SHOOT__020__M__1
TT 14574 "You... asked me to ask Magister Vaudin about the island. The fresco, in his lodge." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__TO_LOOT__020__M__1
TT 14575 "He said it's “just” a symbol." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__TO_LOOT__040__M__1
TT 14576 "I heard this city used to be a commercial door to the Mediterranean sea..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__TO_SOUVENIR__010__M__1
TT 14577 "Don't go any further, Amicia!" VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__TREMORS__030__M__1
TT 14578 "This lockdown is going to get them all killed." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__UPSTAIRS__020__M__1
TT 14579 "Look at that wall..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__UPSTAIRS__040__M__1
TT 14580 "Let's get closer..." VO__LUCAS__CH04__CHATTER__UPSTAIRS__060__M__1
