TT 16382 "EMPTY" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__DEATH_OFFSCREEN__216__M__1
TT 16383 "May his reborn flame light our path!" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__FESTIVAL_BAR__030__M__1
TT 16384 "Yes! The feast is going to be magnificent!" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__FESTIVAL_BAR__060__M__1
TT 16385 "Don't be scared! They much prefer their olive leaves to little children." VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__GOATS__020__M__1
TT 16386 "You're heading to the Child's sanctuary?" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__GOATS__070__M__1
TT 16387 "I'm afraid you're too late. They closed the gate, as you can see. For the ceremony." VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__GOATS__090__M__1
TT 16388 "Well... That goat path to the side will take you closer. But you'll have to look from afar. The Count and Countess are up there and... the guards are on edge since yesterday's mess. They won't take kindly to uninvited guests." VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__GOATS__107__M__1
TT 16389 "By the way, if you stumble on Tramontane, please send her back here. She's one of my goats." VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__GOATS__110__M__1
TT 16390 "Good luck then!" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__GOATS__130__M__1
TT 16391 "Shh... Are you trying to scare my fish away?" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_FOREST_FISHERMAN__010__M__1
TT 16392 "The plants look good... The Child is pleased..." VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_PALACE_NPC_TIME__010__M__1
TT 16393 "Hey there!" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_FIVE__002__M__1
TT 16394 "Well, don't let me stop you..." VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_FIVE__010__M__1
TT 16395 "These youngsters, chasing rocks instead of gold..." VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_FIVE__040__M__1
TT 16396 "It's already gorgeous, dear." VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_FESTIVAL_NPC_BARN__020__M__1
TT 16397 "Hello!" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__POTTER_TALK__020__M__1
TT 16398 "It's varnish. To make it shinier for the Child!" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__POTTER_TALK__040__M__1
TT 16399 "Good-bye!" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH09__CHATTER__POTTER_TALK__080__M__1
TT 16400 "Come give me a hand with this!" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH12__CHATTER__DEFENSES__010__M__1
TT 16401 "Need a bit of help here!" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH12__CHATTER__MORE_WOOD2__010__M__1
TT 16402 "This is but a test the Child sends us. You must not lose faith." VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH12__CHATTER__PREACH__005__M__1
TT 16403 "Still your hearts! Pray to Him. Just pray." VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH12__CHATTER__PREACH__035__M__1
TT 16404 "You sure it will hold?!" VO__PEOPLE_M5__CH15__CHATTER__GATE_BARRICADE__030__M__1
