TT 16426 "Where do you want us to go?!" VO__PEOPLE_M6__CH03__CHATTER__2ND_STREET__170__M__1
TT 16427 "I can't believe they blocked the way to the arena..." VO__PEOPLE_M6__CH03__CHATTER__HALLES_RAIN_CHAT_ARENA__010__M__1
