TT 16458 "We need to get you out of the camp! Follow me closely! Try to blend in!" VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__FIRST_STEPS__010__M__1
TT 16459 "This way." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__FIRST_STEPS__020__M__1
TT 16460 "Protect these humble pilgrims on their holy journey, as they seek mercy in these times of darkness, and receive the prayers of the weakest." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__MASS__010__M__1
TT 16461 "Amen." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__MASS__020__M__1
TT 16462 "Now let us pray." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__MASS_PRAY__010__M__1
TT 16463 "My Lord, I draw nearer to you." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__MASS_PRAY__020__M__1
TT 16464 "Excuse me..." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_DISTRACT__010__M__1
TT 16465 "Have you checked that group over there? Some of them joined us recently. Not that they really look like your fugitives, but... who knows?" VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_DISTRACT__030__M__1
TT 16466 "The way's clear! Come, calmly." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_DISTRACT_OK__005__M__1
TT 16467 "You'll find a path to the sea on the other side of this pen." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_GOODBYE__010__M__1
TT 16468 "Be careful..." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_GOODBYE__040__M__1
TT 16469 "No, but... I hope you'll make amends." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_HELP__011__M__1
TT 16470 "We're all judged, eventually." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_HELP__021__M__1
TT 16471 "No..." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__PROBLEM__010__M__1
TT 16472 "Hide under that cart before they see you! I'll handle them..." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__PROBLEM__030__M__1
TT 16473 "Go under the cart! Quick! I'll take care of them!" VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__PROBLEM_HELPER__010__M__1
TT 16474 "Slowly. There's more of them." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__SLOPE__015__M__1
TT 16475 "Careful." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__CHATTER__SOLDIER_INTERROGATION__005__M__1
TT 16476 "Oh... Hello!" VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__RTC__240_FLAGELLANT__040__M__1
TT 16477 "And welcome. You're new here..." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__RTC__240_FLAGELLANT__050__M__1
TT 16478 "And where are you going? Not to Rome, I would assume?" VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__RTC__240_FLAGELLANT__070__M__1
TT 16479 "Not from memory, but I have an old map of the Mediterranean Sea  somewhere... Do you want to have a look?" VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__RTC__240_FLAGELLANT__090__M__1
TT 16480 "What's going on?..." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__RTC__240_FLAGELLANT__110__M__1
TT 16481 "I know a guilty look when I see one... but whatever you've done, I won't give up a child. Come with me." VO__PILGRIM_LEADER__CH06__RTC__240_FLAGELLANT__295__M__1
