TT 16557 "Watch the houses! Make sure no one leaves! The more dead we have in the streets, the more damn rats we get!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__CHATTER__ANOTHER_SOLDIER_STREET__020__M__1
TT 16558 "Attention! We just caught a looter over there! There may be others! Search the area and kill on sight!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__CHATTER__HERBALIST_ENCOUNTER_START__010__M__1
TT 16559 "Stop there! We'll wait for the executioner, he must be finishing one right now." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__CHATTER__SMOKE_PRESSURE__020__M__1
TT 16560 "Behave in front of the Beast! You're cold meat now. Food for the crows. Act like it." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__CHATTER__SMOKE_PRESSURE__040__M__1
TT 16561 "You killed trained men who were trying to save our city. You've just pushed us a little closer to chaos. Your death will be slow." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__CHATTER__SMOKE_PRESSURE_IDLE__010__M__1
TT 16562 "You're possessed! But we'll choke that demon inside you." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__CHATTER__SMOKE_PRESSURE_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 16563 "What the Hell?!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__CHATTER__SMOKE_TUTO__030__M__1
TT 16564 "I can't see a damn thing!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__CHATTER__SMOKE_TUTO__060__M__1
TT 16565 "You! Stay here and patrol! Report if you see one bloody rat!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST__005__M__1
TT 16566 "The others with me! Look for any valuables! We need food, drugs... any goods!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__RTC__118_CONTROL_LOST__007__M__1
TT 16567 "I'll teach you to kill my men!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__RTC__120_JAIL__040__M__1
TT 16568 "Don't think we're done with you yet." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__RTC__120_JAIL__050__M__1
TT 16569 "onom" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__RTC__120_JAIL_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 16570 "Don't expect a quick death after what you've done! We've paid the executioner to spend a bit of time with you before you hang..." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__RTC__121_JAIL__010__M__1
TT 16571 "Get out. Your nooses are waiting." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH03__RTC__121_JAIL__140__M__1
TT 16572 "Don't think it'll be that easy!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__BLIND_RECOVER_1__010__M__1
TT 16573 "You're not getting away from me!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__BLIND_RECOVER_2__010__M__1
TT 16574 "You won't see another day!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__BLIND_RECOVER_3__010__M__1
TT 16575 "This armour has stopped worse than that!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_CROSSBOW__010__M__1
TT 16576 "Here you are!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_FIGHT__020__M__1
TT 16577 "Now, you'll PAY for your defiance! Now you'll know the bite of the Beast!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_FIGHT__050__M__1
TT 16578 "You're trapped. This is personal—you're mine now." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_FIGHT__060__M__1
TT 16579 "I'll deal with the child too... There are enough weeds in this land!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_FIGHT__090__M__1
TT 16580 "No nooses this time. I'll crush your skull!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_FIGHT__110__M__1
TT 16581 "I'm the law's arm... And I'll be its executioner!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_FIGHT__120__M__1
TT 16582 "Pathetic..." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_FUTILE__010__M__1
TT 16583 "Lost your touch?!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_FUTILE__020__M__1
TT 16584 "You knew this was coming!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_IDLE_1__010__M__1
TT 16585 "Stop running, you little shits!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_IDLE_2__010__M__1
TT 16586 "Your magic won't save you today!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_IGNIFER__020__M__1
TT 16587 "Some people just saw a boy and a girl crossing the camp! Extend the search!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_ORDER_FOREST__010__M__1
TT 16588 "You little brat! That won't stop me!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_RING__010__M__1
TT 16589 "I will kill you both!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_RING__040__M__1
TT 16590 "Where are you?!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_SEARCH__010__M__1
TT 16591 "Trying to hide?" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_SEARCH__020__M__1
TT 16592 "You're not getting away from me! Not in here!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_SEARCH__030__M__1
TT 16593 "Really?! You thought that toy weapon would work on me?!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_SLING__010__M__1
TT 16594 "Found you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_SPOTTED__010__M__1
TT 16595 "Come here!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_SPOTTED__020__M__1
TT 16596 "There you are!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_SPOTTED__030__M__1
TT 16597 "Cheap trick! You have no honour!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_STUNNED_FIRST__010__M__1
TT 16598 "Damn witch! I'll... bash your head in!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_STUNNED_SECOND__010__M__1
TT 16599 "After them! The girl is the dangerous one! Kill her on sight!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__GORGE_ENTRY__009__M__1
TT 16600 "You filth! Come here!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__REINFORCEMENTS_DEAD__005__M__1
TT 16601 "I won't let our brothers' deaths be for nothing!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__REINFORCEMENTS_DEAD__010__M__1
TT 16602 "Any new pilgrims recently? Interlopers?" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__CHATTER__SOLDIER_INTERROGATION__010__M__1
TT 16603 "Good people!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__RTC__240_FLAGELLANT__105__M__1
TT 16604 "We're looking for a boy and a girl! The girl has killed several soldiers! She's armed and dangerous!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__RTC__240_FLAGELLANT__175__M__1
TT 16605 "By order of Count Victor of Arles, we are searching this camp... Go!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__RTC__240_FLAGELLANT__185__M__1
TT 16606 "Get out of my way!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH06__RTC__240_FLAGELLANT__195__M__1
TT 16607 "Have they found more of Arnaud's men?" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH09__CHATTER__BUILDING_CHATTER__010__M__1
TT 16608 "Bastards... Spoiling the most important time of the year." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH09__CHATTER__BUILDING_CHATTER__030__M__1
TT 16609 "Soldiers! The ceremony will start soon! Open your eyes!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH09__CHATTER__MORE_SOLDIERS__005__M__1
TT 16610 "May the Mother's voice reach the Child!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH09__CHATTER__PASSED_DOOR__030__M__1
TT 16611 "Wait here." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__BATTLE_PLAN__010__M__1
TT 16612 "Sire... She's here." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__BATTLE_PLAN__060__M__1
TT 16613 "Follow me..." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__ESCORT__010__M__1
TT 16614 "Best not to keep the Count waiting. Come." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__ESCORT__020__M__1
TT 16615 "This is no time to wander around. Follow me." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__ESCORT__030__M__1
TT 16616 "No." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__ESCORT__050__M__1
TT 16617 "Seeing you must be an urgent matter. Act with dignity in his presence. These are dark times. He's touched, like any of us." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__ESCORT__070__M__1
TT 16618 "All side entrances are locked. Use the main gate." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__GARDEN__010__M__1
TT 16619 "Protect the Countess at all cost!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__MOTHER__025__M__1
TT 16620 "Lady! The Count is waiting for you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__WAITING_1__010__M__1
TT 16621 "Lady... You have an audience with the Count!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__WAITING_2__020__M__1
TT 16622 "People are dying while we're waiting for you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__WAITING_3__030__M__1
TT 16623 "Count." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__CHATTER__WALK_OUT__020__M__1
TT 16624 "Sorry to interrupt." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__RTC__610_A_BANQUET__233__M__1
TT 16625 "The Count wants to see you." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__RTC__610_A_BANQUET__236__M__1
TT 16626 "He is the Count of Provence, my lady." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH12__RTC__610_A_BANQUET__255__M__1
TT 16627 "Nothing yet. The Count must be burying his spouse." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH13__CHATTER__ABOUT_COUNT__020__M__1
TT 16628 "That must be terrible. When you see what they do to the people they catch..." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH13__CHATTER__ABOUT_COUNT__025__M__1
TT 16629 "The Child will fix this!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH13__CHATTER__ABOUT_FUTURE__020__M__1
TT 16630 "He did it because of HER! But the Count will teach him. He'll show him the way to shine on the world!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH13__CHATTER__ABOUT_FUTURE__040__M__1
TT 16631 "It's terrible, what happened to the Count..." VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_IDLE_1__010__M__1
TT 16632 "What is that bloody thing?!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_FOG_1__010__M__1
TT 16633 "Sir! We must evacuate now!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_FOG_2__010__M__1
TT 16634 "How are you still alive?! You destroyed our island! You stole the Brighter Days from us!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_FOG_3__010__M__1
TT 16635 "I'll slay that witch myself!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_NOFOG_6__010__M__1
