TT 16746 "Someone's playing games with us! Look for them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__1
TT 16747 "Help me find who's playing us for fools!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__2
TT 16748 "Jokers are playing with us! Catch them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__3
TT 16749 "You think this is funny, do you?" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 16750 "Stop messing about!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 16751 "I know you're around here somewhere! I'll find you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 16752 "With me! Intruders!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__1
TT 16753 "Alert! Help me catch those intruders!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__2
TT 16754 "We've got company! Catch them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__3
TT 16755 "Stop right now!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 16756 "Stop there immediately!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 16757 "Who are you?! Come here!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 16758 "I'm stuck now but I'll get you soon!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__1
TT 16759 "You! You'll see when I find how to reach you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__2
TT 16760 "I'll find a way to get my hands on you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__3
TT 16761 "It's not over, I'll get to you somehow..." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__4
TT 16762 "Fine! I'm blocked now, but not forever!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__5
TT 16763 "Watch your back, I'll find a way to get to you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__6
TT 16764 "No! Someone's down!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__1
TT 16765 "Man down! Watch out!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__2
TT 16766 "He got killed! Look out!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__3
TT 16767 "The fire will root you out of the grass, believe me!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__1
TT 16768 "Try to hide in that grass now!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__2
TT 16769 "It's not a good idea to hide in the grass!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__3
TT 16770 "We've got intruders... Come with me!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__1
TT 16771 "Intruders here! Get them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__2
TT 16772 "Wake up! We've got intruders!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__3
TT 16773 "Spread out soldiers! We'll get them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__1
TT 16774 "Split up and find them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__2
TT 16775 "Let's spread out and cover the area!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__3
TT 16776 "You won't escape, you know it." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__1
TT 16777 "You've run out of choices." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__2
TT 16778 "Shouldn't have come here!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__3
TT 16779 "Something's burning!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__1
TT 16780 "The hell started this fire?" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__2
TT 16781 "How'd this fire get started?" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__3
TT 16782 "Try to die with some dignity." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__1
TT 16783 "Cheer up, we all die someday." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__2
TT 16784 "Better start praying for your soul." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__3
