TT 16970 "Found you!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__BROKE_POTS_NOISE__020__M__1
TT 16971 "The others are busy, but my bird's worth three of them! You're dead!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__BROKE_POTS_NOISE__070__M__1
TT 16972 "Finally decided to show your face?!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__DISTRACT_01__020__M__1
TT 16973 "Oh, you want to play that game?! Let's play!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__DISTRACT_02__020__M__1
TT 16974 "You'll make a mistake at some point!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__DISTRACT_03__010__M__1
TT 16975 "Come on! Get them! You useless spadger!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__DISTRACT_04__010__M__1
TT 16976 "I know you're there!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__DISTRACT_05__010__M__1
TT 16977 "Ha! It'll get you eventually! Just you wait!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__DISTRACT_08__020__M__1
TT 16978 "I know where you are! You've got nowhere to run!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__FALCON_BEGINNING__010__M__1
TT 16979 "What do you think you'll do with that?!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__NO_DAMAGE__010__M__1
TT 16980 "Your rocks won't even scratch my armour!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__NO_DAMAGE__020__M__1
TT 16981 "Go! I'll keep watch for the others!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__CHATTER__REINFORCEMENT_COUNT__020__M__1
TT 16982 "I'm... sorry, Sire..." VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH08__RTC__370_BASTARD__015__M__1
TT 16983 "Dig trenches along the ramparts and fill them with tar! Keep them burning! Any breach could make the palace fall!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH12__CHATTER__BRIEFING__010__M__1
TT 16984 "Then you're dead. Keep... them... burning!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH12__CHATTER__BRIEFING__030__M__1
TT 16985 "We'll get you, witch!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH12__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_INCOMING_2__020__M__1
TT 16986 "To me! I need every man here, right now!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH13__CHATTER__ASK_REINFORCE_1__010__M__1
TT 16987 "What are you doing?! Attack! Attack!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH13__CHATTER__ASK_REINFORCE_3__010__M__1
TT 16988 "What?! It's her! The Defiler! She has the Child! Take him away from her!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH13__CHATTER__FIRST_SHOT__020__M__1
TT 16989 "We need more men here! Don't be afraid, Child! We'll take you back to your righteous Father!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH13__CHATTER__HEAVY_DEAD__020__M__1
TT 16990 "You! Filthy wretch! Our Countess was a servant of light! And you've murdered her!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH13__CHATTER__HEAVY_INCOMING__010__M__1
TT 16991 "You've doomed this island!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH13__CHATTER__HEAVY_INCOMING__030__M__1
TT 16992 "Come on! Get them! Warn the others!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH13__CHATTER__MORE_WAVE_1__010__M__1
TT 16993 "For the Count Victor of Arles! For the Child of Embers!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH13__CHATTER__MORE_WAVE_1__030__M__1
TT 16994 "This is not just for us! This Child belongs to the world! He's our future! Fight for it!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__CH13__CHATTER__MORE_WAVE_2__010__M__1
