TT 17105 "Looks like we've got some jokers here. Find 'em now!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__1
TT 17106 "Search the area, there's some jokers nearby!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__2
TT 17107 "They're taking us for fools?! Do what it takes, catch them!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__3
TT 17108 "You think this is funny? I'll do whatever it takes to stop ya!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 17109 "Just you wait, I'll find you now." VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 17110 "You are not funny! I'll stop your little games." VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__3
