TT 17115 "Stop where you are!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 17116 "You! Too late to run away! Stay there!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 17117 "When I find a way, I'll beat you hard!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__1
TT 17118 "I'll get my hands on you, I'll find another path!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__2
TT 17119 "I will get to you!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__3
TT 17120 "I won't be stuck here forever! I'll get you!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__4
TT 17121 "Well played so far, but I'll get to you!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__5
TT 17122 "I won't give up on you! Won't be stuck here for long!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__6
TT 17123 "Damn! Man down!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__1
TT 17124 "Oh no! He's dead!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__2
TT 17125 "Shit! One of us is dead!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__3
TT 17126 "You're gonna burn!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__1
TT 17127 "I'll smoke you out, you little bastard!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__2
TT 17128 "These flames'll get you out of the grass!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__3
TT 17129 "Catch those intruders! Quick!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__1
TT 17130 "Wake up! We've got trespassers!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__2
TT 17131 "Move fast! Stop the bastards!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__3
