TT 17133 "Fan out and find them!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__2
TT 17134 "Fan out! Intruders breakin' through!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__3
TT 17135 "Say your prayers!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__1
TT 17136 "You die today!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__2
TT 17137 "Shouldn't have crossed me!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__3
TT 17138 "Flames?!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__1
TT 17139 "Fire? Can't be!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__2
TT 17140 "Come on! Now a fire?!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__3
TT 17141 "Struggling won't help you now!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__1
TT 17142 "Try not to move so much! I want a clean kill!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__2
TT 17143 "Looks like this is your last day." VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__3
TT 17144 "What happened to you? Hey! Can you hear me?!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__1
TT 17145 "Oi! Get up, stop messing around!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__2
TT 17146 "What's wrong with you? Hey!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__3
