TT 17351 "Don't know, don't care... You don't want to go out there, believe me!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH03__CHATTER__NIGHTSHADE_FOUND__102__M__1
TT 17352 "Remember to mark the houses you've cleaned with a cross! It's imperative that the bodies are taken out of the city!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH03__CHATTER__SENTINEL_SQUARE__010__M__1
TT 17353 "Same as us?" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH03__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_PATROL__020__M__1
TT 17354 "We're dead... We're dead!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__CART_PULL__030__M__1
TT 17355 "Ha..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__CART_PULLING_LOOP__010__M__1
TT 17356 "It's the steadiest I can go!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__CART_PUSH__020__M__1
TT 17357 "EMPTY" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__CART_STUCK__010__M__1
TT 17358 "It came from the pontoon! Come with me!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__FLAMES__011__M__1
TT 17359 "Hey!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__FLAMES__040__M__1
TT 17360 "Watch over the jars until we reach the other side!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__GATE__040__M__1
TT 17361 "I believe nothing. I just know bodies keep coming from the city, and we add too many of our own." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__GATE_TALK__020__M__1
TT 17362 "Pray... It's all we have left." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__GATE_TALK__040__M__1
TT 17363 "Hey! All those bodies.... There's no one to guard their houses, right?" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__GUARDS_GATE__010__M__1
TT 17364 "We could take a look. Tonight. With a big bag." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__GUARDS_GATE__030__M__1
TT 17365 "Sure!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__GUARDS_GATE__050__M__1
TT 17366 "The streets are forbidden to all but the city guard!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__LINES_PATROL__020__M__1
TT 17367 "Yes... and we still have a lot of bodies to burn." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__RIGHT_SPEAR__020__M__1
TT 17368 "Damn... You're right... I hope our boys get here with those jars soon... if not..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__RIGHT_SPEAR__040__M__1
TT 17369 "We're out of tar and bodies keep coming..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_PYRE__010__M__1
TT 17370 "This is not “cleaning”... Most of these people weren't even sick! The Beast is emptying the city! It's a massacre!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_PYRE__030__M__1
TT 17371 "Aah!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH04__ONOM__SAFEHOUSE__050__M__1
TT 17372 "Three men with me! You! Go down there! You, up!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_ORDER_FOREST__040__M__1
TT 17373 "Through here! A team found a way down! Move!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__GORGE_ENTRY__060__M__1
TT 17374 "We'll get you! You can't stop us all!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__LASTPART_RATMOVE__040__M__1
TT 17375 "That girl... She took down trained soldiers. Who is she? One of the Wall's dogs of war?" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__MORE_MEN_TALKING__010__M__1
TT 17376 "What do you want?" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_DISTRACT__020__M__1
TT 17377 "It's better than nothing. Let's go and see..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_DISTRACT__040__M__1
TT 17378 "You heard him! Be on guard and keep your eyes open!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_DISTRACT__045__M__1
TT 17379 "Hey! You!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_IDLE__010__M__1
TT 17380 "How long have you been with this procession?!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__PERREUX_IDLE__030__M__1
TT 17381 "Cooperate and no harm will be done!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__PILGRIMS_REACTION__040__M__1
TT 17382 "You'll die for your crimes! There will be no burial for you!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__REINFORCEMENTS_HELMET__010__M__1
TT 17383 "We can't let him live!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__SECONDPART_RATMOVE__020__M__1
TT 17384 "Remember! The Count of Arles wants this land cleaned of its scum! This girl killed your brothers! Her execution will take place here!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_ENCOUNTER__010__M__1
TT 17385 "He's the one giving the orders! Show some respect!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_ENCOUNTER__030__M__1
TT 17386 "Holy Mother... Rats! They're here too!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_ENTERING_DYEING__020__M__1
TT 17387 "We should leave! Come!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_ENTERING_DYEING__050__M__1
TT 17388 "Where are the workers? This mine isn't abandoned, is it?" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_LANDED__020__M__1
TT 17389 "Stay back!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__TENT_EVENT__020__M__1
TT 17390 "For the Red city!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH06__CHATTER__THIRDPART_RATMOVE__020__M__1
TT 17391 "Why do we care about smugglers? Those rats are killing thousands!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH07__CHATTER__CAVE_SOLDIERS__010__M__1
TT 17392 "Bloody rain! It's perfect... No smuggler would be out in this! We're the only ones getting soaked." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH07__CHATTER__ENCOUNTER_1ST_PART__010__M__1
TT 17393 "Should have stuck to carpentry... Lots of work, easy and warm... But no... Wanted a life of adventure... But bloody goddamn rats? No, sir... No..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH07__CHATTER__INSIDE_HOUSE__010__M__1
TT 17394 "Got you!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA__020__M__1
TT 17395 "You got nowhere to run! And the Count doesn't need you alive!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA__040__M__1
TT 17396 "onom" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__040__M__1
TT 17397 "onom" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__080__M__1
TT 17398 "onom" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__120__M__1
TT 17399 "onom" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__130__M__1
TT 17400 "I hope they'll cross the main square once again. It's the best moment!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH08__CHATTER__AUDIENCE_WAITING__030__M__1
TT 17401 "The dancers and musicians are now in place! The festivities are about to begin! Come!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH08__CHATTER__GO_PROCESSION__010__M__1
TT 17402 "Be patient! We need the way clear for the moment! They're just moving goods to the square!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH08__CHATTER__MARKET_CRIER__010__M__1
TT 17403 "Hurry! The Count is being attacked!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH08__CHATTER__REINFORCEMENT_COUNT__010__M__1
TT 17404 "Thank you for your offerings! Sorry to push you out, but the ceremony will begin soon!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH09__CHATTER__BELIEVERS__005__M__1
TT 17405 "We'll be especially careful, don't worry!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH09__CHATTER__BELIEVERS__030__M__1
TT 17406 "It's going to be a hot day..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH09__CHATTER__GARDEN_GUARD_TALK__010__M__1
TT 17407 "Well things got a bit rough yesterday at the harbour, so..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH09__CHATTER__GARDEN_GUARD_TALK__030__M__1
TT 17408 "They stay here for now. We'll bring them up there after the ceremony." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH09__CHATTER__GATE_SOLDIERS__015__M__1
TT 17409 "The Child knows..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH09__CHATTER__GATE_SOLDIERS__050__M__1
TT 17410 "Are you going to the fertility site?" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_NPC_GUARDS__010__M__1
TT 17411 "I hope so. You both deserve the Child's blessing." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_NPC_GUARDS__030__M__1
TT 17412 "Hey! The Count wants no soldier inside the Sanctuary, all right?" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH09__CHATTER__PATROL_UP__010__M__1
TT 17413 "Sure, enjoy the brighter days!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__006__M__1
TT 17414 "Not yet. Not until we've got everybody regrouped." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__ANY_EVACUATION__020__M__1
TT 17415 "Yes, sir!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__BATTLE_PLAN__080__M__1
TT 17416 "Get off my back! This thing's so old it might just explode!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__CHARIOT_BUILT__030__M__1
TT 17417 "Through there. Be safe." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__DOOR__010__M__1
TT 17418 "For now... The Count opened the gates to people... but there's so many dead and wounded..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__FIGHT_RATS__010__M__1
TT 17419 "You're safe, as long as you stay inside this line. But outside, without light..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__FIGHT_RATS_CHARIOT__030__M__1
TT 17420 "Anyway, you're safe now." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__FIGHT_RATS_CHARIOT__070__M__1
TT 17421 "There are more..." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__HOSPITAL__020__M__1
TT 17422 "Please hurry, we don't have much time!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__HOSPITAL_CONTINUE__010__M__1
TT 17423 "Pick up the pace! Keep these flames fed!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__MORE_WOOD__020__M__1
TT 17424 "Careful! Stay back!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__RATS_CHARIOT__030__M__1
TT 17425 "Quiet! This is not time to argue!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__REFUGEES_TALK__010__M__1
TT 17426 "Kill that damned girl! Whatever the cost!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__SECOND_WAVE__040__M__1
TT 17427 "We've got wounded up here, it's not pretty. The... child may want to look away." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH12__CHATTER__STAIRS__010__M__1
TT 17428 "This place is falling apart! To Hell with the executioner!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__BEFORE_EXECUTION__015__M__1
TT 17429 "Yes, sir!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__BELFRY_FALL__030__M__1
TT 17430 "This is it! It's over! You've done enough damage!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__FURIOUS_RATSTRIKE_INTRO__020__M__1
TT 17431 "Surrender the Child and you'll get a quick death!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__FURIOUS_RATSTRIKE_INTRO__030__M__1
TT 17432 "Hey! You heard about Milo?" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__IDLE_ABOUT_MILO__010__M__1
TT 17433 "He's dead. His hideout, his men, the slaves... Gone! They say this mess started there! They say the Defiler used the Child to do it." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__IDLE_ABOUT_MILO__030__M__1
TT 17434 "They're here! Stop them!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__PUSH_FORWARD_1__020__M__1
TT 17435 "Damn! You felt that?! That tremor wrecked the oil jars!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS__010__M__1
TT 17436 "This happened because he's under the influence of that Defiler girl! That's why the Count wants her dead at all costs!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS__040__M__1
TT 17437 "He'll recover. He knows death. Don't forget he's been to war. The man earned glory in hundreds of battles." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_IDLE_1__020__M__1
TT 17438 "Not until we've found the Child of Embers!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_IDLE_2__020__M__1
TT 17439 "Then it will have been worth it! Focus on your mission!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_IDLE_2__040__M__1
TT 17440 "The Child can't have given up on us. Not after everything we gave for him! He's too young... too vulnerable... yes. The Count will figure something out." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__CHATTER__UPSTAIRS_SOLDIER__010__M__1
TT 17441 "I can't believe our Countess is dead! I heard the Count is so devastated he won't even be there for the hanging. They built a gallows on the harbour square for Arnaud." VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__RTC__780_ARNAUD__050__M__1
TT 17442 "Yes, me too!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH13__RTC__780_ARNAUD__085__M__1
TT 17443 "Take that boat! For the Count of Provence!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH14__CHATTER__FIGHT_BEGINNING__010__M__1
TT 17444 "I will avenge our Countess! And all the innocents you murdered!" VO__SOLDIER_N1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_NOFOG_4__010__M__1
