TT 17908 "Yes. We have our dead too. And most of them won't get a proper grave." VO__SOLDIER_N2__CH13__CHATTER__ABOUT_COUNT__030__M__1
TT 17909 "Talk about brighter days! This place looks like proper Hell!" VO__SOLDIER_N2__CH13__CHATTER__ABOUT_FUTURE__010__M__1
