TT 17917 "Too bad the Count's not here to see it!" VO__SOLDIER_N2__CH13__CHATTER__VISTA_GALLOW_UP__030__M__1
TT 17918 "They're hanging the Wall? Damn them! I wanted to see that!" VO__SOLDIER_N2__CH13__RTC__780_ARNAUD__080__M__1
