TT 18410 "I'm not falling for it again! I'll find you..." VO__SOLDIER_N3__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 18411 "You really thought that would work on me again?" VO__SOLDIER_N3__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__3
