TT 18421 "I may be stuck now, but you're not safe." VO__SOLDIER_N3__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__4
TT 18422 "I will not be stuck here long, hear that?" VO__SOLDIER_N3__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__5
TT 18423 "I'm stuck here now! But you won't get away next time!" VO__SOLDIER_N3__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__6
