TT 18678 "The city needs these jars intact! So settle down!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH04__CHATTER__QUAI__090__M__1
TT 18679 "Hey! What's that...?" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH04__CHATTER__TREMORS__010__M__1
TT 18680 "It's a public health matter. You should have left when you still could, Joseph." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH04__RTC__135_MEETING_JOSEPH__010__M__1
TT 18681 "Consider your contract cancelled then. The harbor's locked down and you're trespassing." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH04__RTC__135_MEETING_JOSEPH__030__M__1
TT 18682 "No. You've seen too much. I'm arresting you!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH04__RTC__135_MEETING_JOSEPH__073__M__1
TT 18683 "Argh!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH04__RTC__135_MEETING_JOSEPH_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 18684 "Curfew is still in effect! Go back to your homes!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH04__RTC__140_FIRST_OUTBURST__140__M__1
TT 18685 "Stop!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__ARROW_STUCK__010__M__1
TT 18686 "Kill them anyway! For honour!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__BEGINNING_RATMOVE__080__M__1
TT 18687 "Understood!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__CAPTAIN_ORDER_FOREST__060__M__1
TT 18688 "Here! They're here!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__CHASED__010__M__1
TT 18689 "On me!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__CHASED__030__M__1
TT 18690 "We've had a report that they're close! Search the area! Get that witch!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__ENCOUNTER_CANYON_INTRO__010__M__1
TT 18691 "What are you doing? Slay that demon!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__FOURTHPART_RATMOVE__010__M__1
TT 18692 "The Wall doesn't use women or children." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__MORE_MEN_TALKING__020__M__1
TT 18693 "Hey! Rats... You see that?! Rats!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__NEW_SOLDIERS_DYEFACTORY__010__M__1
TT 18694 "Careful!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__NEW_SOLDIERS_DYEFACTORY__030__M__1
TT 18695 "Make way! Clear your tents!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__PILGRIMS_REACTION__030__M__1
TT 18696 "The girl's here! Rally!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__RATS_APPEARANCE__010__M__1
TT 18697 "Stop the witch!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__REINFORCEMENTS_LIGHT__010__M__1
TT 18698 "On me! They're here! I need reinforcements!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__STANDING_UP__010__M__1
TT 18699 "For our fallen brothers!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__THIRDPART_RATMOVE__010__M__1
TT 18700 "Got you! Here!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__CHATTER__WOODS_FALL__010__M__1
TT 18701 "Look! They're here!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH06__RTC__250_DEAD_END__030__M__1
TT 18702 "HEY! You found any tracks?!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH07__CHATTER__UNEXPECTED_FOES__020__M__1
TT 18703 "Look around ya, this place is a bloody maze! Listen, if we bring back one or two dead smugglers, the Count'll decorate us!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH07__CHATTER__UNEXPECTED_FOES__070__M__1
TT 18704 "It's bad luck I tell you!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH07__CHATTER__VILLAGE_ENTRANCE__010__M__1
TT 18705 "It's called la Rascasse! That fish is bad luck!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH07__CHATTER__VILLAGE_ENTRANCE__030__M__1
TT 18706 "Get them! The girl and the child!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH08__CHATTER__RUN__010__M__1
TT 18707 "Get those fires started again!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__CHATTER__BACKGROUND_NOISE__020__M__1
TT 18708 "Get to the bridge! Hold the line!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__CHATTER__BACKGROUND_NOISE__040__M__1
TT 18709 "Have you fixed the piston yet? We need this cart on the ramparts fast!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__CHATTER__CHARIOT_BUILT__010__M__1
TT 18710 "The rats are pushing on our east flank! We need torches there!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__CHATTER__DEFENSES__020__M__1
TT 18711 "More wood over here!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__CHATTER__FIGHT_RATS_WOOD__010__M__1
TT 18712 "Surround them! For the Brighter Days!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_INCOMING_1__020__M__1
TT 18713 "Hey! My Lady!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__030__M__1
TT 18714 "You're the Countess' guest aren't you? Are you hurt?" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__050__M__1
TT 18715 "We have orders to escort you safely to the palace." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__070__M__1
TT 18716 "You have... guests." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__090__M__1
TT 18717 "Your mother, and a boy." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__110__M__1
TT 18718 "Sire! We can't stay here. We'll get her from inside!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__660_NOW_THEY_DIE__075__M__1
TT 18719 "Sire!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__665_DEVOURED__020__M__1
TT 18720 "Sire! We need to evacuate, Sire! It's too late!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__665_DEVOURED__040__M__1
TT 18721 "Sire, your people need you! Sire!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__665_DEVOURED__050__M__1
TT 18722 "He'll die, all right?! Now shut the hell up!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH13__CHATTER__BEFORE_EXECUTION__035__M__1
TT 18723 "Why do we still want the Child? He'll be the end of us! He ruined everything!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS__030__M__1
TT 18724 "Ha... let's hope it works..." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS__050__M__1
TT 18725 "Does someone know when we're suppose to evacuate?" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_IDLE_2__010__M__1
TT 18726 "So what if the ground collapses entirely before that?!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_IDLE_2__030__M__1
TT 18727 "You heard the Count! Shoot!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH14__CHATTER__ARCHERS_SHOOTING__010__M__1
TT 18728 "May my faith guide my arm! May it lead to brighter days!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_FOG_IDLE_1__010__M__1
TT 18729 "I'm with you, my lord! Reinforcements are coming!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_NOFOG_1__010__M__1
TT 18730 "I will! Right away!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_NOFOG_3__010__M__1
TT 18731 "Your corrupted blood will soak this ground!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_NOFOG_5__010__M__1
TT 18732 "The Child will save us all!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_NOFOG_IDLE_1__010__M__1
TT 18733 "Sir! We need to evacuate!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__RTC__830_NEBULA__290__M__1
