TT 18844 "Someone's playing with us! Start looking!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__1
TT 18845 "Someone wants to mess with us! Find out who!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__2
TT 18846 "Someone's trying to fool us! Search for them!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__3
TT 18847 "You were lucky so far, but I'll find you!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 18848 "Think you can fool me again?! Show yourself now!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 18849 "Trying to play me for a fool? I'll get you!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 18850 "Someone's here! Everyone! With me!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__1
TT 18851 "We've got intruders here!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__2
TT 18852 "Trespassers! Everyone with me!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__3
TT 18853 "You! Come here!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 18854 "Don't try to run away, you bastard!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 18855 "You there! Stop!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 18856 "Don't think I'm stuck for good, I'll come for you!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__1
TT 18857 "We're not finished yet, I'll get to you." VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__2
TT 18858 "We're not done yet, I'll catch you bastards!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__3
TT 18859 "It's not over yet, I'm onto you!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__4
TT 18860 "Won't give up that easily, I'll get you somehow." VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__5
TT 18861 "I may be blocked now but watch your back!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__6
TT 18862 "Someone's been killed! Look out!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__1
TT 18863 "Damn! One down!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__2
TT 18864 "Shit! He's dead!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__3
TT 18865 "You ready to burn?!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__1
TT 18866 "I'm gonna torch anyone who's in there!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__2
TT 18867 "Better come out! It's gonna get hot in there!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__3
TT 18868 "There! We have intruders!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__1
TT 18869 "With me! Stop the intruders!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__2
TT 18870 "They shouldn't be here! Get them!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__3
TT 18871 "Spread out and get the bastards!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__1
TT 18872 "Fan out! Cover the area!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__2
TT 18873 "Get moving! Let's surround them!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__3
TT 18874 "You're not leaving here alive!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__1
TT 18875 "You think you stand a chance?!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__2
TT 18876 "Better start begging for your life!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__3
TT 18877 "Fire? What devilry is this?" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__1
