TT 19629 "It's seen worse! This boat's a survivor." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__CHATTER__SOPHIA_BAR__050__M__1
TT 19630 "Hey! The anchor's on the other side of the ship, Amicia!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__CHATTER__SOPHIA_WARN_ANCHOR__010__M__1
TT 19631 "Caught your breath yet? Ready to go?" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__CHATTER__TO_PONTOON__010__M__1
TT 19632 "Not that pontoon, the other one!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__CHATTER__WRONG_PONTOON__010__M__1
TT 19633 "Amicia! I don't know where you are but we need that anchor raised!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__HELPER__ANCHOR_FREE_1__010__M__1
TT 19634 "Hoist the mainsail or we'll never leave this bloody place!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__HELPER__SAILS_ORDER_MAINSAIL_1__010__M__1
TT 19635 "Amicia, pull down on the halyard line to fasten the mainsail!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__HELPER__SAILS_ORDER_MAINSAIL_2__010__M__1
TT 19636 "Amicia! Get on the pontoon and have a look at the sail!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__HELPER__SAILS_STUCK_TOGETHER_1__010__M__1
TT 19637 "Get on the pontoon and break that lock to free the sail!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__HELPER__SAILS_STUCK_TOGETHER_2__010__M__1
TT 19638 "Let him pass." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__030__M__1
TT 19639 "Arnaud... Even those rot-eating rats didn't want you..." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__050__M__1
TT 19640 "Look at that..." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__060__M__1
TT 19641 "I like the new crew!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__070__M__1
TT 19642 "I see you left your mark on her already." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__110__M__1
TT 19643 "Don't be ashamed, sweetheart. It suits you." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__120__M__1
TT 19644 "What do you want?" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__130__M__1
TT 19645 "We're done, Arnaud. The Count's army is on our back and thousands of rats are shitting on my doorstep. This place is over. I'm disbanding the crew." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__150__M__1
TT 19646 "Alright then! The Call of the Sea it is! I need some time off. Who cares? One thing though..." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__170__M__1
TT 19647 "If you ever hurt her in front of me, I'll kill you." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__190__M__1
TT 19648 "By the way... The Count's men put my boat in dry dock." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__210__M__1
TT 19649 "That part is so true. I need a word with my crew." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__230__M__1
TT 19650 "Go ahead to the village, my boat is there. I'll join you." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__240__M__1
TT 19651 "I'm afraid it's for good this time." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__300_SMUGGLER__280__M__1
TT 19652 "Open up! Open up!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA__010__M__1
TT 19653 "EMPTY" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA__030__M__1
TT 19654 "No... We just met and I already owe you." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA__060__M__1
TT 19655 "You don't make the rules." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA__080__M__1
TT 19656 "Let's try... but you'll end up wanting to kill me too." VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA__100__M__1
TT 19657 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 19658 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 19659 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__030__M__1
TT 19660 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__060__M__1
TT 19661 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__110__M__1
TT 19662 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__140__M__1
TT 19663 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__160__M__1
TT 19664 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__303_SAVING_SOPHIA_ONOM__170__M__1
TT 19665 "Nice work! Now get ready!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__310_SET_SAIL__010__M__1
TT 19666 "Hold on!" VO__SOPHIA__CH07__RTC__310_SET_SAIL__015__M__1
TT 19667 "Hey, you two! The sail's pulling port side! I need a hand!" VO__SOPHIA__CH08__CHATTER__CALL_SAIL__010__M__1
TT 19668 "We know!" VO__SOPHIA__CH08__CHATTER__HUGO_DECK_END__030__M__1
TT 19669 "Hey! The terrible siblings of the storm!" VO__SOPHIA__CH08__CHATTER__HUGO_HELLO_SOPHIA__010__M__1
TT 19670 "Easy... Sirens! They know all the routes." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__CHATTER__HUGO_INTERACT_SOPHIA__020__M__1
TT 19671 "They're pretty shy, you know... That's why I also use tools and maps. It's very technical, but I'm clever, so..." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__CHATTER__HUGO_INTERACT_SOPHIA__040__M__1
TT 19672 "No... But don't break them, or I throw you overboard." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__CHATTER__HUGO_INTERACT_SOPHIA__070__M__1
TT 19673 "I'm not joking." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__CHATTER__HUGO_INTERACT_SOPHIA__090__M__1
TT 19674 "Well done!" VO__SOPHIA__CH08__CHATTER__SAIL_PULL_DONE__020__M__1
TT 19675 "It's worth all the other troubles..." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__020__M__1
TT 19676 "Come on, take it!" VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__030__M__1
TT 19677 "Go on! You won't crash into anything!" VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__050__M__1
TT 19678 "So?" VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__060__M__1
TT 19679 "It's the sea you feel. It's freedom." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__080__M__1
TT 19680 "Thank Arnaud. I'm usually not so kind." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__100__M__1
TT 19681 "He's a bastard, I know. He has reasons to be. Deep scars. Not that it excuses him, but..." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__120__M__1
TT 19682 "You're welcome." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__349_SOPHIA__150__M__1
TT 19683 "Sorry..." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__350_EARTH__110__M__1
TT 19684 "...just wanted to say we'll be preparing to make land soon. I'll need your help. Just... come see me when you're ready..." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__350_EARTH__120__M__1
TT 19685 "I'll stay! I'll fix a few things here and I'll join you later." VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__060__M__1
TT 19686 "Sounds good! By the way... This land is under the Count's law. Be “nice”, see?" VO__SOPHIA__CH08__RTC__360_HARBOR__080__M__1
TT 19687 "How can they stand in that water?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__1ST_STEPS__010__M__1
TT 19688 "It doesn't mean things won't get better!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__1ST_STEPS__070__M__1
TT 19689 "We're almost there..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__2ND_STEPS__010__M__1
TT 19690 "Kites. You've never seen one?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_KITES__020__M__1
TT 19691 "Well they're like... tiny boat sails. They take the wind and off they go!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_KITES__040__M__1
TT 19692 "Sanctuary. That's what I've heard it called. And now I'm even more curious about it." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_SANCTUARY__030__M__1
TT 19693 "Hey! Come here you two!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_SOPHIA__012__M__1
TT 19694 "Upstairs!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_SOPHIA__030__M__1
TT 19695 "Look behind the curtains!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ABOUT_SOPHIA__040__M__1
TT 19696 "This place is crazy..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__AFTER_ATHANOR__010__M__1
TT 19697 "On the bright side... You don't lock a place down if it doesn't hold something important." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__AFTER_CLIMB__020__M__1
TT 19698 "The view from up there must be quite a sight..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__AFTER_MAP__010__M__1
TT 19699 "He shot me in the eyes, all right?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__AFTER_WATER_POND__020__M__1
TT 19700 "Talk about a family..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__AFTER_WATER_POND__050__M__1
TT 19701 "I'll have my revenge..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__AFTER_WATER_POND__070__M__1
TT 19702 "Well let's go then!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ALMOST_TOP__020__M__1
TT 19703 "I've seen things like this. It's typical in Provence and its surroundings." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ARCHES__020__M__1
TT 19704 "Some symbolic passageway?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ARCHES__040__M__1
TT 19705 "It's a lady's armour!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ARMOR_INTERACT__020__M__1
TT 19706 "Protector..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ARMOR_INTERACT__040__M__1
TT 19707 "Hey, you're good. I should hire you." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__BARN_BEAM_DOWN__020__M__1
TT 19708 "It's fine. I wasn't born a smuggler either. You do what you must." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__BARN_BEAM_DOWN__040__M__1
TT 19709 "I'm sure there's a way to change that..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__BARN_CLOSE_DOOR__020__M__1
TT 19710 "Hm. Soldier." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__BELIEVERS__007__M__1
TT 19711 "That was to be expected." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__BELIEVERS__070__M__1
TT 19712 "And what about that staring bird?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__BIRD_REMINDER_2__010__M__1
TT 19713 "Careful..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__BUILDING_WINDOW__010__M__1
TT 19714 "This Basilius was treated like a king!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__CARRIER_BED_INTERACT__030__M__1
TT 19715 "Yes... And even small it's still stunning." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__CLIFF_VISTA_VILLAGE__020__M__1
TT 19716 "It's nothing... It's just... my worst nightmare..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__CROSSING_OK__040__M__1
TT 19717 "We're doing it, my friends... We're getting there!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__DOOR_IN__005__M__1
TT 19718 "Well, I'm trusting you both." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__DOOR_IN__040__M__1
TT 19719 "This is... so strange." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__DRAWING_INTERACT__040__M__1
TT 19720 "Are we... the first to come in here?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ENTER_CARRIER_ROOM__020__M__1
TT 19721 "Too sacred for them, maybe?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ENTER_CARRIER_ROOM__050__M__1
TT 19722 "Are you all right? I saw a Phoenix on that door, then the crack, so..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ENTERING_BATHS__010__M__1
TT 19723 "Shall we go?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__ENTERING_BATHS__030__M__1
TT 19724 "It's up to you!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__FEATHER__030__M__1
TT 19725 "He must be, for them to be so loud about him." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__FESTIVAL_BAR__080__M__1
TT 19726 "Are they even aware of what's happening on the continent?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__FESTIVAL_BAR__100__M__1
TT 19727 "Hence the drinks..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__FESTIVAL_BAR__120__M__1
TT 19728 "Damn, it's getting hot..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__FIRST_STEPS__010__M__1
TT 19729 "Do you know what “almost” means?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__FIRST_STEPS__030__M__1
TT 19730 "So, what d'you expect to find up there?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__FIRST_STEPS__050__M__1
TT 19731 "So, a dream and a bird, hm?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__FOLLOWING_LOOK__010__M__1
TT 19732 "All right, why not..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__FOLLOWING_LOOK__040__M__1
TT 19733 "Looks like they really like their privacy here..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GATE_SOLDIERS__030__M__1
TT 19734 "That was knightly!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_BREAK_IN__030__M__1
TT 19735 "Wow... This is turning into an actual rescue mission..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_BURNING__010__M__1
TT 19736 "That's what heroes do." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_DOOR__030__M__1
TT 19737 "She'll find her way back, don't worry. Goats are climbers." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_FAIL__030__M__1
TT 19738 "Goats... I stared in their eyes for hours when I was a child. You can't know what's going on in there." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_INSIDE__030__M__1
TT 19739 "All right, she's saved, you've overcome your fear, and I want to see that sanctuary! Let's go?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_OVER__010__M__1
TT 19740 "She will. She's her own master." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_OVER__040__M__1
TT 19741 "So here's our fugitive..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_PET__020__M__1
TT 19742 "You've done the difficult part. Don't startle her and it'll be just fine." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_PET__050__M__1
TT 19743 "Screaming's not biting. Just say to yourself it can happen and that's all!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_PET__070__M__1
TT 19744 "Who wouldn't want to dream of goats?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_SAVIOUR__030__M__1
TT 19745 "My hero!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_SEND_HUGO__030__M__1
TT 19746 "He's so funny..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOAT_SEND_HUGO__040__M__1
TT 19747 "Well, well, well... our fierce warrior is afraid of goats?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOATS__050__M__1
TT 19748 "Ah... We came all the way for the little one..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOATS__101__M__1
TT 19749 "We'll keep that in mind. Thank you!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOATS__109__M__1
TT 19750 "Oh come on, it's a goat, not a wolf!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__GOATS__150__M__1
TT 19751 "Erm. I think the little one needs you, Amicia..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HE_NEEDS_YOU__010__M__1
TT 19752 "Hey! We don't have all the time in the world, you know! Come!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HELPER_SOPHIA_1__010__M__1
TT 19753 "Nice find! Some sort of... antique theatre?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_AMPHI_ENTRANCE__020__M__1
TT 19754 "And their... Child of Embers..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_AMPHI_MAP__025__M__1
TT 19755 "I would love to make gold grow like that..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_FIELDS_FIELDVIEW__040__M__1
TT 19756 "All right, you won." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_FIELDS_FIELDVIEW__070__M__1
TT 19757 "So how is it, inside?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_FIELDS_PALACEVIEW__020__M__1
TT 19758 "Tell me, why this fascination with windmills?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_FIELDS_WINDMILLS__020__M__1
TT 19759 "Boy... I just see bloody wheat grinders..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_FIELDS_WINDMILLS__040__M__1
TT 19760 "You're right! Free the fishes!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_FOREST_FISHERMAN_BACK__020__M__1
TT 19761 "That... is a tomb. We call it a mound." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_FOREST_MOUND__030__M__1
TT 19762 "I took some time to wander around this morning. D'you know where you're going yet?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_GOINGDOWN_START__009__M__1
TT 19763 "Take your time. Weather's just fine. People are partying. Even the guards are quite nice." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_GOINGDOWN_START__020__M__1
TT 19764 "You sure it's the right way?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_GOINGUP_NOMAP_MID__010__M__1
TT 19765 "Not sure a centuries-old bird is interested in a tent..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_FOUR_RIVER__020__M__1
TT 19766 "Oh... A treasure hunt? Already?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_ONE__040__M__1
TT 19767 "And we're getting to its centre!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_SEVEN__030__M__1
TT 19768 "That's exciting!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_SEVEN_ALT__020__M__1
TT 19769 "Say, that's a large family of birds..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_SIX__015__M__1
TT 19770 "Imagine if it lead to a real nest..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_SIX__030__M__1
TT 19771 "Your answer might be in there..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_THREE__020__M__1
TT 19772 "So what's this one looking at?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_STONE_TWO__030__M__1
TT 19773 "It's never hot in Guyenne?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_FARM__050__M__1
TT 19774 "I trust you." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_FARM__070__M__1
TT 19775 "Well... same to you!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_FARMER_SAY_HI__030__M__1
TT 19776 "Oh, yes... People who can't have children come here to be blessed." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_FESTIVAL_CLOSE__020__M__1
TT 19777 "I heard the Countess is the one who created all this." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_FESTIVAL_CLOSE__040__M__1
TT 19778 "Embarrassing?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_FESTIVAL_CLOSE__100__M__1
TT 19779 "That's exactly right!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_FESTIVAL_INSIDE__020__M__1
TT 19780 "To pray... for people who want children, but can't have them." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUB_VILLAGE_FESTIVAL_INSIDE__040__M__1
TT 19781 "Hey!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUGO_SLIDES__020__M__1
TT 19782 "Oh sh... bloody hell!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUGO_SLIDES__040__M__1
TT 19783 "I don't like your stunts, kid." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUGO_SLIDES__060__M__1
TT 19784 "You love tents?! Me too!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__HUT_INTERACT__060__M__1
TT 19785 "So, Hugo... D'you often dream of... magic birds and all?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_HUGO_DREAM__010__M__1
TT 19786 "Then you did well following it here." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_HUGO_DREAM__030__M__1
TT 19787 "Good question." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_NO_FEAR__030__M__1
TT 19788 "That's what a place usually looks like after Arnaud's passed by." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_SECURITY__010__M__1
TT 19789 "He wasn't always like that." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_SECURITY__030__M__1
TT 19790 "I owe you. But it's just an excuse because this is all too exciting." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_SOPHIA__020__M__1
TT 19791 "No. Only the Child, the Mother and the Father." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__IDLE_THE_ORDER__020__M__1
TT 19792 "Hey! Quieter! We'll find something!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__INTERACT_EMPTY_JARS__020__M__1
TT 19793 "There's nothing much..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__INTERACT_UNKNOWN__020__M__1
TT 19794 "The windmill mechanism!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_1ST_TIME_PUZZLE_OK__060__M__1
TT 19795 "I'll be damned..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_1ST_TIME_PUZZLE_OK__080__M__1
TT 19796 "Holy..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_BOTTOM__010__M__1
TT 19797 "Good eyes! Can't say it's the greatest drawing I've ever seen." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_CLOSED_DOOR__020__M__1
TT 19798 "It's real. As real as a smuggler's lair. A bloody good one. Hell... who built this?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_LODGES__010__M__1
TT 19799 "It feels abandoned. That's the thing... the more amazing you get, the more likely you are to die." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_LODGES__030__M__1
TT 19800 "Whoever hid this... probably has a lot to hide..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_OPENED_DOOR__030__M__1
TT 19801 "You know what, kid? I think you're right. My hands are getting all tingly. It's a sign." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_STAIRS__040__M__1
TT 19802 "A bracer!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_VAMBRACE__025__M__1
TT 19803 "It's too good to leave it here. Keep it." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LAIR_VAMBRACE__060__M__1
TT 19804 "I'd say that's us?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LATECOMERS_RITUAL__070__M__1
TT 19805 "We'll... think about it." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LATECOMERS_RITUAL__090__M__1
TT 19806 "Erm... You're sure?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LEDGE_START__020__M__1
TT 19807 "Oh, wow..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LEDGE_START__040__M__1
TT 19808 "Your alchemists' library! Looks like they were observing the child from here!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LIBRARY__040__M__1
TT 19809 "No, but they took other notes." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__LIBRARY__070__M__1
TT 19810 "Heavy armour, wow... Arnaud really kept them on their toes! Looks like we're crossing a line here." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__MORE_SOLDIERS__020__M__1
TT 19811 "Imagine these bastards standing there, looking at him..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__MOUCHARABIEH__010__M__1
TT 19812 "I may have a lead..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__MOUCHARABIEH__030__M__1
TT 19813 "Which ones?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__NO_WATER_POND__020__M__1
TT 19814 "Cypresses..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__NO_WATER_POND__040__M__1
TT 19815 "Cy-press-es. Cypresses." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__NO_WATER_POND__070__M__1
TT 19816 "You've acquired bad habits, lady." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__OPENING_1ST_WINDMILL__020__M__1
TT 19817 "There goes our visit..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__PASSED_DOOR__020__M__1
TT 19818 "Heh... That bird again?..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__PHOENIX_ORDER__020__M__1
TT 19819 "Erm. Sorry boy..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__PHOENIX_ORDER__050__M__1
TT 19820 "That explains why it stands above the Child on their frescos..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__PHOENIX_ORDER__070__M__1
TT 19821 "There are stairs I think. Could be an abandoned access point.." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POI_ACCESS__020__M__1
TT 19822 "Yes. You have to be a Count to take that kind of risk." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POST_FESTIVAL_BAR__020__M__1
TT 19823 "And there's no eye gold can't close." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POST_FESTIVAL_BAR__040__M__1
TT 19824 "I must say, I could see myself living here..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POST_VAMBRACE__020__M__1
TT 19825 "I'm happier when people can't see me." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POST_VAMBRACE__040__M__1
TT 19826 "I'm more of a lizard, I think." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POST_VAMBRACE__070__M__1
TT 19827 "All right... Why not." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POST_VAMBRACE__090__M__1
TT 19828 "What's this now?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POTIONS__005__M__1
TT 19829 "But... it looks exactly like what you're searching for, no?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POTIONS__030__M__1
TT 19830 "On it!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POTIONS__050__M__1
TT 19831 "It IS shiny already." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__POTTER_TALK__060__M__1
TT 19832 "Don't forget I'm here if you need a distraction from my prism!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__PRISM_REMINDER__010__M__1
TT 19833 "I have a trick... This prism focuses sunlight. It can scorch tall grass... You get smoke. You get any guard's attention." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__PRISM_TUTO__006__M__1
TT 19834 "Tell me where you want a guard to go. Tall grass only." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__PRISM_TUTO__030__M__1
TT 19835 "Move as soon as he's gone. It never lasts long." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__PRISM_TUTO_OK__030__M__1
TT 19836 "Not just any warrior. Look at the shape of the armour." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__PROTECTOR_ROOM__010__M__1
TT 19837 "Hey, I'd like that!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__RIVER_SPOT__020__M__1
TT 19838 "Oh, you've never seen a naval fight, have you?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__RIVER_SPOT__040__M__1
TT 19839 "Yes. Stay on land for this, believe me." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__RIVER_SPOT__060__M__1
TT 19840 "So, we're done here for now?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SANCT_CONFIRMATION__020__M__1
TT 19841 "Of course they are. They make honey, and I love honey." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SANCT_PATH_BEEKEEPERS__030__M__1
TT 19842 "Damn, these soldiers are so nice. I almost feel bad for all the times I've insulted them." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SANCT_PATH_SOLDIERS__010__M__1
TT 19843 "I see... How many have you...?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SANCT_PATH_SOLDIERS__030__M__1
TT 19844 "Oh, I've seen you “at work”. I'm not surprised. If not for your skills, I'd be dead." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SANCT_PATH_SOLDIERS__050__M__1
TT 19845 "They're in Latin!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SCROLLS_INTERACT__025__M__1
TT 19846 "I can!... Come look! I think I've got something!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SCROLLS_INTERACT__040__M__1
TT 19847 "Tramontane... Yes." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SECRET_HOUSE__020__M__1
TT 19848 "I say this ladder is an invitation." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SECRET_LADDER__030__M__1
TT 19849 "Feels like the place was used not so long ago." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_LAIR__020__M__1
TT 19850 "You're the only goblin here." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_LAIR__040__M__1
TT 19851 "How did you know?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_LAIR__060__M__1
TT 19852 "Typically some kind of smuggler code. Someone had business here." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_SYMBOL_1__030__M__1
TT 19853 "When things go wrong or if a crew splits up, they leave those marks behind... to make sure one of them will retrieve what they hid." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_SYMBOL_1__050__M__1
TT 19854 "Goods, probably... Wine, food— treasure to some." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_SYMBOL_1__070__M__1
TT 19855 "Can't say! These things may have been here a long time." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_SYMBOL_2__020__M__1
TT 19856 "Hey, another smuggler mark here." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_SYMBOL_2__030__M__1
TT 19857 "Smuggler marking." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_SYMBOL_3__010__M__1
TT 19858 "I don't know... Each crew has their own code." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_SYMBOL_3__040__M__1
TT 19859 "Yup..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SMUGGLER_SYMBOL_4__020__M__1
TT 19860 "Hey, it's me." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SOPHIA_BACK__010__M__1
TT 19861 "Come, I've found a passage back there. It's now or never." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SOPHIA_BACK__030__M__1
TT 19862 "I wonder if they were put to use..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SWORDS_AND_SPEARS__030__M__1
TT 19863 "Valuable tiny creatures..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__SWORDS_AND_SPEARS__050__M__1
TT 19864 "So we've got a magic bird, an ancient order of alchemists, the little one has visions... Well, just... What else can I expect?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TO_SANCTUARY_2__010__M__1
TT 19865 "You can." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TO_SANCTUARY_2__030__M__1
TT 19866 "Who could curse such a cute baby?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TO_SANCTUARY_2__037__M__1
TT 19867 "Damn... All right! We'll find what you came for. You have my word." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TO_SANCTUARY_2__060__M__1
TT 19868 "Nice screeching by the way, you two." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_GOING_BACK__030__M__1
TT 19869 "I know. It's my commanding voice. You need one to be heard over the sound of the sea." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_GOING_BACK__050__M__1
TT 19870 "Oh, they've never complained." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_GOING_BACK__070__M__1
TT 19871 "Damn ladders..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_LADDER__060__M__1
TT 19872 "Bullseye!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_LOCK_SHOT__010__M__1
TT 19873 "Oh, so you came to conquer..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_LOCK_SHOT__040__M__1
TT 19874 "Come on, you're not going to let a locked door stop you." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_LOCKED_DOOR__020__M__1
TT 19875 "Not just any bird—A bird of prey!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_SOUVENIR__020__M__1
TT 19876 "EMPTY" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_SOUVENIR__080__M__1
TT 19877 "I was born to screech." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_SOUVENIR__120__M__1
TT 19878 "SCREEEEECH!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_SOUVENIR__150__M__1
TT 19879 "Phew... Nice view..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOWER_TOP__030__M__1
TT 19880 "And she let him... she was the best kind of knight." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TOY_CHEST__020__M__1
TT 19881 "It's a prayer about life and children." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TREE_RITUAL__130__M__1
TT 19882 "An olive tree... Thousands of years I'd say." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TREE_SOUVENIR__030__M__1
TT 19883 "On the contrary. It's strong. It adapted." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TREE_SOUVENIR__050__M__1
TT 19884 "Then tell it. It will listen." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TREE_SOUVENIR__100__M__1
TT 19885 "That's... pretty unpleasant..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TUNNEL_ORDEAL__020__M__1
TT 19886 "Go on..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TUNNEL_ORDEAL__060__M__1
TT 19887 "Bloody nice." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__TUNNEL_ORDEAL__090__M__1
TT 19888 "Yes. Carving that must have hurt..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__VISTA_SANCTUARY__020__M__1
TT 19889 "Pretty sure it was already there back then." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WANDERING_BASINS__020__M__1
TT 19890 "I cannot believe this place is real..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WANDERING_WATER__010__M__1
TT 19891 "Besides, nothing's nearly as fun as being where you're not supposed to be." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WATCHTOWER__040__M__1
TT 19892 "Uh... Sure..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WATCHTOWER__070__M__1
TT 19893 "The big sister has spoken! Although I could have used some fresh water." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WATER_POND_DENIED__030__M__1
TT 19894 "Just what I need anyway!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WATER_POND_EVENT__020__M__1
TT 19895 "I'll get it for you!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WATER_POND_EVENT__040__M__1
TT 19896 "That's better!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WATER_POND_EVENT__060__M__1
TT 19897 "Counter-attack!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WATER_POND_EVENT__100__M__1
TT 19898 "All right, all right, all right! I yield! You soaked me to death." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WATER_POND_EVENT__140__M__1
TT 19899 "How can he run in this heat?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WATER_POND_SPOT__020__M__1
TT 19900 "Yes, it didn't seem close though." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WINDMILL_WIN__030__M__1
TT 19901 "Prophets? Are there prophets in the Order?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WOODEN_TOYS_INTERACT__040__M__1
TT 19902 "Hm. Makes sense. Boys." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WOODEN_TOYS_INTERACT__060__M__1
TT 19903 "Amicia... We should really check what's behind that door, while we can!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__CHATTER__WRONGWAY_EXPLORER__010__M__1
TT 19904 "Hmmm... Shame I don't have a torch. Would take care of that grass in no time." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__HELPER__HUB_AMPHI_BURNING_SOPHIA_1__010__M__1
TT 19905 "Slept well?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__010__M__1
TT 19906 "Where you'd be? That's my life, sweetheart... Wake up early, observe, listen and make the best of it!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__028__M__1
TT 19907 "That's how I discovered Arnaud is in jail." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__030__M__1
TT 19908 "What kind of use he could make of such a tiny creature?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__036__M__1
TT 19909 "Or are you more useful than you look like, little one?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__038__M__1
TT 19910 "So you spent the night celebrating his capture with the Count of Provence and his wife!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__045__M__1
TT 19911 "All right! I hit a nerve there!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__060__M__1
TT 19912 "I was teasing you! I just like to know who my “friends” really are... and I like what I hear! Come, let's take a walk." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__065__M__1
TT 19913 "The island... It's a map of the island." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__030__M__1
TT 19914 "I'd say hundreds of years old... Probably Byzantian. There is a lot of those around here." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__050__M__1
TT 19915 "What Order?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__110__M__1
TT 19916 "But you kneel to no one. I get that." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__150__M__1
TT 19917 "So what did you come here looking for?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__160__M__1
TT 19918 "It's simple... If this symbol indicates important areas..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__180__M__1
TT 19919 "That one... Well, that one is pretty hard to miss." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__190__M__1
TT 19920 "They're called Las Madres. “The Mothers”." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__194__M__1
TT 19921 "I know... boring." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__200__M__1
TT 19922 "If you want me to. I told you. I owe you." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__230__M__1
TT 19923 "Don't be disappointed, we're not there yet..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH__030__M__1
TT 19924 "I don't like mountains. Everything I need is at sea level." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH__050__M__1
TT 19925 "Well in that case, let's be big and tall together!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH__080__M__1
TT 19926 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 19927 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 19928 "No kidding..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__070__M__1
TT 19929 "Their Child of Embers?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__090__M__1
TT 19930 "“The Prima Macula”... This just gets better and better..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__110__M__1
TT 19931 "And it's killing him." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__130__M__1
TT 19932 "Let me guess... Death, war, disease and famine." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__150__M__1
TT 19933 "All of it sounds like a crazy fantasy to me..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__180__M__1
TT 19934 "Stagnating water is rarely magic." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__260__M__1
TT 19935 "It looks like there is more to this place... behind here." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__320__M__1
TT 19936 "Your alchemists wrote down everything that happened to the Carrier. It's sorted by date... The last entry was in the year 541..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__020__M__1
TT 19937 "I haven't studied Latin since the Convent, but it talks about Basilius..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__040__M__1
TT 19938 "...and an “Aelia Dragas”. His... “Protector”." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__046__M__1
TT 19939 "The Order took away the Carrier from her. She rebelled and was arrested close to a “round tower”, they took her to a... a “capella”, a chapel, inside a fort." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__060__M__1
TT 19940 "It doesn't say." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__066__M__1
TT 19941 "We're lucky they didn't come sooner." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__110__M__1
TT 19942 "Through there?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__165__M__1
TT 19943 "Let's try." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__190__M__1
TT 19944 "Spend a full week at sea with my crew... Changes your notion of stench forever." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__450_CROWNED__020__M__1
TT 19945 "Don't you want to know what happened to that Aelia? And your... “ancestor”?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__450_CROWNED__060__M__1
TT 19946 "Cough..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__450_CROWNED_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 19947 "Bold... but believable." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__FIRST_RITUALS__110__M__1
TT 19948 "You all right?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_EVENT_KNIFE__020__M__1
TT 19949 "Damn... bastard..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_EVENT_KNIFE__027__M__1
TT 19950 "Ha... I... promised myself I'd never... do that again..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_EVENT_KNIFE__050__M__1
TT 19951 "Yes, well... just try not to get yourself killed..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_EVENT_KNIFE__070__M__1
TT 19952 "What was that?! This is madness! You never said..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_STRIKE__030__M__1
TT 19953 "Just... go talk to him." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_STRIKE__050__M__1
TT 19954 "I need... some time." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_STRIKE__060__M__1
TT 19955 "Amicia?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_IS_BACK__010__M__1
TT 19956 "Damn..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_IS_BACK__050__M__1
TT 19957 "When you may need me the most? No." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_IS_BACK__070__M__1
TT 19958 "I... I wanted to ask you—are you sure about all this? It seems like a heavy burden for him." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_SOPHIA__020__M__1
TT 19959 "Listen, we may not know each other well but... You're chasing ghosts. Ghosts that scare him." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_SOPHIA__040__M__1
TT 19960 "I can't... The question is, does he need more?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_SOPHIA__060__M__1
TT 19961 "I believe you... Fine." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_SOPHIA__080__M__1
TT 19962 "They're pretty heavily armed for slavers." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__ARMORED_SLAVERS_IDLE__010__M__1
TT 19963 "You know what's waiting for us inside the fort, right?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__ARMY_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 19964 "No..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__ARRESTED_SLAVERS_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 19965 "A lot can happen when there's money to be made..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__ARRESTED_SLAVERS_IDLE__040__M__1
TT 19966 "Yes... who knows what story lies behind it..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BABY_BOAT__020__M__1
TT 19967 "Some survive... Some are taken by the sea and sleep forever, cradled by the waves." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BABY_BOAT__040__M__1
TT 19968 "Then they become crab food." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BABY_BOAT__060__M__1
TT 19969 "Anytime." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BABY_BOAT__090__M__1
TT 19970 "Maybe we'll see some fire jumping and other... safe activities." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_ON_TRACK__030__M__1
TT 19971 "No, but... that symbol could be our chapel?... That “capella” where they took her!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_MAP__020__M__1
TT 19972 "It's a drawing... So, knowing the sanctuary's there, I think it's on the way to that big decorated tree, probably past the windmills." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_MAP__027__M__1
TT 19973 "Well, I can provide you with whatever you want!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_TOPIC__020__M__1
TT 19974 "We'll... finish here, and I'll take you on a trip, yes?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_TOPIC__050__M__1
TT 19975 "Soon." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_TOPIC__070__M__1
TT 19976 "Deal." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_TOPIC__090__M__1
TT 19977 "What?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BAD_SIGNS__030__M__1
TT 19978 "Amicia, we've got a dead man here!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BAD_SIGNS__080__M__1
TT 19979 "We need to be." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BAD_SIGNS__100__M__1
TT 19980 "Not their hideout, obviously..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BASEMENT__020__M__1
TT 19981 "Give me a moment..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BEFORE_SERIOUS_TALK__010__M__1
TT 19982 "Poor girl didn't have much of a brighter future..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BODIES__060__M__1
TT 19983 "Milo's work..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BODIES_TORCHES__030__M__1
TT 19984 "So there's something there..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BODIES_TORCHES__050__M__1
TT 19985 "Worm eaten..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BRIDGE_TUTO__010__M__1
TT 19986 "That bridge looks about to collapse..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BRIDGE_TUTO__030__M__1
TT 19987 "There's a rope and a grapple on this pole!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BRIDGE_TUTO__050__M__1
TT 19988 "Either they don't know or they don't care." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BRIGHTER_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 19989 "Milo said he worked for the Countess. She and the Count probably gave them this place..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BUSINESS_IDLE__010__M__1
TT 19990 "Yes. Dirty business." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BUSINESS_IDLE__030__M__1
TT 19991 "And there goes our way in..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CART_BRIDGE__040__M__1
TT 19992 "I agree." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CART_BRIDGE_IN__030__M__1
TT 19993 "Loud indeed. We should move." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_DOOR__020__M__1
TT 19994 "Hopefully no one heard that..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_DROP__010__M__1
TT 19995 "Be quick, please..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_HOLD__010__M__1
TT 19996 "It lifts a chandelier... A big one!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_MOVING__010__M__1
TT 19997 "The chain still looks pretty solid!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_MOVING__050__M__1
TT 19998 "Go on!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_PULL__020__M__1
TT 19999 "It's barbaric..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_COURTYARD__015__M__1
TT 20000 "Look, on the door... Your Order's symbol..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_COURTYARD__055__M__1
TT 20001 "Listen to me now! Stop this!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_EIGHTH_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 20002 "They're pretty recent. Who did this? Milo?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_ENTER__015__M__1
TT 20003 "So, what?... This chapel was dedicated to her?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_ENTER__030__M__1
TT 20004 "Stay down, Hugo!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_FIFTH_WAVE__040__M__1
TT 20005 "Amicia! We have to get inside the chapel! There's no other way!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_FINAL_WAVE__010__M__1
TT 20006 "What are you doing?! Hey! Stop!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_FINAL_WAVE__040__M__1
TT 20007 "No! Not yet!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_FIRST_WAVE__040__M__1
TT 20008 "You're not doing anything, boy!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_NINTH_WAVE__020__M__1
TT 20009 "Hugo! Let her!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_SEVENTH_WAVE__020__M__1
TT 20010 "Amicia! It's getting urgent!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_SEVENTH_WAVE__070__M__1
TT 20011 "Calm down! Remember what your sister told you!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_SIXTH_WAVE__030__M__1
TT 20012 "It's going to end badly, Amicia! There has to be a way out!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_THIRD_WAVE__010__M__1
TT 20013 "No! You stay there!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_THIRD_WAVE__040__M__1
TT 20014 "This Child thing is a beacon for lunatics..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHILD_IDLE__030__M__1
TT 20015 "What the hell?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLIFF_FALL_REACTION__030__M__1
TT 20016 "Well spotted! That's our way in." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSE_ROPE_BOLT__020__M__1
TT 20017 "Time to take a little look around?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSED_GATE__020__M__1
TT 20018 "So looks like we're conquering it, after all!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSED_GATE_VAULT__020__M__1
TT 20019 "So you'll rule this thing?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSED_GATE_VAULT__040__M__1
TT 20020 "A royal contract! I'm honoured!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSED_GATE_VAULT__060__M__1
TT 20021 "Oh, right. The fort and its chapel..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSED_GATE_VAULT__080__M__1
TT 20022 "Now come down!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__COME_DOWN__010__M__1
TT 20023 "Letting it sink in..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CONTINUE_CHECK__020__M__1
TT 20024 "Rats..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CONTINUE_CHECK__040__M__1
TT 20025 "No use. We should go." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CRANK__020__M__1
TT 20026 "They're everywhere... just like... murderers and traitors." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CROSSING_VILLAGE__020__M__1
TT 20027 "Where the hell is Milo?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CRYPT_ENTER__010__M__1
TT 20028 "Yes... Good work..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__DOOR__010__M__1
TT 20029 "That door looks like it's been stuck for a long time..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__DOOR_LOCKED__005__M__1
TT 20030 "Yes... We'll need a big push..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__DOOR_LOCKED__020__M__1
TT 20031 "I think... for now..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__DOOR_OPEN__020__M__1
TT 20032 "It's exhausting... But it's life." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__EXIT__060__M__1
TT 20033 "A cunning bird! It managed to make people believe it's evil..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FEATHER__050__M__1
TT 20034 "You should see me when I wake up. I'm the evilest." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FEATHER__100__M__1
TT 20035 "It still can be." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FEATHER_PATH__020__M__1
TT 20036 "They're here too..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FIRE_CROSS__030__M__1
TT 20037 "Yes... Bloody little opportunists..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FIRE_EXTINGUISHED__030__M__1
TT 20038 "Now... either it works... or I'm dead... I can't believe I'm doing this..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FIRE_LIT__020__M__1
TT 20039 "Damn..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FIRST_KILL__010__M__1
TT 20040 "Never seen you do... that." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FIRST_KILL__030__M__1
TT 20041 "Let's do this together..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__GATE_HALLWAY__030__M__1
TT 20042 "Look at them... They sure know how to celebrate!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FESTIVAL_TALK__030__M__1
TT 20043 "They don't need it. And WE don't need them to know." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FESTIVAL_TALK__050__M__1
TT 20044 "You just need to bounce back from this." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FESTIVAL_TALK__070__M__1
TT 20045 "You... think of something else!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FESTIVAL_TALK__090__M__1
TT 20046 "Well, a piece of it at least..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FLOWERPATH__020__M__1
TT 20047 "And that sanctuary still had a LOT to tell..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FLOWERPATH__050__M__1
TT 20048 "Hey, if you don't know where to go, don't forget about that map." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FOREST_NOMAP__010__M__1
TT 20049 "So... that was... I don't even know what that was..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_GOINGDOWN_START__005__M__1
TT 20050 "Pragmatic! I like that! Why not check that map again, unless you know where that tower is?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_GOINGDOWN_START__020__M__1
TT 20051 "Here we are! Looks like the real festivities have begun!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_NEW_THINGS__010__M__1
TT 20052 "My mother came from a wealthy family. They weren't exactly pleased when they found out my father was a smuggler. So off to a convent I went— to “cleanse” me of his sins." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_SOPHIA_STORY__010__M__1
TT 20053 "I'd rather be a sinner and be free. So I escaped. I joined my father, and..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_SOPHIA_STORY__030__M__1
TT 20054 "Hey, look around you. It's fine. We're centuries later, right?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_SOPHIA_STORY__070__M__1
TT 20055 "Hm. It's quiet... I think they're all at this feast." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_VILLAGE_NOMAP__010__M__1
TT 20056 "Their leader..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__IDLE_CHAPEL__005__M__1
TT 20057 "Milo. I know that name. Roams around the Mediterranean coasts. He's a butcher." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__IDLE_CHAPEL__020__M__1
TT 20058 "Can't believe you've been through all this before..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__IDLE_FORT_1__010__M__1
TT 20059 "I'm sorry for you, Hugo... But there'll be better times." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__IDLE_FORT_5__010__M__1
TT 20060 "How can you be so calm?..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__INTERACT_CART__020__M__1
TT 20061 "Obviously. Stupid question..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__INTERACT_CART__040__M__1
TT 20062 "Are you hurt?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__INTERACT_FALL__040__M__1
TT 20063 "I'd say... slavers, by the looks of it..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__INTRO_SLAVES__110__M__1
TT 20064 "They capture people... And sell them like animals..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__INTRO_SLAVES__130__M__1
TT 20065 "Shhh... Easy." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KILL_FORT_2__020__M__1
TT 20066 "We need to reach that chapel fast..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KILL_FORT_3__020__M__1
TT 20067 "That was a bit excessive, no?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KILLED_ALL_FORT__020__M__1
TT 20068 "Let's just... move forward, please." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KILLED_ALL_FORT__040__M__1
TT 20069 "Shit!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KNIFE_EVENT__060__M__1
TT 20070 "No... No!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KNIFE_EVENT__075__M__1
TT 20071 "Get... your hands... off her!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KNIFE_EVENT__080__M__1
TT 20072 "Try not to think about that..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__LADY_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 20073 "So, Hugo... You ever offered a flower to a lady your age?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__LIKE_FEATHER__010__M__1
TT 20074 "Hm... Moving on to something more exciting... Flowers... feathers..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__LIKE_FEATHER__030__M__1
TT 20075 "Why?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__LIKE_FEATHER__050__M__1
TT 20076 "I get it." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__LIKE_FEATHER__060__M__1
TT 20077 "Could be a lot. Milo's a big fish..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__MANY_SLAVERS_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 20078 "So, your Protector's supposed to have been taken there?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__MILO_LEFT__030__M__1
TT 20079 "More of them!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__MILO_REPUTATION__020__M__1
TT 20080 "There it is!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__PORTCULLIS_FOUND__010__M__1
TT 20081 "We'll never get through that..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__PORTCULLIS_INSIDE__005__M__1
TT 20082 "Amicia, Milo's right behind that wall..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__PORTCULLIS_MOVING__010__M__1
TT 20083 "Just... Making sure you're prepared..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__PORTCULLIS_MOVING__030__M__1
TT 20084 "How does it... How do you...?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__POST_RAT_CTRL_KILL__020__M__1
TT 20085 "No, nothing. Forget it. Let's move on." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__POST_RAT_CTRL_KILL__040__M__1
TT 20086 "I gave you my word." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__PRISM_1ST_MOVE__040__M__1
TT 20087 "Let me know which fire you want to go to, I'll open a path to it!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__PRISM_REMINDER__010__M__1
TT 20088 "A golden staircase up." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__PULL_SUCCESS__030__M__1
TT 20089 "Are you...? He's doing that, yes?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__RAT_CTRL_KILL__010__M__1
TT 20090 "Fine... Fine..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__RAT_CTRL_KILL__030__M__1
TT 20091 "I wonder what happened to Basilius..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__RATS_PASSED__050__M__1
TT 20092 "You see that? They've barricaded the temple door." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__REACH_TEMPLE_DOOR__020__M__1
TT 20093 "I think that's it. Ready to go?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__READY_TO_FORT__010__M__1
TT 20094 "Hey! Be nice to old people!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__REUNION__020__M__1
TT 20095 "Hey! Here!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__REUNITED_WITH_SOPHIA__010__M__1
TT 20096 "What the hell happened?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__REUNITED_WITH_SOPHIA__040__M__1
TT 20097 "With them around, I don't... maybe! But it's going to be... No matter!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__REUNITED_WITH_SOPHIA__060__M__1
TT 20098 "I need you to start that fire below first!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__REUNITED_WITH_SOPHIA__070__M__1
TT 20099 "Hugo, wait... Would my knight conquer that tower for me?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__RUN_TOWER__020__M__1
TT 20100 "I want to see how you charge it!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__RUN_TOWER__030__M__1
TT 20101 "Claim it for me!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__RUN_TOWER__040__M__1
TT 20102 "Go!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__RUN_TOWER__050__M__1
TT 20103 "Wow... Look at that view!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SEA__010__M__1
TT 20104 "Not yet, but it will come back..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SEA__030__M__1
TT 20105 "No, not until I've repaid my debt to your sister." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SEA__050__M__1
TT 20106 "She didn't tell you?! She saved my life!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SEA__070__M__1
TT 20107 "Well, me too!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SEA__100__M__1
TT 20108 "Can't say I'll miss this one." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SECOND_AREA_KILL_1ST__010__M__1
TT 20109 "We really need to get out of this mess..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SECOND_AREA_KILL_2ND__020__M__1
TT 20110 "Amicia..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SECOND_AREA_KILL_4TH__010__M__1
TT 20111 "Don't get carried away..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SECOND_AREA_KILL_4TH__030__M__1
TT 20112 "That's two..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SECOND_KILL__010__M__1
TT 20113 "All right... Do what you have to..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SECOND_KILL__030__M__1
TT 20114 "There's our fort!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SEE_FORT__020__M__1
TT 20115 "I... think, yes!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SEE_FORT__060__M__1
TT 20116 "Yeah, well... let's just walk." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SERIOUS_TALK__100__M__1
TT 20117 "That's what they do..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SLAVE_RAGDOLL__030__M__1
TT 20118 "There was a child here... Charming." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SLAVE_RAGDOLL__060__M__1
TT 20119 "They killed so many..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SO_MANY_DEAD_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 20120 "Don't let me down..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SOPHIA_SHOW_PRISM__010__M__1
TT 20121 "All right. I'm doing this." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SOPHIA_SHOW_PRISM__040__M__1
TT 20122 "Yes, right..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SOPHIA_SHOW_PRISM__043__M__1
TT 20123 "So far so good!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SOPHIA_SHOW_PRISM__046__M__1
TT 20124 "Whew... Yes! My greatest treasure! I wasn't sure it would channel enough of that fire's light..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__SOPHIA_SHOW_PRISM__060__M__1
TT 20125 "No... Some kind of temple." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__TEMPLE_IN_SIGHT__020__M__1
TT 20126 "So? Found a way to get us out of here?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__TEMPLE_UPSTAIRS__015__M__1
TT 20127 "How could they... ha..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__TORTURE__020__M__1
TT 20128 "So, the chapel's on the other side of that trench, right?..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__TRENCH_OPENING__010__M__1
TT 20129 "Look, they're crossing too!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__TRENCH_TWO__020__M__1
TT 20130 "Listen, I can cover us three with it, but I'll need another fire to get us through... this hell..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__TUTO_PRISM__010__M__1
TT 20131 "Right! I'll leave the rats to you... Just tell me which fire you want to go to now, and when you want me to stop..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__TUTO_PRISM__030__M__1
TT 20132 "Hm. Small problem here..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__UNSTABLE_BRIDGE__010__M__1
TT 20133 "Fine. Looks a bit safer..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__WATER_WAY__010__M__1
TT 20134 "Fine." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__WATER_WAY__012__M__1
TT 20135 "Looks a bit safer..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__WATER_WAY__015__M__1
TT 20136 "Hey, Hugo!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__WATER_WAY__050__M__1
TT 20137 "I know it's hard, but please, stay focused!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__WATER_WAY__070__M__1
TT 20138 "It probably is. But we're still together." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__WATER_WINDOW__025__M__1
TT 20139 "Prepare for some noise..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__WEDGE_INTERACT__020__M__1
TT 20140 "It still doesn't tell us where Milo is." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__WHERE_IS_MILO__010__M__1
TT 20141 "That chandelier looks heavy enough to ram the door open! We'd just need a way to lift it." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__HELPER__CHANDELIER_1__010__M__1
TT 20142 "I can get the chandelier up with that crank. Just tell me when!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__HELPER__CHANDELIER_2__010__M__1
TT 20143 "See another fire you could light up for me?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__HELPER__FIRE_1__010__M__1
TT 20144 "Amicia! Light up that fire over there! Then I'll be able to use my prism!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__HELPER__FIRE_2__010__M__1
TT 20145 "Think you can use your crossbow trick to ram the door open with that chandelier?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__HELPER__RAM_1__010__M__1
TT 20146 "Hey! How about you use that rope to pull the chandelier and get the door open?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__HELPER__RAM_2__010__M__1
TT 20147 "I reckon your crossbow could get us inside the temple. We'd need to find you a rope." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__HELPER__TEMPLE_WEDGE_1__010__M__1
TT 20148 "Could be there's a rope on one of those roofs? That's all we'd need to get inside that temple." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__HELPER__TEMPLE_WEDGE_2__010__M__1
TT 20149 "We're good." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__460_BACK_FROM_SANCTUARY__010__M__1
TT 20150 "Especially you. You're the sneakiest child I've ever met." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__460_BACK_FROM_SANCTUARY__015__M__1
TT 20151 "It surely doesn't sound as... appealing." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__470_LEAVE_TO_FORT__020__M__1
TT 20152 "There is only one way to find out." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__470_LEAVE_TO_FORT__040__M__1
TT 20153 "There's a storm coming." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__480_ENTER_FORT__030__M__1
TT 20154 "Trust me." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__480_ENTER_FORT__042__M__1
TT 20155 "He's sad... All this because of a dream." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__480_ENTER_FORT__050__M__1
TT 20156 "The day I stopped being a child." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__480_ENTER_FORT__070__M__1
TT 20157 "Hey! That's a pretty flower!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__480_ENTER_FORT__106__M__1
TT 20158 "Of course!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__480_ENTER_FORT__120__M__1
TT 20159 "Time passes, sweetheart... They grow up!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__480_ENTER_FORT__140__M__1
TT 20160 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__480_ENTER_FORT_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 20161 "Goddamn maniacs..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__140__M__1
TT 20162 "What... the... hell?..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__290__M__1
TT 20163 "I'm going! Hide in the cart when you can!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__490_ENTER_FORT2__110__M__1
TT 20164 "“Protect one, Protect all.”" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__495_LEGACY__020__M__1
TT 20165 "That's a nice dynasty of morons you got there..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__495_LEGACY__040__M__1
TT 20166 "This thing again... Why?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__495_LEGACY__060__M__1
