TT 20168 "Sure... It makes sense." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__495_LEGACY__150__M__1
TT 20169 "Whatever, just another day in your life" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__495_LEGACY__185__M__1
TT 20170 "Yes" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__495_LEGACY__200__M__1
TT 20171 "EMPTY" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__495_LEGACY_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 20172 "No... She is." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE__110__M__1
TT 20173 "Don't say anything..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE__120__M__1
TT 20174 "Here we go! They're coming!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE__160__M__1
TT 20175 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 20176 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE_ONOM__110__M__1
TT 20177 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE_ONOM__120__M__1
TT 20178 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__500_FRESCOE_ONOM__150__M__1
TT 20179 "HUGO!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__510_END__045__M__1
TT 20180 "AMICIA! THROUGH HERE!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__510_END__120__M__1
TT 20181 "To the sea, quick!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__510_END__130__M__1
TT 20182 "Hugo. Look at me." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__510_END__134__M__1
TT 20183 "Hugo, look at me!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__510_END__136__M__1
TT 20184 "Why are you crying?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__510_END__140__M__1
TT 20185 "Calm down! Now you listen to me... I've never seen anything like you two." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__510_END__150__M__1
TT 20186 "And, for some stupid reason, I like you. And I like you at the shittiest worst of your life, right? I'm fine with that. Even the strangest things happen for a reason. Sailors stories are full of it. That said..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__510_END__155__M__1
TT 20187 "YOU need to seriously calm down and listen to what adults tell you! Deal?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__510_END__157__M__1
