TT 20194 "Door's pretty ruined..." VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__2ND_TWISTED_DOOR__010__M__1
TT 20195 "You know... I'm starting to see her in you... Aelia..." VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__AFTER_EXPLOSION__020__M__1
TT 20196 "Because you don't let go." VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__AFTER_EXPLOSION__040__M__1
TT 20197 "These bastards are not giving up!" VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__BEAM_WALK__030__M__1
