TT 20210 "We need some fire, Amicia, quick!" VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__BRIDGERATS__011__M__1
TT 20211 "What?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__BRIDGERATS__030__M__1
