TT 20229 "Definitely... Prepare to run... just in case..." VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__CISTERN_LEVER__018__M__1
TT 20230 "This place is a goddamn underground fortress!" VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__CISTERN_LEVER__035__M__1
TT 20231 "Move! Move! Move!" VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__CLIMB_BURST__030__M__1
TT 20232 "She'll be fine. She's the most resourceful woman I've ever met!" VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__CONTINUE__020__M__1
