TT 20237 "Urgh... What are we... breathing?" VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__CORRIDOR__020__M__1
TT 20238 "Well, she means it, boy. Trust her." VO__SOPHIA__CH11__CHATTER__CROSSING_CART__060__M__1
